SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_CONTAINER,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_MFGR,
    P.P_BRAND,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ADDRESS,
    S.S_PHONE,
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    C.C_PHONE,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    R.R_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
S.S_COMMENT, S.S_NATIONKEY, S.S_NAME, S.S_PHONE, S.S_ADDRESS, S.S_SUPPKEY, S.S_ACCTBAL,
LI.L_SHIPMODE, LI.L_TAX, LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LI.L_COMMITDATE, LI.L_ORDERKEY, LI.L_RETURNFLAG, LI.L_LINESTATUS, LI.L_RECEIPTDATE, LI.L_PARTKEY, LI.L_LINENUMBER, LI.L_SHIPDATE, LI.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, LI.L_SUPPKEY, LI.L_DISCOUNT, LI.L_COMMENT, LI.L_QUANTITY
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' AND S.S_NAME LIKE 'Heavy%'

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT),
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_SIZE) DESC, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR) + LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND) + LENGTH(PART.P_NAME) + LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE) + LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_PART_DESCR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_DESCR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_DESCR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_TAX) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_DESCR_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SHIPPED,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_BRAND, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (
        SELECT
            AVG(PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
        FROM
            PARTSUPP PS2
        JOIN
            PART P2 ON PS2.PS_PARTKEY = P2.P_PARTKEY
        JOIN
            CUSTOMER C2 ON P2.P_PARTKEY = C2.C_CUSTKEY
        JOIN
            SUPPLIER S2 ON PS2.PS_SUPPKEY = S2.S_SUPPKEY
        WHERE
            C2.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT_X' -- replace 'SEGMENT_X' with the actual market segment name
        GROUP BY
            C2.C_NAME, P2.P_NAME
    )
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (
        SELECT AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
        FROM PARTSUPP PS
        JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
        JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
        JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
        JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
    )
AND N.N_NAME IN ('Country1', 'Country2', 'Country3')
AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MarketSegment4'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    C.C_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLYER_COUNTRY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_SUPPKEY IN (SELECT S_SUPPKEY FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SomeRegion'))))
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS ExtendedPrice,
    LI.L_QUANTITY AS Quantity
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON LI.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'THAILAND')
AND
    P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P2.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART P2)
AND
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    S.S_ACCTBAL < (SELECT AVG(S2.S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER S2)
ORDER BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS TotalSuppliers,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN ORDERS ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    r.r_name AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_custkey) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(o.o_totalprice) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalRevenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_custkey) > 100
    AND AVG(o.o_totalprice) > 50
    AND SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) > 100000
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) > 5
    AND AVG(s.s_acctbal) > 0

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' THEN O.O_TOTALPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalShippedOrdersValue,
    AVG(L.L_QUANTITY) AS AverageQuantityPerOrder,
    MAX(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS MaxCustomerAccountBalance,
    MIN(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS MinSupplierAccountBalance,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    PART AS P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION AS R1 ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R1.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    NATION AS N2 ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N2.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_TAX > 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalExtendedPriceWithTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS LineItemCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    NS.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUM(PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PSS
JOIN
    PART P ON PSS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION NS ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON NS.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NS.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
    AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Airshipments,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnedQuantity
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_REGIONKEY
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_CUSTKEY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_CUSTKEY) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TOTAL_ORDER_TYPES,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AVG_RETURN_FLAG_A,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_F,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 100
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 20
    AND AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) > 15

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    SUM(CASE WHEN NATION.N_NAME LIKE '%%USA%%' THEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE 0 END) / SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS USA_SUPPLYCOST_PERCENTAGE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN NATION.N_NAME LIKE '%%Europe%%' THEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE 0 END) / SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS EUROPE_SUPPLYCOST_PERCENTAGE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
    ORDER BY SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN PART.P_SIZE END) AS HighDiscountPartsSize,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT <= 0 THEN PART.P_SIZE END) AS NoDiscountPartsSize
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS))

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 500 AND AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) > 200 AND AVG(S_ACCTBAL) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 5
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 15

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierAccountBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatusLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE IS NOT NULL THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS OrderCount,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceiptDate
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrderLineItems,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgOrderQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HighPriorityOrderCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2-HIGH' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HighOrderCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '3-NORMAL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NormalOrderCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '4-LOW' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS LowOrderCount
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS Avg_TotalPrice,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AccountBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_QuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS Avg_OrderCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_LineITEMCommentLength,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LineStatus
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY -- Assuming O_CUSTKEY refers to the foreign key in CUSTOMER table, modify as necessary
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'AFRICA')
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE
HAVING
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_TYPE LIKE '%Metal%'
    AND NATION.N_NAME NOT IN ('Antarctica', 'Europe')
    AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
    AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL < (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierAverageBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    MIN(LI.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS EarliestReceivedDate,
    MAX(LI.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS LatestReceivedDate
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME LIKE 'North%')
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_PHONE As CustomerPhone,
    C.C_ACCTBAL As CustomerBal,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    S.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierBal,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP) -- This assumes PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY is unique and correctly links to NATION through PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
       CASE
           WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART) THEN 'Large & High Price'
           WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE <= (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART) THEN 'Large & Average Price'
           WHEN PART.P_SIZE < 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART) THEN 'Small & High Price'
           ELSE 'Small & Average Price'
       END AS PriceCategory
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE (PART.P_SIZE >= 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART))
   OR (PART.P_SIZE >= 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE <= (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART))
   OR (PART.P_SIZE < 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART))
   OR (PART.P_SIZE < 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE <= (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT R.R_REGIONKEY) AS UniqueRegions,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS UniqueSuppliers,
    OT.O_ORDERPRIORITY
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN (SELECT DISTINCT O_ORDERPRIORITY FROM ORDERS) OT ON TRUE
WHERE
    R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME IN ('USA', 'Canada'))
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    OT.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    CASE
        WHEN PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP) THEN 'AboveAvgCost'
        ELSE 'BelowAvgCost'
    END AS CostCategory,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    C.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey,
    C.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipmodeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLinestatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipinstructLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOrders,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_PARTSUPP,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength_PART,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_PART,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_REGION,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS PS_SUPPLYCOST_AVG,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS PS_AVAILQTY_SUM,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS DistinctPSCommentCount,
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE) AS PartSizeSum,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS NATION_REGIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_MFGR, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    n.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME NOT IN (SELECT DISTINCT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION))

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            PART.P_PARTKEY
        FROM
            PARTSUPP
        JOIN
            PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
        GROUP BY
            PART.P_PARTKEY
        HAVING
            SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100
    )
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    su.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    r.R_NAME As Region_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER su ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    su.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    r.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'Building'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'Furniture'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN 'Household'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'Automobile'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE LIKE '%electronic%')
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_CONTAINER,
    P_NAME,
    S_NAME,
    N_NAME,
    N_REGIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_P_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_C_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_S_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_AVAILABLE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_CONTAINER,
    P_NAME,
    S_NAME,
    N_NAME,
    N_REGIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS N_AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS PART_AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS C_AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS S_AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS N_AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS PART_AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS C_AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS S_AvgNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS PART_AvgSize,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
PART.P_CONTAINER AS PartContainer,
CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_CONTAINER, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY) > 1

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AS CustomerCustKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AS SupplierSuppKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME As RegionName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD POLISHED BRASS' THEN 'STANDARD POLISHED BRASS'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS PartTypeCategorized
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGIONS.R_REGIONKEY,
    REGIONS.R_COMMENT
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN REGION REGIONS ON REGIONS.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY > 0
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY > 0
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY > 0
    AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY > 0
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CASE
        WHEN REGION.R_NAME = 'ASIA' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
  AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
  AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
  AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
  AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
  AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
  AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
  AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
  AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
  AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
  AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
  PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
  AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0
  AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 0

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(Length(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustAddrLen,
    AVG(Length(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLen,
    AVG(Length(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustCommentLen,
    AVG(Length(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSuppCommentLen,
    AVG(Length(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLen,
    AVG(Length(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSuppPhoneLen,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQty,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeys,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgManfLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS Supplier_Count_With_Positive_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL <= 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS Supplier_Count_With_Non_Positive_Balance,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE)
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_SIZE) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'UNPLANNED' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END), COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN REGION.R_NAME LIKE '%Asia%' THEN NATION.N_NATIONKEY END), CASE
        WHEN AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) THEN 'Suppliers have higher avg. account balance'
        ELSE 'Customers have higher avg. account balance'
END AS acct_balance_comparison,
CASE
    WHEN COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'UNPLANNED' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) > 0 THEN 'Unplanned market segment exists'
    ELSE 'No unplanned market segment found'
END AS unplanned_market_segment_check
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_PART_MFGR_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DISTINCT_PART_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_BRAND, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM 
    NATION
INNER JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, 
    NATION.N_COMMENT, 
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    SUM(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    SUM(L.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 10
    AND SUM(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000
    AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 500
    AND AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 300

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_SUPPLIER,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS HouseholdCustKeyCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Other' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS OtherCustKeyCount
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN ('HOUSEHOLD', 'Other')
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumUniqueOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    L_LINENUMBER AS LineNumberOfOrder
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT IS NOT NULL THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS UniqueCommentsCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    MIN(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MIN_SUPPLY_COST,
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MAX_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    MIN(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAIL_QTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AVERAGE_TYPE_LENGTH,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AVERAGE_SIZE,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAIL_QTY,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM
    NATION INNER JOIN ORDERS ON TRUE INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_COMMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TOTAL_TAX,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Distinct_OrderKeys,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Min_ExtendedPrice,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Max_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipMode_Length,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceiptDate
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) AS OrderMonth, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) As DeliveryMonth, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice, REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE IN ('AIR', 'OTHER')
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, LineItem.L_SHIPMODE, REGION.R_NAME, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, Region.R_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (
    SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
    FROM PART
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
)
AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (
    SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    FROM NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT REGION.R_NAME) > 1
)
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_MFGR)),
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)),
    P_TYPE,
    N_NAME,
    C_NAME,
    R_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY P_TYPE, N_NAME, C_NAME, R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    SUM(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    MIN(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MinExtendedPrice,
    MAX(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN O.O_TOTALPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS HighPriorityOrderPrice
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT 
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    P_MFGR AS MFGR,
    N_NAME AS NationName
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    P_MFGR, N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O_ship' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalShippedOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY)) AS AvgCustKeyLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgTotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneNumberLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    n.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA') -- Assuming 'NORTH AMERICA' exists in REGION table
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG LIKE '%R%' THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END AS HasReturn,
    AVG(L_TAX),
    SUM(L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE, L_RETURNFLAG, L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CASE
        WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0 THEN 'Yes'
        ELSE 'No'
    END AS HasSupplier,
    AVG(CASE WHEN S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY THEN L_DISCOUNT ELSE NULL END) AS AverageDiscount,
    AVG(CASE WHEN C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY THEN C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AverageAccountBalance,
    R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
    LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
    RIGHT JOIN LINEITEM L ON S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
    LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) AS UniquePartTypes,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPartRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_MFGR_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_SIZE,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_Retail,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlag_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_ShipInstruct_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Distinct_Orders,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Orders_With_ShipDate,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE IS NOT NULL THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice_WithShipment,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE IS NULL THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice_WithoutShipment
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructionsLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS NationRegionId,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY AS RegionRegionId
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_PART_MFGR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_PART_BRAND_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, 
    PART.P_NAME, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGRLengthPart,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLengthPart,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQuantity,
    P_SIZE AS PartSizeGroup
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P_SIZE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CASE
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Canceled'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'P' THEN 'Delivered'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ORDER_STATUS_CATEGORY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN SUPPLIER.S_PHONE IS NULL THEN 'No phone'
        ELSE 'Phone number exists'
    END AS SUPPLIER_PHONE_STATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE DESC,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DISTINCT_SUPPLIER_KEYS,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_PART_RETAILPRICE,
    SUM(OL.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TOTAL_ORDER_PRICE,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS OL ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = OL.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 50
    AND AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100.00
    AND SUM(OL.O_TOTALPRICE) > 100000.00
    AND AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000.00

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) > 500
    AND SUM(LI.L_DISCOUNT) > 1000

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity,
    AVG(Customer.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 8
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 12
    AND AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) > 15
    AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
    AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 500

SELECT PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnableLineItemCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DiscountLineItemCount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLineItemQuantity
FROM
    NATION
        INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
        LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returnable'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 'Discount'
        ELSE 'Neither'
    END

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS DiscountedQuantityShipped,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT = 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS NonDiscountedQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRCommentLen,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgTotalPrice,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnableItems,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLen
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
