INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON c.C_CUSTKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    r.R_NAME = 'ASIA'
    AND p.P_NAME LIKE 'S_%' -- Example filter for parts starting with 'S'
    AND li.L_SHIPDATE BETWEEN '2000-01-01' AND '2000-12-31' -- Example timeframe filter
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS DistinctCommentCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR, PART.P_TYPE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_COMMITDATE, L.L_RETURNFLAG, L.L_LINESTATUS, L.L_RECEIPTDATE, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPDATE, L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, L.L_DISCOUNT, L.L_COMMENT
FROM ORDERS O
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' AND L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
AND O.O_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE O_TOTALPRICE > 1000)
AND O.O_CUSTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 50000)
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgLength_C_COMMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgLength_C_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgLength_C_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLength_C_ADDRESS,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLength_S_COMMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgLength_S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgLength_S_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLength_S_ADDRESS,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS Avg_L_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLength_L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLength_L_RETURNFLAG,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLength_L_LINESTATUS,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS Sum_L_QUANTITY,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS Sum_L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeErrorLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    MIN(PART.P_SIZE) AS MinPartSize
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE
HAVING
    PART.P_SIZE IS NOT NULL

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SuppliersNation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_NATIONKEY) > 1
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY * PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgWeightedSize
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY * PART.P_SIZE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS OrdersWithReturns,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST), N_NAME, AVG(P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(C_ACCTBAL), R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY R_NAME, N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKey = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION))  -- Get the Nation with the smallest region key (assumed to be the smallest region to simplify, could adjust for real-world scenarios)
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, 
    PART.P_NAME, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLen,
       SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalQualifiedLineItemsQuantity,
       SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumLineItemsWithReturnFlags,
       AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
       AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
       AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_COMMENT

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    nyt.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    nty.N_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION nyt ON n.N_REGIONKEY = nyt.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION nty ON n.N_NATIONKEY = nty.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerSegment, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped, REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, N_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME, N_REGIONKEY, R_NAME, PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'North America'))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000
    AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 500

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS AvgOrderShipPriority,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS AirshipsTotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS RailshipsTotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TruckshipsTotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) As AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY) AS DistinctNationCount,
AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = 1)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), ORDERS.O_CLERK AS O_CLERK FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_CLERK ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AVERAGE_ORDER_PRICE,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS AVERAGE_SHIP_PRIORITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SHIPPED,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS TOTAL_RETURNED_ORDERS
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS NationRegionKey
FROM PartSupp
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PartSupp.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_SIZE, NATION.N_REGIONKEY
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'ASIA')

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
FROM
    PART
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR
ORDER BY
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SuppCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_LinInstrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegNameLength,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Max_ExtendedPrice,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Min_Discount,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceiptDate,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ReturnStatus
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG
ORDER BY
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(CASE WHEN P_TYPE = 'Component' THEN P_RETAILPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS Average_Retail_Price_Components,
    AVG(CASE WHEN P_TYPE = 'Finished Goods' THEN P_RETAILPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS Average_Retail_Price_Finished_Goods,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) > 1
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(PART.P_PARTKEY) AS AvgPartKey, AVG(NATION.N_NATIONKEY) AS AvgNationKey, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS AvgCustomerKey, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS AvgSupplierKey,
SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty, SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBal,
AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT DISTINCT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE AS Total_Price,
    li.L_QUANTITY AS Quantity,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As Extended_Price,
    li.L_DISCOUNT As Discount
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION)
    AND c.C_CUSTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER)
    AND s.S_SUPPKEY IN (SELECT S_SUPPKEY FROM SUPPLIER)
    AND o.O_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT L_ORDERKEY FROM LINEITEM)
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER))

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)) AS AvgOrderPriorityLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS AvgShipPriority,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthSupplier,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS TotalLineItemCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthLineItem,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    O_CLERK AS OrderClerk,
    L_COMMITDATE AS LineItemCommitDate
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    O_CLERK,
    L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    S.S_NATIONKEY,
    S.S_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    S.S_NATIONKEY,
    S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > (
        SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE)
        FROM PART
        WHERE P_CONTAINER LIKE 'S_%'
    )
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT' THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS ComponentCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT' THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) > 50

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST * PART.P_SIZE) THEN 'High AcctBal vs SupplyCost'
        ELSE 'Low AcctBal vs SupplyCost'
    END AS ACCTBal_SupplyCost_Comparison
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY REGION.R_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (
        SELECT N.N_NAME
        FROM NATION N
        JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
        WHERE R.R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA'
    )
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, CUST.C_NAME, CUST.C_ACCTBAL
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeys,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 10

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS2.PS_PARTKEY
                   FROM PARTSUPP PS2
                   JOIN PART P2 ON PS2.PS_PARTKEY = P2.P_PARTKEY
                   GROUP BY PS2.PS_PARTKEY
                   HAVING SUM(PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000)
AND N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = 1)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    P.P_PARTKEY ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    (SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) / SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)) * 100 AS RETURN_DISCOUNT_PERCENTAGE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY) AS DistinctNationKeys
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    N_REGIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOT_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_CONTAINER_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AVG_PART_TYPE_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_PART_BRAND_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LEN
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT, N_REGIONKEY

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY AND c.C_CUSTKEY = (SELECT p.P_PARTKEY FROM PART p WHERE p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT MIN(P_PARTKEY) FROM PART)) -- join with a dummy PART table condition to ensure the left join
GROUP BY 
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 THEN 'High Quantity'
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY <= 100 AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 50 THEN 'Medium Quantity'
        ELSE 'Low Quantity'
    END DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DISTINCT_CUSTOMER_CUSTKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS customer_count,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS avg_acctbal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS avg_supp_name_length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS avg_supp_phone_length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS avg_tax,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS total_quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS avg_comment_length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS avg_region_comment_length,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Return'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT IS NOT NULL THEN 'Discount'
        ELSE 'Normal'
    END AS PurchaseStatus
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY IS NOT NULL
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY IS NOT NULL
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY IS NOT NULL
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY IS NOT NULL

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'E%')
    AND Li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
    AND Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM LINEITEM)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Nation_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Part_Container_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Part_Comment_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_Part_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_Part_Type_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND
    PART.P_TYPE LIKE '%BRUSH%'
AND
    NATION.N_NAME IN ('UNITED STATES', 'CANADA')
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 1
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMfgLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPartBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT PART.P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
       AVG(CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE <= 5 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_SupplyCost_Small,
       AVG(CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 5 AND PART.P_SIZE <= 10 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_SupplyCost_Medium,
       AVG(CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 10 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_SupplyCost_Large
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMERS_COUNTE,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIERS_COUNTE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS TOTAL_PARTKEYS,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AVG_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE AS OrderTotal,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS LineItemPrice,
    YEAR(O.O_ORDERDATE) AS OrderYear,
    L.L_TAX AS TaxAmount,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    CASE
        WHEN L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Air'
        WHEN L.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN 'Sea'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ShippingMode
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY AND C.C_CUSTKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY AND C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgLengthNationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthOrdersComment,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY) AS AvgOrdersCUSTKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgLengthOrdersClerk,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthSupplierAddress,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)) AS AvgLengthLineItemLineNumber,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthLineItemComment,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgLengthRegionName,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE,
    ORDERS.O_CLERK AS O_CLERK,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE,
    O_CLERK,
    R_NAME,
    N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPartRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLen,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Unreturned_Items,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN ORDERS ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS
FROM NATION
JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY  -- Assuming O_CUSTKEY in ORDERS refers to the customer's NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNATION,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalanceCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSUPPLIER,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalanceSUPPLIER,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 END) AS ReturnFlagATotal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 END) AS ReturnFlagRTotal
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost, COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers, AVG(N_NATIONKEY) AS AvgNationKey, AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength, AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize, AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN NATION ON TRUE -- NATION is joined implicitly with no condition, as there's no common column mentioned
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_Comment_Length,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Supplier_Comment_Length,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_LineItem_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_LineItem_Discount,
    P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS Avg_Part_Type_Length
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY, P_TYPE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY)
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) DESC,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS PartRetailPrice,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthCustomer
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 10

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
       AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
       COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
       NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
       PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
       CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 10000 THEN 'HighBalance' ELSE 'LowBalance' END AS BalanceSegment
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS total_sales,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_partkey) ASdistinct_parts_count,
    AVG(li.l_discount) AS average_discount
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE
    r.r_name IN ('AMERICA', 'EUROPE') -- supposing we only consider suppliers from 'AMERICA' and 'EUROPE'
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name, s.s_name

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) as AvgExtendedPrice, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) as TotalQuantityShipped
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
HAVING SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

SELECT
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
  AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
  SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY,
  COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustCount,
  SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), ORDERS.O_CLERK AS O_CLERK FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_CLERK

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_CustMKTSegmentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS HighBalanceCustCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupPhoneLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupAcctBal
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 100000
ORDER BY
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT 
    C_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AVERAGE_PART_SIZE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AVERAGE_TYPE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_PHONETIME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_BALANCE
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY -- assuming C_CUSTKEY is linked to L_ORDERKEY through some implicit relationship (not explicitly defined in provided schema)
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS N_RegionKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Container_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_Size,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Total_Available_Quantity,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_TypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_BrandLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierAccountBalance,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Total_SupplyCost
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, PART.P_TYPE, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Customer_Nation,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE As Total_Order_Price,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As Line_Item_Price,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT As Line_Item_Discount
FROM
    ORDERS O
    JOIN LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN NATION N ON O.O_CUSTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)) ))
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION))))
ORDER BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)) AS AvgOrderPriorityLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)) > 10 THEN 'Long Priority'
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) > 50 THEN 'Long Comment'
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 30 THEN 'Long Comment'
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 20 THEN 'Long Name'
        ELSE 'All Short'
    END AS StringLengthCategory
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 50 THEN 'Large'
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE <= 50 AND PART.P_SIZE > 20 THEN 'Medium'
        ELSE 'Small'
    END AS SIZE_CATEGORY,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'SMALL PART')
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShippingInstructionLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS AvgReturnRate,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS CountOrdersWithReturns
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C.C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER C GROUP BY C.C_NATIONKEY HAVING COUNT(*) > 100) -- Example: Only include nations with more than 100 customers
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShipModeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderKeys,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLineItemLineNumber,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructionLength
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 1000 AND AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) > 100

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    s.S_NAME, -- assuming S_NAME exists in SUPPLIER table
    c.C_NAME,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY -- assuming S_SUPPKEY in SUPPLIER table
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, p.P_BRAND, s.S_NAME, c.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgREGIONNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    MIN(PART.P_SIZE) AS MinPartSize,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCount
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    NATION ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) > 3 AND AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) > 15 AND AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) > 10
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthRegion,
    PART.P_MFGR AS PartManufacturer,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    PART.P_TYPE AS P_Type,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AVG_OrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalDistinctOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS Avg_OrderCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_QuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    LINEITEM,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY AND
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AND
    ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    ORDERS.O_CLERK

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBal,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
        INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
        INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100
    AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) > 10000
    AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AVG_PART_SIZE,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    AVG(o.o_totalprice) AS avg_order_price,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS total_customers,
    AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS avg_supplier_balance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
LEFT JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.n_nationkey = o.o_custkey
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DifferentPartsCount,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) As AvgRegionNameLength,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_BRAND, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    p.p_name AS Part,
    c.c_name AS Customer,
    s.s_name AS Supplier,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) AS TotalPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_orderkey) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(li.l_quantity) AS AverageQuantity
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name, c.c_name, s.s_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) > 10000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    P.P_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LL.L_QUANTITY AS QuantityShipped,
    LL.L_DISCOUNT AS Discount,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * (1 - LL.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalPriceBeforeTax,
    LL.L_TAX AS Tax,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * (1 - LL.L_DISCOUNT) + LL.L_TAX AS TotalPriceAfterTax
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LL ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LL.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON LL.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LL.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    LL.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'P') -- only including shipped and partial orders
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE >= DATE('1998-01-01') -- filtering on a specific date range
    AND N.N_REGIONKEY = 12 -- filter on a particular region
ORDER BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    LL.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_COMMENT,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
    REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_COMMITDATE, L.L_RETURNFLAG, L.L_LINESTATUS, L.L_RECEIPTDATE, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPDATE, L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, L.L_DISCOUNT, L.L_COMMENT, L.L_QUANTITY
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' AND L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' AND O.O_TOTALPRICE > (SELECT AVG(O_TOTALPRICE) FROM ORDERS)
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_SHIPDATE ASC, O.O_TOTALPRICE DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    MAX(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)),
    MIN(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE
