SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_ORDERSTATUS FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    p.P_CONTAINER,
    p.P_MFGR
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    p.P_CONTAINER,
    p.P_MFGR,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 5 AND
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) < 50 AND
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 200

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_NATIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (
        SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
        FROM LINEITEM
        JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
        JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        GROUP BY YEAR(L_RECEIPTDATE)
        HAVING COUNT(*) > 20
    )

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'RETAIL' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS RetailCustomerAverAccountBalance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'WHOLESALE' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS WholesaleCustomerAverageAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShipmodeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionIdCommentLength
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS COUNT_RETURNABLE_ORDERS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS RETURNABLE_ITEMS_COUNT
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) > 10
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalextendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    MIN(LI.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS EarliestReceiptDate,
    MAX(LI.L_SHIPDATE) AS LatestShipDate
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOrderClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLineItemLineNumber,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ReturnFlagCategory
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS customer_name,
    MAX(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS max_supply_cost,
    MIN(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS min_available_quantity,
    p.P_NAME AS part_name,
    p.P_TYPE AS part_type,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS part_retail_price,
    n.N_NAME AS nation_name
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, p.P_RETAILPRICE, n.N_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
    AND MIN(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) < (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT 
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalOrderedQuantity,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON LI.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT,
    P.P_CONTAINER,
    P.P_MFGR,
    P.P_COMMENT,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_PHONE,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND 
    P.P_SIZE > (SELECT AVG(P_SIZE) FROM PART)
AND 
    C.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA'))
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NATION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_MKTSEGMENT_Length,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_LineItem_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LINESTATUS_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Distinct_L_OrderKey_Count,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Sum_L_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_LineItem_COMMENT_Length
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_PartAvailability,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeys,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 1000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Above1000Availability,
    AVG(CASE WHEN NATION.N_NAME LIKE 'S%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS StartsWithS,
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 5000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AcctBalOver5k,
    AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_NAME LIKE 'A%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SupplierNameStartsWithA
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistOptOrderKeys,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS MaxReceiptDate,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) AS MinShipDate
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE' ELSE 'Other' END AS MarketSegment,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY DESC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY)

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PS_AVAILQTY ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_AvailQTY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Comments_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PS_AVAILQTY ELSE 0 END) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    SUM(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalSales,
    AVG(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SupplierCount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND SUM(O.O_TOTALPRICE) > 100000

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN ('France', 'Germany', 'UK') -- filtering by specific nations for interest
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 -- only showing parts with average supply cost above 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthORDERS,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthSUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthLINEITEM,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthREGION,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG( LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS AvgShipPriority,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    ORDERS ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddrLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) IS NOT NULL THEN AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))
        ELSE 0
    END DESC,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) IS NOT NULL THEN AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))
        ELSE 0
    END DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLen,
    P_MFGR AS Manufacturer,
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS NumUniquePartKeys,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P_MFGR, N_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    c.C_ACCTBAL As CustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLength_C_ADDRESS,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgLength_C_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgLength_S_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLength_S_ADDRESS,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLength_L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_L_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLength_L_LINESTATUS,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrders
FROM
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) > 100 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) > 10

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COALESCE(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 0) AS SupplyCost,
    COALESCE(ps.PS_AVAILQTY, 0) AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST IS NOT NULL OR ps.PS_AVAILQTY IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, ps.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_SUPPKEY) > 1
    AND SUM(COALESCE(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 0)) > 1000
    AND SUM(COALESCE(ps.PS_AVAILQTY, 0)) > 500
ORDER BY
    SUM(COALESCE(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 0)) DESC,
    p.P_NAME

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    li.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE '%R%' -- Exclude returns
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, li.L_QUANTITY, li.L_DISCOUNT, r.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100 -- Filter nations with total quantity above 100
ORDER BY
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_Name,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_MTKSegment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Total_Tax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS Avg_Line_Number,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMKTSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLineItemNumber,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS TOTAL_PARTKEY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS SHIPMENT_DATE
FROM
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    NATION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE O_CLERK = 'CXTKT-21508')
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCount,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT 
  PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, 
  PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, 
  SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, 
  NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, 
  PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 
  PART.P_SIZE, 
  CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, 
  CASE 
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'LEATHER' THEN 'Leather' 
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'PLASTIC' THEN 'Plastic' 
    ELSE 'Other' 
  END AS PART_CONTAINER, 
  CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM 
  PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
  SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY 
INNER JOIN 
  NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY 
INNER JOIN 
  PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
  CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY 
ORDER BY 
  PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
  PART.P_SIZE DESC, 
  CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Paid'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Reversed'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ReturnStatus,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER = 1 THEN 'Last Order'
        ELSE 'Previous Order'
    END AS SupplyLinePosition
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMfrLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPartBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_BRAND AS P_Brand,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_Name
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_BRAND, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT c.C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER c WHERE c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AGRI-PRODUCTS')
ORDER BY
    n.N_NATIONKEY,
    c.C_NAME DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_PHONE,
    C.C_COMMENT,
    CASE
        WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'BUILDING'
        WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'CONSUMER_PACK' THEN 'CONSUMER_PACK'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_PHONE,
    S.S_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE')

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSupplierName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthSupplierPhone,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'AirShipments'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'REG' THEN 'RoadShipments'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN 'RailShipments'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'SEA' THEN 'SeaShipments'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ShipModeCategory
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_ORDERSTATUS FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL AS Customer_Account_Balance,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS Supplier_Account_Balance,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX AS LineItem_Tax,
    YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE) AS Order_Year,
    YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS Receipt_Year
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY -- Assuming O_CUSTKEY refers to C_CUSTKEY in CUSTOMER
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LEN,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_PART_RETPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_PART_BRAND_LEN,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LEN,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LEN,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AVG_LINEITEM_LINENUMBER,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS DISTINCT_LINEITEM_PARTKEY_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_COMMENT_LEN
FROM 
    PART
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY),
    MAX(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_TYPE, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumReturns,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT 
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS DistinctCommentsCount
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_MFGR

SELECT
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSuppCommentLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalFilledOrders,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE NULL END) AS AvgFilledOrderQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'S' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalShippedOrders,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'S' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE NULL END) AS AvgShippedOrderQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Fulfilled'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 'Open'
        ELSE 'Cancelled'
    END AS LineStatusCategory,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM LINEITEM) THEN 'AboveAverage'
        ELSE 'BelowAverage'
    END AS PriceCategory
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS IN ('F', 'O')
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST / (PART.P_RETAILPRICE * PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY * PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCountInCustomer,
    COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY) As NationCount
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MARKET_SEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY, C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeys,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS A_RETURNFLAG_Rate,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS R_RETURNFLAG_Rate
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    COUNT(p.p_partkey) AS PartCount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
WHERE
    p.p_partkey IN (
        SELECT
            p2.p_partkey
        FROM
            PART p2
        JOIN
            CUSTOMER c2 ON p2.p_partkey = c2.c_custkey
        GROUP BY
            p2.p_partkey
        HAVING
            COUNT(c2.c_custkey) > 1
    )
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, c.c_name, p.p_name, s.s_name

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_Size,
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 10 THEN 'Low Stock'
        ELSE 'Adequate Stock'
    END AS StockCategory
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_SIZE,
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 10 THEN 'Low Stock'
        ELSE 'Adequate Stock'
    END

SELECT PART.P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 1
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCstmrMKTSegmentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATION_KEY,
    S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATION_KEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 100 AND AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) > 50 AND AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) > 30
    AND AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 20 AND AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) > 40
    AND AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) > 25

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLengthCName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthCComment,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthSCComment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS NonNegativeAcctBalSuppKeys,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL < 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS NegativeAcctBalSuppKeys,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION) -- Assuming NATION table exists with N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
  NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
  AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
  AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY) AS AvgCustomerKeys,
  AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneNumberLength,
  AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
  AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantityPerLineItem,
  AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
  COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeys
FROM
  NATION
  INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
  INNER JOIN ORDERS ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
  NATION.N_NAME,
  ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUM(PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CS.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP PSS
JOIN
    PART P ON PSS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CS ON P.P_PARTKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON CS.C_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CS.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT CS.C_CUSTKEY) > 10

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AverageRefundRate
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000000
    AND AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0.05

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS E_NATION_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_PART_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PART_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_PART_Type_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Custo_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Custo_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_R_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_R_Comment_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Distinct_CustKey_Count,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_RetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS Distinct_PartKey_Count
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), 
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength, 
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength, 
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength, 
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength, 
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength, 
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY 
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY 
ORDER BY 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, 
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_TypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_BrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)) AS Avg_RetailPriceLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_AccountBalances
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQty
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    R.R_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgN_CommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgP_ContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_PHONE)) AS AvgS_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgS_AddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgR_CommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    R.R_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'Automobile'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'Automobile'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MARKET_SEGMENT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS NUM_PARTS_SUPPLIED,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST * PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_VALUE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAIQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AVG_PART_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SUPPLIER_NATIONKEY,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TOTAL_PART_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AVG_PART_SIZE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AVG_PART_TYPE_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
CASE
  WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'New'
  WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Refund'
  ELSE 'Other'
END as RETURN_STATUS
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'ANTARCTICA')

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LI.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LI.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnedQuantity
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'Status-YouTube')
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, C.C_ACCTBAL, S.S_ACCTBAL, N.N_REGIONKEY, R.R_NAME, R.R_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT MIN(C_NATIONKEY) FROM CUSTOMER GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY)
AND N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY NOT IN (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 100000)))
ORDER BY N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_OverAllQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_CustomerMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NationKey,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NationKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NationKey
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS NUM_ORDERS,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TOTAL_ORDER_PRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AVG_ORDER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionLength
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
   NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
   PART.P_NAME,
   COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS LINEITEM_COUNT,
   AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
   AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
   COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
   AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
   NATION.N_COMMENT,
   AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
   AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
   AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
   AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM
   NATION,
   PART,
   ORDERS,
   CUSTOMER,
   SUPPLIER,
   LINEITEM
WHERE
   SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
   AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
   AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
   AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
   AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
   NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
   PART.P_NAME,
   NATION.N_COMMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) > 20
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGRLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 5 AND AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 50 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 30 AND SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    Su.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Su.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    Su.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierBalance,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER Su ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON Su.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 100
AND C.C_ACCTBAL > 5000
AND N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Region#3'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_CLERK,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) AS total_order_value,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_PARTKEY) AS num_parts,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS avg_discount,
    MIN(li.L_SHIPDATE) AS earliest_ship_date,
    MAX(li.L_SHIPDATE) AS latest_ship_date
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_CLERK,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_COMMITDATE
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantitySold,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength
FROM
    NATION
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON CUST.C_CUSTKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    (PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 500)
    AND (PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS AvgMachineryCustomers,
    AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 5000 THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS AvgHighAccountSuppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS FractionStatusF,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    n.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    r.R_NAME AS SupplierRegion,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    cu.C_NAME AS CustomerBrand,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_CONTAINER,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER cu ON p.P_PARTKEY = cu.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    O.O_ORDERDATE
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON LI.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    MAX(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    MIN(L.L_QUANTITY) AS MinQuantity,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName
FROM
    PART P
    JOIN LINEITEM L ON P.P_PARTKEY = L.L_PARTKEY
    JOIN ORDERS O ON L.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE, C.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgN_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgC_CommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgS_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgL_ShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgR_CommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgL_Discount,
    SUM(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN L_ORDERKEY ELSE NULL END) AS FaultyCount,
    SUM(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'S' THEN L_ORDERKEY ELSE NULL END) AS SuspendedCount,
