    SUM(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'L' THEN L_ORDERKEY ELSE NULL END) AS PendingCount
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IS NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY END) as AIR_SHIPMENTS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY END) as SHIP_SHIPMENTS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY END) as TRUCK_SHIPMENTS
FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
  AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOClarkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSAccountBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLineStatusLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Oprio1UrgentCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2-HIGH' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Oprio2HighCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '3-NORMAL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Oprio3NormalCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '4-LOW' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Oprio4LowCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRNameLength
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(NATION.N_REGIONKEY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) > 1
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'S%')
    AND C.C_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'C%')

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    MIN(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT L_SHIPMODE, AVG(L_DISCOUNT), AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE
HAVING AVG(L_DISCOUNT) > 5
AND AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100
AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) > 10
AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 15
AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) > 10
AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 20
AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 15
AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS CountDistinctParts
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) > 5
    AND LENGTH(PART.P_NAME) > 8
    AND LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE) > 3
    AND LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) > 4
    AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 10000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTAX,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    MAX(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS MaxAccountBalance,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE,
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > PART.P_RETAILPRICE THEN 'Overpriced supplier'
        ELSE 'Supplier within expected price range'
    END AS PriceComparison
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0.1 THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT END) AS HIGH_DISCOUNT_LINEITEMS_PRICE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S.S_COMMENT,
    P.P_CONTAINER,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE),
    PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgOrderCommentLen,
       AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY) AS AvgCustKey,
       AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddrLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLen,
       SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalLineItemExtendedPrice,
       SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS TotalLineItemPartKey,
       SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS TotalLineItemLineNumber,
       AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
       LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_CommitDate
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    CASE
        WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Air'
        WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Sea'
        ELSE 'Road'
    END AS SHIPPING_MODE
FROM 
    PART
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE
ORDER BY 
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'LARGE POLISHED COPPER' THEN 'Large Polished Copper'
        WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#35' THEN 'Brand#35'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS Category
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    Sa.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER Sa ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = Sa.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON Sa.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, Sa.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, Sa.S_NAME, PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY),
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
HAVING
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) > 10000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 12
ORDER BY
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) DESC,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND   PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND   N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT 
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnedItems,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength
FROM 
    NATION
INNER JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    CASE 
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
        ELSE 'Not Returned'
    END

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS ORDERS_COUNT,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AVG_ORDER_PRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_LINE_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_LINE_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_LINE_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100
    AND AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) = 1

SELECT 
    REGION.R_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    NATION 
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    CS.C_NATIONKEY,
    CS.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CS ON P.P_PARTKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CS.C_NATIONKEY,
    CS.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    P.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (
        SELECT
            AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST)
        FROM
            PARTSUPP
        WHERE
            PS_PARTKEY IN (
                SELECT
                    P_PARTKEY
                FROM
                    PART
                WHERE
                    P_TYPE = 'specific_part_type' -- specify the type here, e.g., 'MOTOR'
            )
    )
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_PartMFGRLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_BrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustomerAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_CustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), MIN(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_RETURNED_QUANTITY,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_SOLD_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TOTAL_ORDER_KEYS
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS C_CUSTKEY_COUNT,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS SUM_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_LINEITEM_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgLengthPartName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLengthCustomerName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSupplierName,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)) AS AvgLengthLineItemType,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLengthShipInstruct,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOrders,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NationKey
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_SIZE, PRODUCTS.P_RETAILPRICE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN (SELECT P_PARTKEY, MAX(P_RETAILPRICE) AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PART GROUP BY P_PARTKEY) AS PRODUCTS ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PRODUCTS.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE '%%A%' OR N_NAME LIKE '%%E%')

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_MFGR, PART.P_SIZE, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL BRUSHED BRASS' THEN 'SMALL BRUSHED BRASS' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerKeysCount,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailabilityQuantity,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailabilityQuantity
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG( Length(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT) ) AS AvgInstructionLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    PART
    JOIN LINEITEM ON PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
    JOIN ORDERS ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistDistinctSuppKeyCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMfgrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_SizeGrouped
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Part,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_TypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Supplier,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMKTSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctParts
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT 
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_COST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_MFGR_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_BRAND_LEN,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUST_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_MKTSEGMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS TotalParts,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgOrderCommentLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderTotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_CommitDate
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_PartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
    AND NATION.N_COMMENT NOT LIKE '%complaint%'
    AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    NATION.N_COMMENT ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMarketSegLength,
    PART.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PART.P_PARTKEY END) AS PartsWithAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY = 0 THEN PART.P_PARTKEY END) AS PartsWithNoAvailQty,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplyCostForPartsWAvail,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY = 0 THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplyCostForPartsWNoAvail
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_BRAND, PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgManLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY THEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderKeys
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND   
   PART.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR IN ('Manufacturer1', 'Manufacturer2'))
AND 
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING 
    COUNT(PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 1

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    P_NAME AS PartName,
    S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME,
    P_NAME,
    S_ACCTBAL,
    R_NAME,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    R_NAME,
    R_COMMENT
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT
HAVING
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'PROCESSED' THEN AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'RAW' THEN AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) * 1.1
        ELSE AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) * 0.9
    END AS AdjustedAvgSupplyCost
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE

SELECT 
    C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(CASE WHEN C_NATIONKEY = N_NATIONKEY THEN C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(CASE WHEN S_NATIONKEY = N_NATIONKEY THEN S_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY)
GROUP BY 
    C_NAME, N_NATIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) AS CountUniquePartTypes,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_BRAND, PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS avg_supply_cost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS avg_comment_len,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS avg_part_size,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS avg_part_type_len,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS avg_customer_addr_len,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS avg_supplier_name_len,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS distinct_partkey_count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_SUPPKEY) AS distinct_supplierkey_count
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, C_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) > 10 AND COUNT(DISTINCT S_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS O_ORDERPRIORITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AVG_PART_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LEN,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TOTAL_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AVG_PART_TYPE_LEN,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalSales,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 1000
    AND AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) > 50.00
    AND SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 500000.00
    AND AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 10000.00

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    SUM(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalSales,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerBalance,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS PartsAvailableCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY = 0 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS PartsOutOfStockCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AVG_LINEITEM_LINENUMBER,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS SHIPMODE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDERS
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY) AS TotalCustomerKeys,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderTotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalances,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrices
FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgLengthPContainer,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgLengthPBRAND,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthS_COMMENT,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLengthL_RETURNFLAG,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS TotalL_PARTKEY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgL_LINENUMBER,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthL_COMMENT
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) < 10

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PART.P_CONTAINER = 'SM CASE'
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS NumReturnedItems,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnedOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthNationComment,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthRegionComment
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) > 5

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance, COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalLineItems, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND   P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND   C.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderTotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantitySold,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS LineStatus,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY BETWEEN 1 AND 10 -- example filter for specific nations
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) * PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR) + LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    PART.P_TYPE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    o.o_orderstatus,
    SUM(CASE WHEN l.l_returnflag = 'I' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS InStockOrders,
    AVG(l.l_quantity) AS AverageQuantity,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS TotalRevenue,
    r.r_name AS Region
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
    JOIN ORDERS o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
    JOIN NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
    JOIN REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
    JOIN LINEITEM l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey
    JOIN SUPPLIER s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, o.o_orderstatus, r.r_name

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) > 10 AND SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100000
ORDER BY SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    COUNT(PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION S_NATIONKEY ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = S_NATIONKEY.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, S_NATIONKEY.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    COUNT(PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalPartRetailPrice,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P_SIZE, P_BRAND

SELECT P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, PS.PS_COMMENT, P.P_RETAILPRICE, P.P_SIZE, P.P_BRAND, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, C.C_PHONE, C.C_ACCTBAL, S.S_ACCTBAL, R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    o.O_COMMENT AS OrderComment,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS AS OrderStatus,
    o.O_ORDERKEY AS OrderKey,
    o.O_CUSTKEY AS CustomerKey,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE AS TotalPrice,
    o.O_CLERK AS AssignedClerk,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS OrderPriority,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS ShippingPriority,
    li.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMethod,
    li.L_TAX AS TaxAmount,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS ExtendedPrice,
    li.L_COMMITDATE AS CommitDate,
    li.L_ORDERKEY AS LineItemOrderKey,
    li.L_RETURNFLAG AS ReturnFlag,
    li.L_LINESTATUS AS LineStatus,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceivedDate,
    li.L_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    li.L_LINENUMBER As LineNumber,
    li.L_SHIPDATE As ShippingDate,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT As ShippingInstruction,
    li.L_SUPPKEY As SupplierKey,
    li.L_DISCOUNT As Discount,
    li.L_COMMENT As LineComment,
    li.L_QUANTITY As Quantity
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' AND li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, li.L_QUANTITY DESC, o.O_TOTALPRICE ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY  -- assuming S_NATIONKEY refers to NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    n.n_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS distinct_customers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS distinct_suppliers,
    AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_accsbal,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS total_acctbal
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) > 100 AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) > 50 AND AVG(c.c_acctbal) > 1000

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            PS2.PS_PARTKEY
        FROM
            PARTSUPP PS2
        JOIN
            PART P2 ON PS2.PS_PARTKEY = P2.P_PARTKEY
        WHERE
            PS2.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
            AND PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (
                SELECT AVG(PS3.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
                FROM
                    PARTSUPP PS3
                    JOIN PART P3 ON PS3.PS_PARTKEY = P3.P_PARTKEY
                WHERE
                    P3.P_NAME LIKE 'A%'
            )
        ORDER BY
            PS2.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
            PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
        
    )
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE NATION.N_NAME = 'AFRICA') -- Assuming the continent is specified by N_NAME, replace 'AFRICA' with desired value
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 50000 -- Adjust this condition as needed
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLShipmodeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRCommentLength,
    SUM(CASE
        WHEN L_QUANTITY > 100 THEN L_QUANTITY
        ELSE 0
    END) AS TotalQuantityOver100,
    SUM(CASE
        WHEN L_QUANTITY <= 100 THEN L_QUANTITY
        ELSE 0
    END) AS TotalQuantityUpTo100
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    PART.P_TYPE IS NOT NULL AND
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    NS.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailabilityQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NS ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON NS.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NS.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    NS.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_SUPPKEY, P_NAME, C_ADDRESS, C_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > ( SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP )
AND P_RETAILPRICE > ( SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART )
AND C_ACCTBAL > ( SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER )

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC, REGION.R_NAME ASC, MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) DESC, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)) AS AvgOrderPriorityLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS SumCAccountBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS SumLQuantity,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_OrderStatus,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) >= 1000 THEN 'High'
        WHEN AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) < 1000 AND AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) >= 500 THEN 'Medium'
        ELSE 'Low'
    END AS PriceRange
FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
  AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS, ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN L_ORDERKEY END) AS A_RETURNED_ORDERS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L_ORDERKEY END) AS R_RETURNED_ORDERS,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_REGIONKEY)) AS R_REGIONKEY_LEN,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
having COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOrderClerkLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS TotalOrderShipPriority,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS TotalLineItemLineNumber,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLineItemQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS NumDistinctSuppliers,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgLineItemReturnRate
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_BRAND

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS TotalPartKeys,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength
FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
