    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) > 10000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 5
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 15
    AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) > 0.05
    AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50
    AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 10
    AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 20

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVE_N_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVE_C_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVE_C_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVE_S_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVE_C_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVE_C_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVE_S_PHONE_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TOTAL_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVE_R_NAME_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDERS,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVE_L_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AVG_LINEITEM_TAX,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_NAME), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME As Nation_Name,
    R.R_NAME As Region_Name,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As Supply_Cost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_COMMENT LIKE '%Hardware%')

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_Name)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) * 100.0 / COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS ReturnPercentage
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 100

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'BUILDING'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME DESC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgOrderCommentLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderTotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY)) AS AvgOrderCustomerKeyLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOrderClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS SumLineItemExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS SumLineItemLinenumber,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_ShipMode,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY AS R_RegionKey
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE, R_RegionKey

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPPartContainerLength, AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPPartSize, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPPartNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPBrandLength, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCCommentLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSAddressLength, SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost, SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST < (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART WHERE P_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY) THEN 'Cost-Effective'
        ELSE 'Not Cost-Effective'
    END AS AvailabilityCostEffectiveness,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    r.R_NAME = 'EUROPE' -- or any other specific region name
GROUP BY 
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING 
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000.00 -- or any other specific supply cost threshold
ORDER BY 
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME As Region,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    C.C_NAME As Customer_Name,
    C.C_PHONE,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    MIN(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP_NAME.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUST_NAME.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N_NAME.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP_NAME ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP_NAME.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_NAME ON SUP_NAME.S_NATIONKEY = N_NAME.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST_NAME ON SUP_NAME.S_SUPPKEY = CUST_NAME.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N_NAME.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_CUSTKEY = (SELECT MIN(C_CUSTKEY) FROM CUSTOMER))))
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierBalance,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE = 1 THEN 'Small'
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE = 2 THEN 'Medium'
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE = 3 THEN 'Large'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS SizeCategory
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_PS,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_N,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_N,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGRLength_P,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_P,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength_R,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RetailPrice,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    r.R_NAME AS region_name,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS total_customer_account_balance,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS total_supplier_account_balance,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS avg_line_item_extended_price,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_PARTKEY) AS distinct_parts_count,
    MAX(li.L_SHIPDATE) AS latest_shipment_date
FROM
    REGION r
JOIN
    NATION n ON r.R_REGIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    r.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_PART_Container_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_PART_MFGR_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Total_Tax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Max_RetailPrice,
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Min_RetailPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierAccountBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100
    AND MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalRevenue,
    AVG(li.l_discount) AS AverageDiscount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_orderkey) AS OrdersCount
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name, c.c_name, s.s_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) > 100000

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_CONTAINER, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY >= 0 AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_CONTAINER, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 1
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) ASC, ABS(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS Order_Count,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS Average_Order_Price,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Order_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) As Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_LineItem_Tax,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Returned_Orders_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)) AS Avg_ReceiptDate_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) As Avg_Region_Name_Length
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAcctBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierAcctBal,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSuppAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    PS_PARTKEY AS PartKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_BRAND_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH_SUPPLIER,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS DISTINCT_SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_INSTRUCTION_LENGTH,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMfgrLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT) AS DistinctPartCommentCount,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY N_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    S.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER C)
AND 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P2.P_PARTKEY 
                   FROM PART P2 
                   JOIN PARTSUPP PS2 ON P2.P_PARTKEY = PS2.PS_PARTKEY 
                   GROUP BY P2.P_PARTKEY 
                   HAVING SUM(PS2.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000)
ORDER BY 
    S.S_ACCTBAL DESC, 
    P.P_NAME ASC, 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME LIKE '%%N%%' -- Replace 'N' with a specific required nation name in upper or lower case
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPartRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgOrderCommentLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS SumLineItemTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_COMMITDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipmodeLength,
    MIN(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MinExtendedPrice,
    MAX(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY IS NOT NULL AND
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY IS NOT NULL AND
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME NOT IN ('Antigua And Barbuda', 'Dominica', 'Dominican Republic')
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100 AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgOrderCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineitemLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS AvgOrderShipPriority,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM NATION
JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY -- assuming O_CUSTKEY references NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAILABILITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT N_NATIONKEY) AS NUM_NATIONS,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    P_BRAND AS PART_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_BRAND

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthRegion
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DEL_ORDERS_COUNT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AVG_TOTALPRICE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS RETURNS_COUNT,
    CASE
        WHEN SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0 THEN SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100
        ELSE 0
    END AS RETURNS_RATE
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS IN ('D', 'F') -- 'D' for Delivered, 'F' for Fulfilled
    AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG NOT IN ('A', ' ') -- exclude Aspected and blank rows, focusing on Returns
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    MAX(CASE WHEN l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY THEN l.L_RECEIPTDATE END) AS LATEST_SUPPLIER_RECEIPT_DATE,
    MIN(CASE WHEN l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY THEN l.L_SHIPDATE END) AS EARLIEST_SUPPLIER_SHIPMENT_DATE
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM l ON p.P_PARTKEY = l.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    p.P_PARTKEY, p.P_NAME, c.C_CUSTKEY, c.C_NAME
HAVING 
    MAX(CASE WHEN l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY THEN l_receiptdate END) IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)) AS AVG_ACCTBAL_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILQTY,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_NAME
ORDER BY 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME, PART.P_NAME AS P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME AS R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY N_NAME, P_NAME, C_NAME, R_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS QUANTITY_RETURNED,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS QUANTITY_REDealD,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AVERAGE_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_SUPPKEY,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AVERAGE_PART_SIZE,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PS_PARTKEY, PS_SUPPKEY, P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRNameLength,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_ShipMode,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MarketSegment
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE, C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH_C,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS CUST_ACCTBAL_SUM,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_S,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH_S,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH_S,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AVG_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS L_QUANTITY_SUM
FROM
    CUSTOMER
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderTotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_ShipMode,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalLineItemDiscount
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE, L_LINESTATUS, L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Comments_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 100
    AND AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) > 15
    AND AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) > 20
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    MAX(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    MAX(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    MAX(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    MAX(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    MAX(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME))
FROM
    NATION
        JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
        JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY -- Assuming C_CUSTKEY is a key in both CUSTOMER and SUPPLIER tables
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100000 AND AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_N_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_C_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_S_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_L_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_UNIQUE_SUPPLIERS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER) + LENGTH(P_NAME) + LENGTH(P_BRAND) + LENGTH(C_NAME) + LENGTH(C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(S_NAME) + LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_TOTAL_CHARACTERS,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_RETAILPRICE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS DISTINCT_CUSTOMERS,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE
FROM
    PART
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) > 5
    AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    PART
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgNamePhoneLen,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSuppPhoneLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSuppCommentLen
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthC_COMMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgLengthC_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthC_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthC_ADDRESS,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalS_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthS_COMMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthS_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthS_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthS_ADDRESS,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS AvgL_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLengthL_LINESTATUS,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLengthL_RETURNFLAG,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLengthL_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TotalL_QUANTITY
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON C_CUSTKEY = S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON S_SUPPKEY = L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL),
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE L_SHIPMODE IN ('AIR', 'SHIP') -- Only consider shipments via air or sea
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    MIN(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MinSupplyCost,
    MAX(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) > 10
    AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
    AND MIN(PS_SUPPLYCOST) < 100
    AND MAX(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 500
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_MFGR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    L_DISCOUNT,
    L_COMMITDATE
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, L_DISCOUNT, L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    n.n_name,
    r.r_name,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) AS supplier_count
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON s.s_suppkey = li.l_suppkey
WHERE
    r.r_regionkey IN (SELECT r_regionkey FROM REGION WHERE r_name = 'ASIA')
GROUP BY
    n.n_name,
    r.r_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSAddressLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctLOrderKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS SumLExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS SumLDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_MktSegment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Supplier_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME IS NOT NULL
AND PART.P_NAME IS NOT NULL
AND PART.P_TYPE IS NOT NULL
AND CAST(CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS VARCHAR(100)) IS NOT NULL
AND SUPPLIER.S_NAME IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS OrderStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > PART.P_SIZE
AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST < (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    PART.P_BRAND,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NationKey
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_MFGR, C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    R.R_REGIONKEY,
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_CONTAINER,
    P.P_MFGR,
    P.P_COMMENT,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_COMMITDATE, L.L_ORDERKEY, L.L_RETURNFLAG, L.L_LINESTATUS, L.L_RECEIPTDATE, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPDATE, L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, L.L_SUPPKEY, L.L_DISCOUNT, L.L_COMMENT, L.L_QUANTITY
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' AND L.L_SHIPMODE IS NOT NULL AND O.O_CUSTKEY > 1000
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_SHIPDATE ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE),
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE),
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    NATION
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) DESC, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Accounts,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Supplier_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_Region_Name_Length
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    Li.L_LINESTATUS,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'P') -- 'A' for Ahead, 'P' for Partial
    AND Li.L_SHIPMODE LIKE 'RAV%' -- Assuming 'RAV%' ships via Rail Air Vehicle mode
    AND Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) * 1.1 FROM LINEITEM) -- Parts priced 10% above average extended price
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY -- Ensuring that supplier and nation are of the same nation
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY) AS NumNations,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupp,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT PART.P_BRAND, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM PART
INNER JOIN PARTSUPP ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_BRAND
HAVING AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) < (SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG END) AS RETURNED_COUNT, AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUM(OI.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TOTAL_ORDER_REVENUE,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_LINE_ITEM_PRICE
FROM
    CUSTOMER C JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN ORDERS OI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = OI.O_CUSTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM LI ON OI.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(OI.O_TOTALPRICE) > 10000
    AND AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT p.P_PARTKEY FROM PART p JOIN PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY WHERE ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0)

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    MAX(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE END) AS MaxExtendedPriceR,
    MAX(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE END) AS MaxExtendedPriceN,
    CASE
        WHEN MAX(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE END) > MAX(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE END) THEN 'Return'
        ELSE 'No Return'
    END AS ReturnFlagComparison
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantityShipped,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrdersShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOrderClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_CLERK

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) + LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) + LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtPrice,
    AVG(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE NULL END) AS AvgReturnQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRjNameLength,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomersSupplying,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_SIZE, P.P_RETAILPRICE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) > 1
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY, SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)),
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS FULL_FULFILLED_QUANTITY,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS ABANDONED_QUANTITY,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMKTSegmentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgLineItemTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceivedDate,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 100 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 8 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 500.00 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 15 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000.00

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineITEM_LineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineITEM_ShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineITEM_ReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineITEM_ShipInstructLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    p.p_name AS Part,
    CAST(SUM(lij.l_quantity) AS DECIMAL) / SUM(DISTINCT CASE WHEN lij.l_returnflag = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnedQuantity,
    CAST(SUM(lij.l_extendedprice * lij.l_discount) AS DECIMAL) / SUM(DISTINCT CAST(lij.l_extendedprice AS DECIMAL)) AS AvgDiscountRate
FROM
    LINEITEM lij
JOIN
    PART p ON lij.l_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON lij.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.p_partkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name
HAVING
    SUM(DISTINCT CASE WHEN lij.l_returnflag = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    SUP.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    NAT.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    REG.R_NAME As Region_Name,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As Supply_Cost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As Available_Quantity,
    CUST.C_NAME As Customer_Name,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL As Customer_Account_Balance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NAT ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = NAT.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION REG ON NAT.N_REGIONKEY = REG.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLYER_NATION_NAME,
    CUS.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER CUS ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = CUS.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = 3) -- assuming region 3 for a specific case
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_NAME ASC, SUP.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_PARTKEY) AS Total_Parts,
    AVG(LENGTH(n.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(n.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NNameLength,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(p.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_PContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(p.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(p.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_PTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(p.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_PBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(c.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(s.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SCommentLength,
    c.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = ps.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON c.C_CUSTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    n.N_REGIONKEY AS NATION_REGIONKEY,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
    AND n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'PACIFIC'))
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLineNumber,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
        INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
        INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)) AS AvgOrderPriorityLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG
FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION
