WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME = 'some_specific_nation_name' -- replace with actual nation name
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000 -- replace with desired threshold
ORDER BY
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'AUTOMOBILE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegmentType,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 10 AND PART.P_SIZE <= 20 THEN 'SizeMedium'
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 20 THEN 'SizeLarge'
        ELSE 'OtherSize'
    END AS SizeCategory,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPMFGRLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRCommentLength,
    PART.P_BRAND AS P_Brand,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_BRAND, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_MktSegment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_Extended_Price,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_Region_Name_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Distinct_Customer_Keys,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Nation_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Product_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_PARTKEY,
    li.L_LINENUMBER,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM LINEITEM)
AND
    c.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND
    s.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    s.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    li.L_SHIPDATE ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_MFGR_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_BRAND_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_C_NAME_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_S_COMMENT_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_S_NAME_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_L_SHIPMODE_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_L_SHIPINSTRUCT_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_ReturnFlag_R,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_ReturnFlag_I,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
CASE
    WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL PLATED BRASS' THEN 'SMALL PLATED BRASS'
    ELSE 'Other'
END AS PartType,
S_PHONE,
S_COMMENT AS SupplierComment
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL PLATED BRASS' OR PART.P_TYPE IS NULL

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOOrdersClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRRegionNameLength,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliersCount
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returnable'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Non-returnable'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ReturnFlagCategory
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < PART.P_SIZE
AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > PART.P_RETAILPRICE
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 1
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGRLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER On PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER On SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM On LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT) AS DistinctPartComments,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalances,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineitemDiscount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN NULL END) AS ReturnedExtPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN NULL END) AS AcceptedExtPrice
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY =CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    sup.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER sup ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = sup.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON sup.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT 
            p.P_PARTKEY
        FROM 
            PART p
        JOIN 
            PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
        WHERE 
            ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
        GROUP BY 
            p.P_PARTKEY
        HAVING 
            SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    )
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT SUM(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_LINEITEM_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION N
INNER JOIN REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM L ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    R_NAME, L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS A_RETURN_FLAGS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AIR_SHIP_MODES,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT))
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeysCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShipModeLength,
    PART.P_CONTAINER AS ContainerType
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT T1.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
    AVG(T1.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Account_Balance,
    AVG(T2.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    SUM(T3.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount,
    MONTH(T3.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS Receipt_Month,
    T3.L_SHIPMODE,
    T1.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    T2.S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    CUSTOMER T1,
    SUPPLIER T2,
    LINEITEM T3
WHERE
    T1.C_CUSTKEY = T2.S_SUPPKEY AND
    T2.S_SUPPKEY = T3.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    T1.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    MONTH(T3.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    T3.L_SHIPMODE,
    T2.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT T1.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND
    AVG(T1.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND
    AVG(T2.S_ACCTBAL) > 500

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthSupplier,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBalCustomer,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBalSupplier,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_SIZE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_Brand_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length_Cust,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatus_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Num_Orders,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
       AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
       AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    P_MFGR AS P_MFGR_Grouped
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Delivered' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DELIVERY_COUNT,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TOTAL_PRICE,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERGE_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVERAGE_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS ORDER_PRIORITY
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    CASE
        WHEN PS.PS_AVAILQTY < P.P_SIZE THEN 'Low Stock'
        ELSE 'Sufficient Stock'
    END AS StockStatus
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY)

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Re-shipped'
        ELSE ' Not Returned'
    END AS RETURN_STATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'EIFFoIL Heavy' THEN 'Special Container'
        ELSE 'Standard Container'
    END AS CONTAINER_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'R')
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END ASC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER GROUP BY C_CUSTKEY HAVING COUNT(C_CUSTKEY) > 1)

SELECT
  AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
  AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
  AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
  AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
  PART.P_CONTAINER AS PartContainer,
  SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
  COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliersCount
FROM
  NATION
JOIN
  CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
  PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
  SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
  PART.P_CONTAINER,
  PART.P_MFGR

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(NATION.N_NATIONKEY), -- Assuming N_NATIONKEY is an integer, averaging might not make sense, consider LENGTH(N_NAME) or COUNT(NATION.N_NATIONKEY) instead
    MAX(PART.P_SIZE),
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    MAX(REGION.R_REGIONKEY)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY -- Assuming PART_KEY relates to NATION through some implicit connection, adjust as necessary
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 -- Example condition, adjust as necessary
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, REGION.R_COMMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCust,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthSupp,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnableOrders,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS LatestReceiptDate,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) AS EarliestShipDate
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddrLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    L_LINESTATUS,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    CASE
        WHEN L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 'Yes'
        ELSE 'No'
    END AS DiscountApplied,
    L_COMMITDATE
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE, L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Total_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NS.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    NS.N_REGIONKEY,
    NS.N_COMMENT,
    MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    MIN(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MinSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CS.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NS ON S.S_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CS ON P.P_PARTKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NS.N_NAME, NS.N_REGIONKEY, NS.N_COMMENT

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_PS_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Length_N_COMMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Length_P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Sum_C_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Length_S_PHONE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT, N_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    O.O_ORDERKEY,
    O.O_ORDERDATE,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'BRAZIL%')
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE >= DATE('1995-01-01')
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE < DATE('1996-01-01')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PSUP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RETAIL_PRICE,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PSUP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PSUP.PS_COMMENT AS PARTSUPP_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PSUP
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PSUP.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION AS R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS SUP ON PSUP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PSUP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND
    PSUP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > P.P_RETAILPRICE AND
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe'))
ORDER BY
    PSUP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    C.C_PHONE AS CUSTOMER_PHONE,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS ORDER_DATE,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE AS ORDER_TOTAL_PRICE,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS AS ORDER_STATUS,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_PHONE AS SUPPLIER_PHONE,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS LINE_ITEM_PRICE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY AS LINE_ITEM_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE AS SHIPPING_MODE,
    Li.L_TAX AS TAX_AMT,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE AS SHIPMENT_DATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    Li.L_RETURNFLAG IS NULL
AND
    Li.L_SHIPDATE IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT DESC,
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) As AvgSuppAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) As TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) As AvgDiscount,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_CommitDate
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    p.p_name,
    SUM(ps.ps_supplycost),
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost),
    MIN(ps.ps_supplycost),
    MAX(ps.ps_supplycost),
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.ps_suppkey),
    n.n_name AS supplier_nation,
    r.r_name AS region_name
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY
    p.p_name,
    n.n_name,
    r.r_name
ORDER BY
    SUM(ps.ps_supplycost) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS NumDistinctComments,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT N.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION N JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'INFEASIBLE')

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailabilityQuantity,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT 
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPartBrandLen,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCmktSegmentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLen,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDiscountReturning,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDiscountReturned,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLineStatusLen,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE
FROM 
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY 
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY 
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY 
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipmodeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    L_SHIPMODE AS ShipMode,
    O_ORDERPRIORITY AS OrderPriority,
    AVG(O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgTotalPrice
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'P') -- include only 'A' (all items shipped) and 'P' (partially shipped)
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERPRIORITY, L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthAddress,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS CountDistinctPartKeys,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLengthReturnFlag,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLengthLineStatus,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS MaxReceiveDate,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS MinReceiveDate
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUST_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_CUST_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUST_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 15
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 1
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASAvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(CASE WHEN PART.P_NAME LIKE 'P%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumPartsStartingWithP,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBal,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    SUM(CASE WHEN PART.P_NAME LIKE 'P%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P1 ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P1.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P1.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    s.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    s.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    s.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    SUPPLIER s
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_REGIONKEY IN (
        SELECT r.R_REGIONKEY
        FROM REGION r
        ORDER BY r.R_REGIONKEY DESC
    )
AND n.N_NATIONKEY IN (
        SELECT MIN(n2.N_NATIONKEY)
        FROM NATION n2
        JOIN SUPPLIER s2 ON n2.N_NATIONKEY = s2.S_NATIONKEY
        GROUP BY n2.N_NATIONKEY
        HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT s2.S_SUPPKEY) > 1
        ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT s2.S_SUPPKEY) DESC
    )
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME

SELECT PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_CONTAINER, P.P_SIZE, P.P_RETAILPRICE, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, C.C_ACCTBAL, S.S_ACCTBAL, P.P_BRAND
FROM PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_COMMITDATE, L.L_RETURNFLAG, L.L_LINESTATUS, L.L_RECEIPTDATE, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPDATE, L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, L.L_DISCOUNT
FROM ORDERS O
INNER JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' AND L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_SHIPDATE DESC, O.O_TOTALPRICE DESC

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_ADDRESS_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Account_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Supplier_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS Market_Segment,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    CUSTOMER
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_SHIPINSTRUCT_LEN,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MAX_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_COMMENT_LEN,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS REC_DATE
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLY_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    p.P_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_PS_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_ShippingInstructionLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returnable'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Return Pending'
        ELSE 'Non-returnable'
    END AS ReturnFlagCategory
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnPercentage
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND
    PART.P_SIZE IN (SELECT P_SIZE FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'B')
AND
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
AND
    REGION.R_NAME = 'ASIA'

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS NationRegionKey,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 500
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) DESC,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) ASC,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) ASC

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY
                   FROM PARTSUPP PS
                   JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
                   WHERE PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 1000)
ORDER BY
    P.P_PARTKEY, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    MAX(LI.L_SHIPDATE) AS LatestShipDate
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
    AND MAX(LI.L_SHIPDATE) >= DATE('2023-01-01')
    AND AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50.00

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR AS Manufacturer,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AveragePartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumReturnedItems,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS NumPartKeys
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumOfCustomers,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY * LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscountValue,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS NumOfSuppliers
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY * LI.L_DISCOUNT) > 1000

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE
HAVING PART.P_TYPE LIKE 'START_%'
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
       MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Max_Supply_Cost,
       AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Available_Quantity,
       S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
       N.N_NAME As Nation_Name
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME = 'Nation_Name_You_Want' -- replace 'Nation_Name_You_Want' with actual nation name
GROUP BY P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME
ORDER BY MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))

SELECT 
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)),
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)),
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(L_LINENUMBER),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)),
    SUM(L_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L_ORDERKEY END) AS ReturnLineItemCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L_SUPPKEY END) AS ReturnSupplierCount
FROM 
    PART, 
    CUSTOMER, 
    SUPPLIER, 
    LINEITEM 
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY 
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY 
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    S_NATIONKEY, 
    P_CONTAINER

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_L_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_L_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_L_DISCOUNT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_SUPPLIERS
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT PART.P_MFGR, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE, COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartCount
FROM PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_MFGR, L_SHIPDATE, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT
ORDER BY PART.P_MFGR, L_SHIPDATE

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantitySold
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    NS.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION NS ON S.S_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON NS.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    NS.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME DESC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AGRICULTURAL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AgriculturalCustomerPercentage,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(CASE WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AGRICULTURAL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    c.C_NATIONKEY,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    MAX(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MAX_EXTENDED_PRICE
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    c.C_NATIONKEY,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    REGION.R_COMMENT,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'Automobile'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    REGION.R_COMMENT DESC,
    PART.P_TYPE ASC,
    PART.P_BRAND ASC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE LIKE 'Brass%') -- filter parts of a specific type (e.g., Brass)
    AND SUP.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'France') -- filter suppliers from a specific nation
    AND N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe') -- further filter regions by name
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgLineItemTax,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'Component' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 100  -- Example condition, feel free to adjust
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 5  -- Example condition, feel free to adjust
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailableQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_BrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Region,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_CustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_COMMENT, CASE WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'WRAP PACK' THEN 'WRAP PACK' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#1' THEN 'Manufacturer#1' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgTotalPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneNumberLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShippingMethodLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLineItemLineNumber,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartSoupPartition,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
  NATION.N_NAME,
  COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
  AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance,
  COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
  AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance,
  COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS Part_Count,
  SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
  AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_Region_Name_Length
FROM
  NATION
  JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
  JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
  JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
  NATION.N_NAME,
  REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Part_Comment_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_Part_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_LineItem_ShipMode_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatus_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_LineItem_ShipInstruct_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_Size,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_TAX AS L_TAX FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_TAX

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TOTAL_ORDER_REVENUE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AVG_QUANTITY_PER_ORDER,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_MFGR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AVG_CLERK_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) AS UniquePartTypes,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
