    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    CASE
        WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUSINESS' THEN 'Business Customers'
        ELSE 'Consumer Customers'
    END AS C_MKTSEGMENT_TYPE
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CASE
        WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUSINESS' THEN 'Business Customers'
        ELSE 'Consumer Customers'
    END
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartsCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discounted_Revenue,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantities_Shipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ReturnFlagCategory,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD BURNISHED TIN'
    AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'R')

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX)

SELECT O.O_ORDERKEY, C.C_NAME, S.S_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, LP.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LP.L_TAX, LP.L_SHIPMODE, YEAR(LP.L_RECEIPTDATE), LP.L_RETURNFLAG, CASE WHEN LP.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Return' ELSE 'No Return' END, case when C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AGRICULTURAL' THEN 'Agricultural' ELSE 'Others' END as C_MKT_SEGMENT
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LP ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LP.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LP.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' -- 'D' for Delivered orders
AND LP.L_RETURNFLAG IN (' ', 'R') -- ' ' for No return, 'R' for Refunded
ORDER BY LP.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE IN ('AIR', 'SEA')
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 10000
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS LineItem_OrderCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_AddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_LineItem_Quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatusLength
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE <= 10 THEN 'Small'
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE <= 100 THEN 'Medium'
        ELSE 'Large'
    END AS SizeCategory
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
       AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
       SUM(PART.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize,
       AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
       CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT P_MFGR, AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)), AVG(C_ACCTBAL), C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PART, CUSTOMER
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY P_MFGR, C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalPartRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    PART.P_CONTAINER AS ContainerType,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSupplierCount,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_MFGR

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 50 AND NATION.N_NAME NOT IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL < 1000))
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 25

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgOrderCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLineItemQuantity,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS AvgOrderShipPriority,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    MAX(PS_AVAILQTY) AS MaxAvailabilityQuantity,
    MIN(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MinSupplyCost,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    Count(Distinct PART.P_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPHONELength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, R_NAME, S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT
FROM
    NATION
        INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
        INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
        LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_Nation_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Market_Segment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 50
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 20
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 30
    AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 500000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Country,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS Unique_Customers,
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Balance,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Customer_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS Unique_Suppliers,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Balance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Supplier_Balance,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 500 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) > 50 AND
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) > 300

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (
    SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'Electronic')
) AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) > 10

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGRLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumUniqueCustKeys
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)),
    SUM(CASE WHEN PS_SUPPLYCOST > 1000 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ELSE 0 END) AS HighCostAvailQty,
    SUM(CASE WHEN PS_SUPPLYCOST <= 1000 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ELSE 0 END) AS LowCostAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLen,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMKTSegmentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLen
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'WELL' THEN PART.P_PARTKEY END) AS WELL_PART_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 THEN 'HighCost'
        ELSE 'LowCost'
    END AS COST_CATEGORY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 10 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) > 2 AND
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100 AND
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50000
ORDER BY
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILABILITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_COMMENT) AS UNIQUE_COMMENTS,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_MFGR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_BRAND_LENGTH,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    C.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCount
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    O.O_ORDERKEY AS OrderKey,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE AS OrderTotalPrice,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    L.L_SHIPMODE As ShippingMode,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As ExtendedPrice,
    L.L_DISCOUNT As Discount,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' AND L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY DESC,
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_S,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length_S,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_AcctBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipMode_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatus_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Ordered_Items_Count
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLen,
       AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLen
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM
    NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVG_N_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_RETATILPRICE,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS SUM_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 5000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS CountHighBalanceCustomers,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'segment4' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS CountSegment4Customers
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME, p.P_NAME, ps.PS_AVAILQTY, s.S_NAME, p.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_PHONE),
    P_SIZE
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    P_SIZE
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_US_Addr_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_US_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_SHIP_Instr_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlag_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AverageAvailability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY) AS UniquePartCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY) > 10

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) < AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))
            THEN 'CASE STUDY: Supplier names longer than nation names but customer names shorter'
        ELSE 'OTHER'
    END AS SpecialCase
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS Avg_PartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength,
    SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CustomerBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P_SIZE
HAVING
    P_SIZE > 10

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_TypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMgrrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS PartQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SuppNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Total_Tax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SuppKey
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS PART_Country,
    P_NAME AS PART_Name,
    P_TYPE AS PART_Type,
    P_BRAND AS PART_Brand,
    P_RETAILPRICE AS PART_RetailPrice,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_Name,
    C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_Name,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS CUSTOMER_MarketSegment,
    R_NAME AS REGION_Name
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_CLERK,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    li.L_LINESTATUS,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_PARTKEY,
    li.L_LINENUMBER,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    li.L_SUPPKEY,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_COMMENT AS LINE_COMMENT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    ORDERS o
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailabilityQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartSuppCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME) + LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT) + LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalQuantityReturned,
SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalQuantityStored,
AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L_TAX ELSE NULL END) AS AvgTaxForReturns,
AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN L_TAX ELSE NULL END) AS AvgTaxForStorage
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N_C.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_S.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N_S.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N_C.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND    N_C.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe'))
ORDER BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART P)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineitemShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineitemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineitemShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineitemCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax
FROM
    NATION
        JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
        JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_COMMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    SUM(p.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize,
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    (SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) / COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_PARTKEY)) AS AvgRetailPricePerPart
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 10000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS ReturnOrdersCount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL ANODIZED TIN' THEN 'SMALL ANODIZED TIN'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_TYPE_GROUP,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HARDWARE' THEN 'HARDWARE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS CUSTOMER_MKTSEGMENT_GROUP,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS UNIQUE_SUPPLIERS,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AVERAGE_RETURN_RATE,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS LATEST_RECEIPT_DATE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    n.n_name,
    r.r_name,
    o.o_orderstatus,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(li.l_orderkey) AS order_count,
    AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS avg_supplier_balance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.n_nationkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name, o.o_orderstatus
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) > 10000
    AND AVG(s.s_acctbal) > 5000
ORDER BY
    n.n_name ASC, o.o_orderstatus DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SuppNameLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnFlagA,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnFlagR,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)) AS AvgLineNumLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_TAX)) AS AvgTaxLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLen,
    C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND
    S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')
AND
    C.C_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT N.N_NATIONKEY) > 1 AND AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT),
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_PARTKEY),
    MAX(L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MIN(L_SHIPDATE)
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS
ORDER BY
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) DESC

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    REGION.R_COMMENT ASC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE NULLS FIRST

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE,
    CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 'Open' ELSE 'Closed' END AS LINE_STATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION))
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAILABILITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUST_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUP_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUP_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS PARTS_OVER_100_AVAIL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) > 0

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS
HAVING
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) > 10000 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 10

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT' AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'ACCESSORIES' THEN 'Component-Accessories'
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'FINISHED' AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOMES' THEN 'Finished-Homes'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS Category
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSASLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalInStockQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCDELength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLDiscount,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    Su.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER Su ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH'))
AND 
    Su.S_NAME IN (SELECT S_NAME FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'COLOMBIA'))
ORDER BY 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    li.L_PARTKEY,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM 
    ORDERS o
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    c.C_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_PARTKEY, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, li.L_DISCOUNT, li.L_SHIPDATE, li.L_RECEIPTDATE
HAVING 
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY 
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, c.C_NAME ASC, li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS NationAvgNameLen,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLen,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLen,
AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
MAX(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS MaxAccountBalance,
SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Length_P_Container,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS Avg_Length_P_Brand,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Length_S_Comment,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS Sum_S_AcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_Length_L_ReturnFlag,
    SUM(L_PARTKEY) AS Sum_L_PartKey,
    AVG(L_LINENUMBER) AS Avg_L_LineNumber,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Length_L_Comment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS Distinct_CustKey_Count
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'COLLECT COD' THEN 'COLLECT COD' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AVG_P_TYPE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_C_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_C_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_C_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_S_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_ORDERSTATUS FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_Size
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierTotalAccountBalance,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS AvgLineItemPartKey,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalLineItemDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_Quantity,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LineStatus
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_LineStatus, L_Quantity

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderTotalPrice,
AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccBal,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSCommentLength,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLength,
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLReturnFLAGLength,
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLinestatusLength,
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLength,
SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLQuantity,
ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS OrderPriority
FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Return'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R|I' THEN ' Restock | In Transit'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN 'In Transit'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ReturnFlagCategory,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Line Status: Fault'
        ELSE 'Line Status: Other'
    END AS LineStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE ASC,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R|I' THEN 2
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN 3
        ELSE 4
    END ASC,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END ASC,
    REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
   REGION.R_NAME AS R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    O_ORDERSTATUS,
    COUNT(O_ORDERKEY),
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END),
    AVG(LENGTH(O_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(O_SHIPPRIORITY)
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERSTATUS, O_SHIPPRIORITY
ORDER BY
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceiptDate
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddrLen,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    N_NAME AS CountryName,
    R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT, N_NAME, R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    NATION.N_NAME As NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME As RegionName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice,
    PART.P_SIZE As Size,
    PART.P_TYPE As Type,
    PART.P_BRAND As Brand,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME As CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL As CustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustName_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_SuppName_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CustPhone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SuppAddress_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CustComment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SuppComment_Length,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_SHIPINSTRUCT) AS UniqueShippingInstructions
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AVG_PART_SIZE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AVG_MFGR_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT C_NATIONKEY, AVG(C_ACCTBAL), AVG(S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT L_PARTKEY), COUNT(DISTINCT L_SUPPKEY)
FROM CUSTOMER C, SUPPLIER S, LINEITEM LI
WHERE C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY AND S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY AND C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY
HAVING SUM(LI.L_DISCOUNT) > 0

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    p.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME, p.P_NAME, ps.PS_AVAILQTY, s.S_NAME, p.P_SIZE, p.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000 -- Example condition, adjust as needed
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LEN,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_PART_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AVG_PART_BRAND_LEN,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUST_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LEN,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LEN,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AVG_LINEITEM_LINENUMBER,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDER_KEYS
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY / PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgAvailQuantityPerSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgMFGRLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) AS NumUniquePartTypes
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnedItems
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 50

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUST_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUST_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LEN,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST * PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_QUANTITY, L_LINESTATUS

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
