SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS ORDER_DATE,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE AS ORDER_TOTAL_PRICE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS EXTENDED_PRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY AS ORDER_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON p.P_PARTKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
    AND li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2000-01-01' AND '2000-12-31'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_RETAILPRICE
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS Order_Count,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS Average_Order_Price,
    MAX(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Returned_Quantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS Cumulative_Returned_Quantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Average_Quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Container_Len,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_MFGR_Len,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Len,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Len
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    LINEITEM,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    SUM(li.l_quantity) AS TotalShippedParts,
    AVG(li.l_discount) AS AverageDiscount,
    MAX(li.l_extendedprice) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    MIN(li.l_extendedprice) AS MinExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) AS NumSuppliers
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_Region_Name_Length,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Total_SupplyCost,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailabilityQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_CUSTKEY AS CustomerKey,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityOrdered,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * (1 - LI.L_DISCOUNT)) AS TotalRevenue,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderValue,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_SUPPKEY AS SupplierKey
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON LI.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_NAME, C.C_CUSTKEY, P.P_NAME, P.P_PARTKEY, S.S_NAME, S.S_SUPPKEY
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100 AND AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) > 100

SELECT
    P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    P_MFGR

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktsgSegmentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NationKey,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name, -- Assuming S_NAME is in SUPPLIER table
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    c.C_ADDRESS AS Customer_Address -- Assuming C_ADDRESS is in CUSTOMER table
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_BRAND

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength_S,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_LI,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnFlagA,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnFlagN,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    NATION
        JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
        JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
        JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeStringLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeysCount,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL,
    CUST.C_PHONE,
    CUST.C_ADDRESS,
    CUST.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR LIKE '%Jr%')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    SUP.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE As TotalPrice,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As ExtendedPrice,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE As ShipMode,
    Li.L_TAX As Tax,
    R.R_NAME As Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE >= DATE('1998-01-01')
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE <= DATE('1998-12-31')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, S.S_NAME, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Country,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
       AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
       AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
       AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtendedPrice,
       AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000
    AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100
    AND AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.1

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_BRAND, P.P_RETAILPRICE, SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName, SUP.S_PHONE, SUP.S_ADDRESS
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 5
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 6
    AND SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) > 10

SELECT 
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantitySold,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice
FROM 
    PART
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_MFGR,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDAT
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
HAVING
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) > 100 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 50

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS As Order_Status,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE As Order_Total,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE As Shipping_Mode,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT As Discount_Rate,
    Li.L_QUANTITY As Quantity_Ordered
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY = 1 -- Assuming you want data for a specific nation, here N_NATIONKEY = 1
ORDER BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    Li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance, COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS NumParts, SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 10 AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON (S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY OR C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY)
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05

SELECT
    P.P_NAME ASPartName,
    P.P_TYPE ASPartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE ASRetailPrice,
    P.P_SIZE ASSize,
    S.S_NAME ASSupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AsNationName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL ASSupplierAccountBalance,
    C.C_NAME ASCustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL ASCustomerAccountBalance,
    N.N_REGIONKEY ASRegionKey,
    R.R_NAME ASRegionName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASAvailableQuantity,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT 
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_CLERK,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    li.L_LINESTATUS,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_PARTKEY,
    li.L_LINENUMBER,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    li.L_SUPPKEY,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_COMMENT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    ORDERS o
INNER JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalPartRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AVG_PART_SIZE,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    CASE
        WHEN P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN P_MFGR
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MFGR_CATEGORY,
    CASE
        WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#42' THEN P_BRAND
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS BRAND_CATEGORY,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_CONTAINER,
    CASE
        WHEN P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN P_MFGR
        ELSE 'Other'
    END,
    CASE
        WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#42' THEN P_BRAND
        ELSE 'Other'
    END,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT),
    MAX(C_ACCTBAL) - MIN(S_ACCTBAL) AS BALANCE_DIFF,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_Name,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    R_Name, C_Name, S_Name, N_Name DESC, PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_PARTSUPP_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QTY,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DISTINCT_PART_KEYS,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalSales,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_BRAND, PART.P_SIZE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'USA%')
AND
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM LINEITEM)
AND
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_TAX AS L_TAX FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_TAX

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT1' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS CustKeyCount_SEGMENT1,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT2' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS CustKeyCount_SEGMENT2,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT3' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS CustKeyCount_SEGMENT3,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) > 10 THEN 'Long_N.'
        ELSE 'Short_N.'
    END AS NationNameLengthCategory,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 15 THEN 'Long_P.'
        ELSE 'Short_P.'
    END AS PartNameLengthCategory,
    MAX(MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)) AS LatestReceiptMonth,
    MAX(YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)) AS LatestReceiptYear
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 10 AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) DESC, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Country,
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Account_Balance,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Account_Balance,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 100000
    AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 500
    AND AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 300

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Customer_Balance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Supplier_Balance
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, ps.PS_AVAILQTY
ORDER BY
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY) AS Total_Parts,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_LineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_FulfilledOrderRatio,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS Distinct_Parts,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    n_region.N_NAME AS Nation_Region,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    p.P_SIZE
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n_region ON r.R_REGIONKEY = n_region.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER CUST ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR = 'ManufacturerX')

SELECT PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_RETAILPRICE, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, R.R_NAME,
CASE
    WHEN P.P_TYPE = 'BRUSH STEEL' THEN 'Brush'
    ELSE 'Other'
END AS PartTypeCategory,
CASE
    WHEN P.P_RETAILPRICE > 50 THEN 'High Price'
    ELSE 'Low Price'
END AS PriceCategory
FROM PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM
    PART
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS))

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierACCTBAL,
    SUM(LI.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LI.L_PARTKEY) AS TotalPartKeys,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    LI.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_ShipInstruct,
    R.R_REGIONKEY AS R_RegionKey
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT, R_RegionKey

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    r.R_NAME As Region_Name,
    p.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    p.P_BRAND AS Part_Brand,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    p.P_SIZE DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 'MACHINERY'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MktSegment,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY IS NOT NULL
    AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), CASE WHEN MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) = 1 THEN 'January' WHEN MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) = 2 THEN 'February' ELSE 'Other' END AS SHIP_MONTH
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 1 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 500

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS
HAVING
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) > 1000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 15
    AND AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) > 20
    AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY REGION.R_NAME ASC, NATION.N_NAME DESC, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC NULLS FIRST, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'REG AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 2 END, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'MEDIUM BRUSHED NICKEL' THEN 'MEDIUM BRUSHED NICKEL' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS, ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_ORDER_VALUE
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'North America'))
AND
    S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    N_NAME DESC

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_P_CONTAINER_Length,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_P_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS Avg_P_BrandLength,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_C_AcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_S_CommentLength,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS Sum_S_AcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_L_ReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(L_LINENUMBER) AS Avg_L_LineNumber,
    SUM(L_PARTKEY) AS Sum_L_PartKey,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_L_CommentLength
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlagLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS Num_UniqueParts,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 'Discounted'
        ELSE 'No Discount'
    END AS DiscountType
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 'Discounted'
        ELSE 'No Discount'
    END

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    CASE
        WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
        ELSE AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
    END AS QuantityByStatus,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_LINESTATUS

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_BRAND, CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 10000 THEN 'High Bal'
        ELSE 'Low Bal'
    END AS AcctBalCategory,
    REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'West') -- Focus on a specific region, 'West' in this example
ORDER BY REGION.R_REGIONKEY, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER
ON
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION
ON
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART
ON
    PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER
ON
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE'))
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            PS_PARTKEY
        FROM
            PARTSUPP
        WHERE
            PS_AVAILQTY > 0
            AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (
                SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST)
                FROM PARTSUPP
            )
        ORDER BY
            PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
            PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC
        
    )
ORDER BY
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    SUP.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierAccountBalance,
    CUST.C_NAME As Customer,
    CUST.C_ADDRESS As CustomerAddress,
    CUST.C_MKTSEGMENT As CustomerMarketSegment,
    C_CUSTKEY,
    P_PARTKEY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, SUP.S_NAME, SUP.S_ACCTBAL, CUST.C_NAME, CUST.C_ADDRESS, CUST.C_MKTSEGMENT, C_CUSTKEY, P_PARTKEY
HAVING 
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 -- filtering for parts with more than 1000 available units
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_P_Container_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_MFGR)) AS Avg_P_MFGR_Length,
    AVG(O_TOTALPRICE) AS Avg_O_TotalPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_CLERK)) AS Avg_O_Clerk_Length,
    SUM(O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS Total_O_ShipPriority,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_C_MktSegment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_S_Comment_Length,
    SUM(L_LINENUMBER) AS Total_L_Linenumber,
    AVG(L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_L_Quantity,
    P_BRAND AS P_Brand
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    P_BRAND

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvidPhoneLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOrders,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS NUM_UNIQUE_PARTS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_UNIQUE_SUPPLIERS
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDER_COUNT
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    O.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS OrderPriority,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE AS TotalPrice,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT,
    LI.L_SHIPMODE,
    LI.L_RETURNFLAG,
    R.R_REGIONKEY AS Region,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY = 1 -- assuming you want data for a specific nation, here N_NATIONKEY = 1
ORDER BY
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE DESC,
    R.R_REGIONKEY ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Name_Comment_Length,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME) + LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_AcctBal
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) > 50

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerSegment,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) As MinExtendedPrice
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 15 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 AND AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) > 7 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 50

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT Li.L_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierTransactions,
    AVG(Li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_NAME) AS UniqueParts,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    c.C_NAME AS BUYER_NAME,
    c.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000))))
AND
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierAvgBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS AvgExtendedPriceAir,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LI.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS AvgDiscountAir,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS AvgExtendedPriceShip,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN LI.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS AvgDiscountShip,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS AvgExtendedPriceRail,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN LI.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS AvgDiscountRail
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_MFGR_Len,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartName_Len,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Addr_Len,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Len,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Len,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_SupplierComments,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS N_RegionKey
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    L_LINENUMBER
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_BRAND
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUST_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TOTAL_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AVG_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    R_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS DISTINCT_SUPPLIERS
FROM
    NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS UniqueSuppliers,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 500 AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 10000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_LEN,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVERAGE_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS RETURNED_ITEMS_COUNT,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    REGION.R_NAME
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLengthShipMode,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLengthReturnFlag,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS DiscountedExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DiscountedLineItemCount
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NATIONKEY,
    c.C_NAME,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    s.S_NAME,
    s.S_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Revenue,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NATIONKEY, c.C_NAME, c.C_ACCTBAL, s.S_NAME, s.S_ACCTBAL
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) > 100000 AND AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05

SELECT
    PART.P_BRAND,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_BRAND,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    P_MFGR

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT 
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    MAX(PART.P_SIZE),
    MIN(PART.P_SIZE)
FROM 
    PART,
    CUSTOMER
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_TYPE
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 100
