SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN (SELECT C_MKTSEGMENT FROM CUSTOMER GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT HAVING COUNT(C_CUSTKEY) > 10)
ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) as AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) as AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) as AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) as AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) as AvgSupplierNameLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) as DistinctPartKeyCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT N.N_NAME AS Nation, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName, O.O_ORDERDATE, P.P_NAME AS PartName, LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN PART P ON LI.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME = 'GERMANY'
AND O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND O.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31'
AND LI.L_RETURNFLAG = ' '
AND S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CustPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_COMMENT)) AS Avg_OrderCommentLength,
    SUM(O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_LineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT 
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, R.R_NAME
ORDER BY
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT PART.P_NAME, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM PART
JOIN ORDERS ON PART.P_PARTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.1
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS ExtendedPrice,
    L.L_DISCOUNT AS Discount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PERU')
    AND P.P_TYPE = 'RIBBON'
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31'
    AND L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 500.00
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)) AS AvgOrderPriorityLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemIdLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_ShipMode,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 500
AND
    P.P_SIZE BETWEEN 1 AND 10
AND
    C.C_ACCTBAL > 10000
AND
    S.S_ACCTBAL < 5000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC,
    C.C_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    O.O_ORDERDATE,
    O.O_COMMENT,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    O.O_ORDERKEY,
    O.O_CUSTKEY,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE,
    O.O_CLERK,
    O.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    O.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    L.L_SHIPMODE,
    L.L_TAX,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    L.L_COMMITDATE,
    L.L_ORDERKEY,
    L.L_RETURNFLAG,
    L.L_LINESTATUS,
    L.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    L.L_PARTKEY,
    L.L_LINENUMBER,
    L.L_SHIPDATE,
    L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    L.L_SUPPKEY,
    L.L_DISCOUNT,
    L.L_COMMENT,
    L.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_MFGR_Length,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length_CUSTOMER,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Supplier_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length_SUPPLIER
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    MIN(n.N_NATIONKEY),
    MAX(n.N_NATIONKEY),
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY OR s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY > (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION))
ORDER BY REGION.R_NAME DESC, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) DESC, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_TAX AS L_TAX FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_TAX ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER))

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    S.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_RETAILPRICE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, S.S_NATIONKEY, N.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierCountry,
    P.P_SIZE,
    MAX(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST END) AS BuildingSupplyCost,
    MAX(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'CONSTRUCTION' THEN PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST END) AS ConstructionSupplyCost,
    MAX(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = ' PACKAGING' THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST END) AS PackagingSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION RN ON N.N_REGIONKEY = RN.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_SIZE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_Part_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthSUPPLIER,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(CASE
        WHEN L_DISCOUNT >= 0.1 THEN L_QUANTITY
        ELSE 0
    END) AS QuantitiesWithDiscountOver10,
    SUM(CASE
        WHEN L_DISCOUNT < 0.1 AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PERU') THEN L_QUANTITY
        ELSE 0
    END) AS QuantitiesWithDiscountUnder10FromPeru
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 AND
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 10000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrdersCount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_TAX > 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_TAX ELSE NULL END) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_TAX = 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_TAX ELSE NULL END) AS AvgNoTax
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    L_DISCOUNT
ORDER BY
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
CASE
    WHEN LINEITEM.L_TAX > 0 THEN 'High Tax'
    ELSE 'No High Tax'
END AS Tax_Group
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_TAX IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY CASE
    WHEN LINEITEM.L_TAX > 0 THEN 'High Tax'
    ELSE 'No High Tax'
END

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation_Name,
    P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    S_PHONE As Supplier_Phone,
    R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    N_NAME, PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    sup.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    reg.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST As Supply_Cost,
    cu.C_NAME AS Customer_Name
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER sup ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = sup.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION nAT ON sup.S_NATIONKEY = nAT.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON nAT.N_REGIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION reg ON N.N_REGIONKEY = reg.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER cu ON p.P_PARTKEY = cu.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_SIZE)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LI.L_ORDERKEY,
    LI.L_LINENUMBER,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT,
    LI.L_QUANTITY,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE,
    LI.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    R.R_REGIONKEY,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (
        SELECT
            C_NATIONKEY
        FROM
            CUSTOMER
        WHERE
            C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SALES-REP'
    )
AND
    LI.L_RETURNFLAG <> 'A'

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL),
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_PHONE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY),
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_PHONE
ORDER BY
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CASE
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Backordered'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'S' THEN 'Shipped'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 'Delivered'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ORDER_STATUS_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Return'
        ELSE 'Regular'
    END AS LINE_ITEM_STATUS
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    REGION.R_NAME ASC,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END DESC,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, S.S_PHONE
FROM NATION N
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION))
AND S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT S_NATIONKEY FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER))
ORDER BY N.N_NAME ASC, S_PHONE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), S_PHONE, R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
HAVING AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 0 AND AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_PHONE IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_NAME,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    S_NAME,
    S_ACCTBAL,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    C_NAME,
    C_CUSTKEY,
    C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    CASE
        WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, MONTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE), CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'N' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, SUPplier.S_NAME

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPContainerLen,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPBrandLen,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSCommentLen,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS SumSAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLReturnFlagLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS SumLPartKey,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLLinenumber,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLen
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 0.5 * (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT R_NAME FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE '%%S%'))
ORDER BY PART.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            PS_PARTKEY
        FROM
            PARTSUPP
        WHERE
            PS_AVAILQTY > 0
            AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (
                SELECT
                    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST)
                FROM
                    PARTSUPP
            )
        ORDER BY
            PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC
        FETCH FIRST 5 ROWS ONLY
    )
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE AS O_ORDERDATE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
  AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 0 AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 50

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(R.R_REGIONKEY) AS AvgRegionKey, -- Assuming R_REGIONKEY has integer values for simplicity
    SUM(CASE WHEN LI.L_SHIPMODE LIKE '%AIR%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(LI.L_ORDERKEY) AS AirShippingPercentage
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS NUM_PARTSUPP,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUST_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUP_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUST_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUP_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_NAME,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILQTY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AVG_PART_TYPE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_NAME,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    S_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructionLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOrders
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPARTSUPP_PARTKEY_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMKTSEGMENT_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MktSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS SUPPLIER_REGION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    MAX(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    AVG(l.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    MIN(r.R_NAME) AS MinRegionName
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 10000
    AND AVG(l.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05
    AND MIN(r.R_NAME) LIKE 'S%'

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SuppPhoneLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_LineItemShipModeLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_LineItemReturnFlagLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItemLineStatusLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_LineItemShipInstrLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS LineItemCount
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) AS Year_Committed, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) AS Month_Committed,
CASE
    WHEN YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) = YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) AND MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) < MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) THEN 'Early'
    WHEN YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) > YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) THEN 'Delayed'
    WHEN YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) = YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) AND MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) = MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) THEN 'On Time'
    ELSE 'N/A'
END AS Delivery_Status
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION N
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_LineItem_Tax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_LineItem_ReturnFlag_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS Distinct_PartKeys,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_PARTKEY) AS NumPartsToShip,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumAirShipments
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, SUP.S_NAME, P.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    c.c_name AS customer_name,
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    o.o_orderdate AS order_date,
    o.o_totalprice AS order_total_price,
    li.l_extendedprice AS line_item_extended_price,
    li.l_discount AS line_item_discount,
    li.l_quantity AS line_item_quantity,
    li.l_shipmode AS shipment_mode
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.n_nationkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_Nation_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Part_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_Comment_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_Part_Size,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_Part_RetailPrice,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_AccountBalance
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Part,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength_Part,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_Supplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength_Supplier,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPplier.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Length_C_Comment,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Length_C_Name,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Length_S_Comment,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Length_S_Name,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_S_AcctBal,
    AVG(L.L_TAX) AS Avg_L_Tax,
    AVG(LENGTH(L.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_Length_L_LineStatus,
    SUM(L.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_L_Discount,
    AVG(LENGTH(L.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_Length_L_ShipMode,
    SUM(L.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_L_Quantity
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AverageAvailability,
    MIN(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS MinSupplierBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) >= 50
    AND MIN(S_ACCTBAL) IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_BRAND LIKE 'B%'
GROUP BY
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    SUM(p.P_SIZE) AS Total_Size,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS Unique_Customers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS Unique_Suppliers
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50
    AND SUM(p.P_SIZE) > 100
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 5
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'WRAP PKG' THEN 'WRAP PKG' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost, COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY) AS DistinctNations, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    N.N_COMMENT AS NationComment,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY = 11
AND
    P.P_TYPE LIKE 'COMPONENT%'
AND
    Li.L_SHIPDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31'
AND
    Li.L_DISCOUNT > 0.1
ORDER BY
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderCount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS AvgLineItemLinenumber,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneNumberLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME,
    S_NAME,
    R_NAME

SELECT
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100 AND AVG(PART.P_SIZE) < 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 10

SELECT
    c.c_name AS customer_name,
    p.p_name AS part_name,
    SUM(li.l_quantity) AS total_ordered_quantity,
    AVG(li.l_extendedprice) AS avg_extendedprice,
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS total_order_value
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    c.c_name, p.p_name, s.s_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_quantity) > 100

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AveragePrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
    AND AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) >= 3

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLDiscount,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_MFGR) AS NumUniqueManufacturers,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, PART.P_MFGR

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgLineItemTax,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS PartRetailPrice
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    R.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMKTSegmentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
    PART.P_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUP.S_ADDRESS,
    SUP.S_PHONE,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING')
AND
    SUP.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
ORDER BY
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX)
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT 
    NP.N_NAME,
    NS.N_NAME,
    NS.N_REGIONKEY,
    NS.N_COMMENT,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY) AS NUM_PARTS_SUPPLIED,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS_SUPPLYING,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    NATION NP ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = NP.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION NS ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON NS.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    NP.N_NAME, NS.N_NAME, NS.N_REGIONKEY, NS.N_COMMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    P_SIZE,
    P_CONTAINER,
    P_TYPE,
    P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAIL_QTY,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000 AND
    AVG(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50 AND
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000 AND
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 20000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    MAX(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS MaxShipModeLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderCount
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS National_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    R.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS Customer_Balance,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS Supplier_Balance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL < 0))
    AND R.R_NAME NOT IN (SELECT R_NAME FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT S_NATIONKEY FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_ACCTBAL > 50000)))
ORDER BY
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC, S.S_ACCTBAL ASC, N.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
    JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    REGION.R_NAME ASC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    NATION.N_COMMENT DESC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_CLERK,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    li.L_LINESTATUS,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_PARTKEY,
    li.L_LINENUMBER,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    li.L_SUPPKEY,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_COMMENT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MKTSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS DistinctCommentsCount
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, C_NATIONKEY

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName, LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(N_NATIONKEY) FROM NATION))
AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N_NATIONKEY) FROM NATION))
ORDER BY L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(C.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH, AVG(LENGTH(N.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN NATION N ON TRUE -- NATION is directly linked to CUSTOMER and indirectly to other tables through N_NATIONKEY, but the join condition is straightforward with 'ON TRUE' for this composite query.
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY -- Links PARTSUPP to PART to get part names
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY -- Links PARTSUPP to CUSTOMER to get customer details
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY AND S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY -- Links CUSTOMER to SUPPLIER and NATION, ensuring supplier names are retrieved
GROUP BY P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers, AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance, COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers, AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance
FROM NATION N
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100
AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 500
AND COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) > 50
AND AVG(S_ACCTBAL) > 800

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY
FROM PART P
JOIN PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructionLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ReturnFlagCategory
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'BRASS' THEN 'BRASS'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_Type_Group,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'WAREHOUSE' THEN 'WAREHOUSE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS CustomerSegment_Group
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCPhoneLen,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCAcctBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLineStatusLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLen,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctLOrderKeys
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT p.P_PARTKEY FROM PART p JOIN PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY WHERE ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 100)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    s.S_NAME DESC,
    c.C_NAME ASC,
    r.R_NAME DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount
FROM
