    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE, c.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE ORDER BY SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 500 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 8
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUP.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    SUP.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCustomer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgTaxRATE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS UniqueOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthRegion,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS RETURNED_ITEMS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DISCOUNTED_ITEMS,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_L_SHIPMODE_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY -- assuming supplier key in NATION is unique
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY -- assuming supplier key in SUPPLIER is unique
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- assuming customer key in SUPPLIER matches CUSTOMER's key
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'North America'))
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 100000

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'AUTOMOBILE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS C_MKTSEG,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    S_SUPPKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN NATION.N_NATIONKEY = 11 THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    L_RETURNFLAG DESC,
    L_SHIPMODE ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(Case When ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY THEN ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS CustomerSupplyCost,
    MIN(Case When ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY THEN ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS CustomerMinSupplyCost,
    AVG(Case When ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY THEN ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_PARTKEY) > 1

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Cancelled'
        ELSE 'Shipped'
    END AS Status
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS DISCOUNTED_PRICE,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_COMMENT,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    MONTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE) AS ORDER_MONTH,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 50 THEN 'Large'
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE <= 50 AND PART.P_SIZE > 20 THEN 'Medium'
        ELSE 'Small'
    END AS PART_SIZE_CATEGORY
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_CNAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_CA_LENGTH,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS NUM_ORDERS,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_L_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AVG_P_SIZE,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVG_PN_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AVG_PB_LENGTH
FROM
    PART
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    S_NATIONKEY,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > (
        SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
        FROM PART
        JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        WHERE CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MOST PROFITABLE'
    )
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA'))
    AND ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistPartCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CASE
        WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'SM CASE' THEN 'SM CASE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ContainerType,
    CASE
        WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    C_CUSTKEY,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    S_NAME,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    P_SIZE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_CONTAINER IN ('SM CASE', 'LG CASE')
ORDER BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT DESC,
    CASE
        WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'SM CASE' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    S_NATIONKEY DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'BRASS' AND
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE')) AND
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPKEY,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND   ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    r.R_NAME

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 0 AND COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 1

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    CASE
        WHEN NATION.N_NAME IS NOT NULL THEN NATION.N_NAME
        ELSE 'Nation Data Not Available'
    END AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PART
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddrLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    sup.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER sup ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = sup.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON sup.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, p.P_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PAR.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART PAR ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = PAR.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON PAR.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    SUP.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PAR.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMKTSegmentLengthC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthS,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS TotalPartKeys,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscounts,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthL,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N_NAME AS Nation,
    R_NAME AS Region,
    S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS NumParts,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON N_NATIONKEY = PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON R_REGIONKEY = N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C_CUSTKEY = PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S_SUPPKEY = C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, R_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) > 50 AND
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_LineItem_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_LineItems_Shipped_Air,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Discount_Air,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_LineItems_Shipped_Rail,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Discount_Rail,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_LineItems_Shipped_Truck,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Discount_Truck
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AVG_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    C_ACCTBAL,
    S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LEN
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    C_ACCTBAL,
    S_ACCTBAL
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) ASC,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    o.o_orderdate AS OrderDate,
    o.o_totalprice AS TotalPrice,
    li.l_extendedprice AS ExtendedPrice,
    li.l_discount AS Discount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
WHERE
    n.n_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM NATION WHERE n_regionkey = (SELECT r_regionkey FROM REGION WHERE r_name = 'AMERICA'))
    AND o.o_orderdate >= DATE('1994-01-01')
    AND o.o_orderdate < DATE('1995-01-01')
    AND li.l_extendedprice > (li.l_discount + li.l_extendedprice * 0.1)
ORDER BY
    n.n_name, c.c_name, s.s_name, o.o_orderdate DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    c.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    s.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER))
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER)))
ORDER BY
    c.C_CUSTKEY, s.S_SUPPKEY, li.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NAME) AS DistinctNationNames,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME) AS DistinctSupplierNames,
    COUNT(DISTINCT REGION.R_NAME) AS DistinctRegionNames,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_RegionCommentLen
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    SUM(li.l_quantity) AS total_quantity,
    AVG(li.l_discount) AS avg_discount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.n_nationkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) > 50
    AND AVG(li.l_discount) > 0.05

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_REGION_NAME_LENGTH
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE ORDER BY SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    MAX(LI.L_SHIPMODE) AS MostFrequentShippingMode
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS CountryName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, n.N_NAME, p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS Part,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < PART.P_RETAILPRICE
ORDER BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS CountDistinctSupplierComments,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) > 50
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 20
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    O.O_ORDERKEY,
    O.O_ORDERDATE,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    LI.L_ORDERKEY,
    LI.L_SHIPMODE,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE,
    LI.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, LI.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalPartsOrdered,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    SUM(oi.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderValue,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS oi ON li.L_ORDERKEY = oi.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON oi.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT
    L_SHIPDATE AS SHIP_DATE,
    R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LEN,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPDATE,
    R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) >= 2
ORDER BY
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (
        SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST)
        FROM PARTSUPP
    )
AND
    N.N_NAME IN (
        SELECT N_NAME
        FROM NATION
        JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
        WHERE REGION.R_NAME LIKE 'A%'
    )
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT P.P_NAME, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_CUSTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000))))
ORDER BY P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, S.S_ACCTBAL DESC, N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT 
    n.n_name AS Nation_Name,
    r.r_name AS Region_Name,
    COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS Total_Orders,
    AVG(li.l_extendedprice) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.l_discount) AS Total_Discount
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN 
    ORDERS o ON n.n_nationkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY 
    n.n_name, r.r_name

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AverageAvailability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000 AND
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    L.L_DISCOUNT AS DiscountAmount
FROM
    ORDERS O
    JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
    AND L.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE '%R%'

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    SUM(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS SuppliersUsed,
    MAX(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS MaxSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(O.O_TOTALPRICE) > 10000
    AND AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) > 50
    AND MAX(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 50000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN NATION ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) DESC,
           AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT))
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) DESC,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 1
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT DISTINCT N.N_NAME AS NationName, R.R_NAME AS RegionName, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerBalance, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM NATION N
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AverageAvailability
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) < 50

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS ProductName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS AS OrderStatus,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS ExtendedPrice,
    L.L_DISCOUNT AS DiscountGiven
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY = 1 -- Replace 1 with the desired NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' -- Filter orders to only shipped ones
    AND P.P_TYPE = 'Vlieding' -- Assume 'Vlieding' is a specific product type of interest
    AND L.L_DISCOUNT > 0 -- Include only lines with a discount
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS IN_STOCK_PARTS
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), ORDERS.O_CLERK AS O_CLERK FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_CLERK

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_CLERK,
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    o.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    li.L_ORDERKEY AS LI_ORDERKEY,
    li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    li.L_LINESTATUS,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_PARTKEY,
    li.L_LINENUMBER,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    li.L_SUPPKEY,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_COMMENT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS MAX_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS MAX_NAME_LENGTH,
    MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS MAX_PHONE_LENGTH,
    MAX(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS MAX_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName, COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount, AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance, MIN(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS MinSupplierBalance
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY AND C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR LIKE 'Premium%')
    AND N.N_NAME = 'GERMANY'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_PARTKEY ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    P.P_CONTAINER,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME = 'CountryName' -- replace 'CountryName' with the desired country
    AND P.P_CONTAINER = 'DesiredContainer' -- replace 'DesiredContainer' with the desired container type
    AND P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
    AND C.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN 'Manufacturer#4'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS SupplierManufacturer,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#42' THEN 'Brand#42'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ProductBrand,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PART.P_CONTAINER IS NOT NULL AND SUPPLIER.S_PHONE IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_MFGR, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalRevenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    SUM(CASE WHEN r.R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumOrdersFromNorthAmerica,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumAkwardReturns,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumRefundedReturns,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumIncompleteReturns
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY > 0)))
    AND C.C_ACCTBAL > 5000.00
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL < 3000.00

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
ORDER BY
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1500
    AND AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05
ORDER BY
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY AND S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 500000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SHIPPED,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    d.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION d ON s.S_NATIONKEY = d.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, d.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
    AND AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100

SELECT 
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    P.P_TYPE,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUP.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUP.S_ADDRESS,
    SUP.S_PHONE,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME, 
    P.P_TYPE DESC, 
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AvgBal_Positive,
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL <= 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AvgBal_NonPositive,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 100 THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AvgRetailPrice_High,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE <= 100 THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AvgRetailPrice_Low
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    N_C.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    N_S.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N_C.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_S.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N_S.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'Screw' THEN 'Hardware'
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'Bolt' THEN 'Fastener'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_TypeCategory,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'Automotive'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'ANTARCTICA'))
    AND N.N_NAME NOT IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AMERICA'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_REGION,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRefundLineItems,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AvgValueRefundLineItems,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY END) AS SupplierCountRefundLineItems,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_SupplierName
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 10

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'P' THEN 'P' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_NAME,
    P_SIZE,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    C_NAME,
    S_ACCTBAL,
    CASE
        WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#42' THEN 'Brand#42'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_BRAND_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#1' THEN 'Manufacturer#1'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_MFGR_TYPE,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    S_PHONE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    P_SIZE DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AVG_BRAND_LENGTH,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCDBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_LINENUMBER) AS AVG_LINENUMBER,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME = 'Country_Name' -- replace 'Country_Name' with the desired country
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 -- replace 1000 with the desired threshold
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLhModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLength,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,REGION.R_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Replaced'
        ELSE 'Not Returned'
    END AS ReturnStatus
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP PS)
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    sup.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    reg.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART p ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER sup ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = sup.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON sup.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION reg ON n.N_REGIONKEY = reg.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Average_Supply_Cost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS Average_Comment_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Average_Part_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Average_Part_Type_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Average_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Average_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS Customer_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShipMode
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
ORDER BY
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) ASC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_ORDERED_QUANTITY,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_ORDER_PRICE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    o.O_ORDERDATE
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 AND
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Country,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT,
    LI.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    R.R_REGIONKEY = 1 -- Assuming region key 1, replace with desired region key
