    AND O.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31' -- Example date range, adjust as necessary
ORDER BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) < 500

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DISTINCT_PARTS,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT 
    PART.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AVG_PART_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS NUM_UNIQUE_RETAIL_PRICES
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_TYPE, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS Distinct_Customers,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_ACCTBAL,
    S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_MKTSEGMENT) > 1 AND AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND AVG(S_ACCTBAL) > 500

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLen,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS NumDistinctSupplierComments
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_CONTAINER

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeListLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIERNationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS PartRetailPrice,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    P.P_CONTAINER AS PartContainer,
    P.P_BRAND AS PartBrand
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY  -- Adjusted join condition for CUSTOMER
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP PS2)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    R.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) AS DistDistinctSuppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistDistinctCustomers
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50

SELECT MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), MIN(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    n.N_NAME AS RegionName,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    p.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    p.P_CONTAINER AS Container,
    p.P_MFGR AS Manufacturer,
    p.P_TYPE As PartType,
    p.P_BRAND As Brand
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PR.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART PR)
    AND n.N_NAME LIKE 'S%'

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierBalance,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    LI.L_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE O_ORDERSTATUS = 'shipped')
ORDER BY
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    S.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT DESC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS TotalCustomers,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS TotalSuppliers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMKTSEGMENTLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_COMMENT) AS NUM_DISTINCT_COMMENTS,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME,
    S_NAME,
    R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen, AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShippingInstrLen, AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
CASE
    WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Keep'
    WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Return'
    ELSE 'Unknown'
END AS ReturnFlagDescription
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG,
CASE
    WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Keep'
    WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Return'
    ELSE 'Unknown'
END

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART WHERE P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 100))
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    AVG(c_acctbal + s_acctbal) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(l.l_orderkey) AS LineItemCount,
    r.r_name AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON s.s_suppkey = l.l_suppkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name
HAVING
    AVG(c_acctbal + s_acctbal) > 10000
    AND COUNT(l.l_orderkey) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLineItemQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS TotalLineItemNumbers,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) > 10 THEN 'Long Nation Name'
        ELSE 'Short Nation Name'
    END AS NationNameLengthCategory,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 50 THEN 'Long Supplier Comment'
        ELSE 'Short Supplier Comment'
    END AS SupplierCommentLengthCategory
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Balances,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    PS_SupplyCost DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT
    R_NAME ASREGION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT N_NATIONKEY) AS NUM_NATIONS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SHIPPED,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_REGION
FROM
    REGION
JOIN
    NATION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY))

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    o.o_orderdate AS OrderDate,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    li.l_extendedprice AS ExtendedPrice,
    li.l_discount AS Discount
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    PART p ON li.l_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Ro.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    Ro.O_ORDERDATE
FROM
    LINEITEM Li
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS Ro ON Li.L_ORDERKEY = Ro.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE '...') -- replace '...' with desired nation name patterns
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT DESC,
    Ro.O_ORDERPRIORITY ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'R' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgOrderClerkLength,
    SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY) AS TotalOrderPriority,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktdSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS TotalLineNumber,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLineItemQuantity,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AS CustomertKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AS SupplierKey
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    n.n_name AS country_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS distinct_customers,
    SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS total_customer_balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS distinct_suppliers,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS total_supplier_balance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_nationkey = r.r_regionkey
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name,
    r.r_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) > 100
    AND SUM(c.c_acctbal) > 100000
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) > 50
    AND SUM(s.s_acctbal) > 50000

SELECT
    p.p_name,
    n.n_name AS supplier_nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    SUM(ps.ps_supplycost) AS total_supplycost,
    AVG(ps.ps_availqty) AS avg_availqty
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY
    p.p_name, n.n_name, r.r_name
HAVING
    SUM(ps.ps_supplycost) > 100000
    AND AVG(ps.ps_availqty) < 50

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 100
    AND AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) > 15
    AND AVG(P_SIZE) > 50
    AND AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) > 5
    AND AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) > 30
    AND AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) > 20

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS Supplier_Country,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    S.S_PHONE AS Supplier_Phone,
    S.S_ADDRESS AS Supplier_Address,
    LI.L_ORDERKEY AS Order_Key,
    LI.L_PARTKEY AS Part_Key,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS Extended_Price,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT AS Discount,
    LI.L_QUANTITY AS Quantity,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    R.R_NAME AS Region_Name
FROM 
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    ORDERS O ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Region with chosen name'))
    AND LI.L_RETURNFLAG <> 'R'
    AND LI.L_DISCOUNT > 0.05
ORDER BY 
    LI.L_ORDERKEY,
    LI.L_PARTKEY,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    O.O_ORDERDATE

SELECT SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    P.P_CONTAINER AS PartContainer,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL As AccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierAccountBalance,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    O.O_COMMENT AS OrderComment,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS AS OrderStatus,
    O.O_ORDERKEY AS OrderKey,
    O.O_CUSTKEY AS CustomerKey,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE AS TotalPrice,
    O.O_CLERK AS Clerk,
    O.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS OrderPriority,
    O.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS ShipPriority,
    LI.L_SHIPMODE,
    LI.L_TAX,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_COMMITDATE,
    LI.L_ORDERKEY,
    LI.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LI.L_LINESTATUS,
    LI.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LI.L_PARTKEY,
    LI.L_LINENUMBER,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE,
    LI.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    LI.L_SUPPKEY,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT,
    LI.L_COMMENT,
    LI.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS DistCommentCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailabilityQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartSupplyCommLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    MIN(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MinSupplyCost,
    MAX(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST * PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalSupplyValue
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE REGION.R_COMMENT IS NOT NULL
AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL < (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ASC, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    PART.P_BRAND
FROM
    PART
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_BRAND
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) > 3
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 7
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 5
    AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 100
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY -- Assuming PART.P_PARTKEY is linked to NATION.N_REGIONKEY through some implicit or expected relationship
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY -- Assuming NATION.N_NATIONKEY is linked to SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            PS2.PS_PARTKEY
        FROM
            PARTSUPP PS2
        JOIN
            PART P2 ON PS2.PS_PARTKEY = P2.P_PARTKEY
        JOIN
            NATION N2 ON P2.P_PARTKEY = N2.N_REGIONKEY
        WHERE
            N2.N_NAME = 'some_specific_nation' -- replace 'some_specific_nation' with actual nation name
            AND PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 1000 -- example condition for PS_SUPPLYCOST, adjust as necessary
    )
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_STRING_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_ACTIVE_LINEITEMS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_EASTERN_elineITEMS
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalPartValue,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 10000

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS NumParts,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS PartRetailPrice
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY) AS Num_Nations,
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_CustomerBal_Pos,
    AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_SupplierBal_Pos,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY > 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS Sum_Positive_LineItemExtPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_Length_ShipInstruct
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    CP.P_NAME AS Part,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    AVG(CP.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers
FROM
    PART CP
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON CP.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, CP.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) > 50 AND
    AVG(CP.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100.00
ORDER BY
    AVG(CP.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC, N.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AcctBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS Total_PartKeys,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS Returning_Orders,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) * 100.0 AS ReturnPercentage
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'Angol Moyn' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPriceAngolMoyn,
    SUM(CASE WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'Angol Zarnovic' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPriceAngolZarnovic,
    SUM(CASE WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'Dakota' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPriceDakota,
    SUM(CASE WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'England' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPriceEngland,
    SUM(CASE WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'India' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPriceIndia,
    SUM(CASE WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'Japan' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPriceJapan
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, PART.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(NATION.N_REGIONKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE < 10 THEN 1
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 10 AND PART.P_SIZE < 50 THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Planet_Avg_Account_Balance, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Mkts_Segment_Length
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10 AND AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_TYPE, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY -- Assuming PART.P_PARTKEY indirectly links to NATION via REGION (via N_REGIONKEY)
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT R.R_NAME FROM REGION R WHERE R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT N.N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION N WHERE N.N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N.N_NATIONKEY) FROM NATION N))) -- Selecting the region with the smallest region key, assuming it's of interest
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN 'In Stock'
        ELSE 'Out of Stock'
    END AS StockStatus
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS UniquePartKeys,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_TYPE IN ('MEDIUM POLISHED TIN', 'LARGE BURNISHED BRASS')
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'MEDIUM POLISHED TIN' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS2.PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP PS2 WHERE PS2.PS_AVAILQTY > 100)
AND
    S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N2.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION N2 WHERE N2.N_NAME LIKE '%%US%%')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_TYPE = ' component '
AND    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTHERN' OR R_NAME = 'NOETHERN'))
AND    c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC NULLS FIRST, 
    n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
   PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    C.C_CUSTKEY AS CustomerKey,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME = 'some_nation_name' -- replace with desired nation name
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT C_NATIONKEY, AVG(C_ACCTBAL), S_NATIONKEY, AVG(S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(L_ORDERKEY)
FROM CUSTOMER C, SUPPLIER S, LINEITEM Li
WHERE C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY AND S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(L_ORDERKEY) > 100 AND AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 10000 AND AVG(S_ACCTBAL) > 50000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    r.R_NAME As RegionName
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.N_NATIONKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
    AND li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 1000
    AND YEAR(o.O_ORDERDATE) = 2022
    AND r.R_NAME LIKE 'Americas%'
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS SupplierNation,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalPartValue,
    AVG(li.l_discount) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    PART p ON li.l_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.l_partkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, c.c_name, p.p_name, s.s_name
HAVING
    AVG(li.l_discount) > 0.05
    AND SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) > 10000

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)),
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY * P_RETAILPRICE) AS TOTAL_RETAIL_VALUE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_P_Container_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_P_MFGR_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_P_BRAND_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_C_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_C_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_S_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_S_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_S_Phone_Length,
    PART.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS Customer_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_RetailPrice
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQty
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, 
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipmodeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Total_Available_Quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS Avg_PartSuppCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
    AND C.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING 
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 5000 AND AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) > 12 AND AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 5 AND AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 100

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_PartSize,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS Num_Unique_Parts,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 50 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 100
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_SIZE, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) ASC, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HighPriorityOrderCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2-HIGH' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HighPriorityOrder2Count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '3-NORMAL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NormalPriorityOrderCount,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS AvgReturnableQuantityRatio
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
    JOIN ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN REGION R ON N.N_NATIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Private')
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE >= '2022-01-01'
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE < '2023-01-01'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_LineItemShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_LineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItemLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_LineItemTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_LineItemDiscount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_LineItemQuantity
FROM
    CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS Distinct_Parts,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Container_Length,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS Avg_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS Avg_Brand_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND AVG(P_SIZE) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) > 10

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)),
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT PART.P_TYPE AS Part_Type, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Average_Supply_Cost,
COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Comments_Count,
AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_Retail_Price
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength_N,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength_S,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength_S
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LI.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnPrice
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVERAGE_EXTENDED_PRICE, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
CASE
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'MED BAG' THEN 'Med Bag'
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'SMALL BOX' THEN 'Small Box'
    ELSE 'Other'
END AS Container_Category
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PART.P_CONTAINER IN ('MED BAG', 'SMALL BOX')
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, PART.P_CONTAINER
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Cust_Name_Length,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Cust_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Num_Unique_Supplier_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
