    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000 AND COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) > 10
ORDER BY
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT 
    PS_COMMENT AS SupplyComment,
    N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM 
    PARTSUPP, 
    NATION, 
    CUSTOMER, 
    SUPPLIER 
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'S%')
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
ORDER BY 
    N_NAME, 
    C_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT REGION.R_NAME), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SuppAddressLength
FROM NATION INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT REGION.R_NAME) > 1 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 6 AND COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME) > 5

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 100 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- Assuming CUSTKEY can also reference SUPPLIER through CUSTOMER
JOIN
    NATION SN ON S.S_NATIONKEY = SN.N_NATIONKEY -- Adjust if S_NATIONKEY is not directly referenced
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    R.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_BRAND AS Part_Brand,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Part_RetailPrice,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    S.S_PHONE AS Supplier_Phone,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    C.C_ACCTBAL As Customer_AccountBalance,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'ENGINE' AND
    S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN') AND
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SUPPLIER_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT) AS DISTINCT_COMMENTS_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MARKET_SEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    r.R_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_SIZE = (SELECT MAX(P_SIZE) FROM PART)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    s.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    n.N_NATIONKEY DESC,
    r.R_REGIONKEY DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Country,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS UniqueParts,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalSales,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) > 10 AND
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturns,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' AND L_DISCOUNT IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnsWithDiscount,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE NULL END) AS AvgReturnedQuantity
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_returned_items,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS total_returned_and_reversals,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameAddrLength,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumDifferentOrders
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE')
AND
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
AND
    P.P_TYPE = 'canvas'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_COMMITDATE, L.L_ORDERKEY, L.L_RETURNFLAG, L.L_LINESTATUS, L.L_RECEIPTDATE, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPDATE, L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, L.L_SUPPKEY, L.L_DISCOUNT
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' AND L.L_DISCOUNT > 0.1
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_SHIPDATE ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    REGION.R_COMMENT AS RegionComment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliersCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    REGION.R_COMMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnedQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDeliveredQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierCountry,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AverageAvailability,
    MAX(P_RETAILPRICE) AS HighestRetailPrice,
    MIN(P_SIZE) AS SmallestSize
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000 AND AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 500

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE L_SHIPDATE IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS) DESC, NATION.N_COMMENT ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000) -- example condition for customer account balance
    AND n.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe') -- example condition for region name
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N_C.N_NAME AS SUPPLYING_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_COUNTRY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N_S.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N_S.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_C.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_ORDER_VALUE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON LI.L_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_ORDERKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 10000
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY) > 50

SELECT
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_AirShipMode_Quantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_AirShipMode_TotalQuantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_RailShipMode_Quantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_RailShipMode_TotalQuantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_TruckShipMode_Quantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_TruckShipMode_TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) * 100.0 / COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS MachineryPercentage
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) > 1 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 500 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 12 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailabilityQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_Extended_Price,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS Avg_Order_Price
FROM
    PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    n.n_name AS CustomerNationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    li.l_extendedprice AS ExtendedPrice,
    li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity AS TotalPrice,
    ri.r_name AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.c_custkey = s.s_suppkey -- customer acts as a bridge for supplier since SUPPLIER has a FK to CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON s.s_suppkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    REGION ri ON n.n_regionkey = ri.r_regionkey
WHERE
    n.n_nationkey IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM CUSTOMER WHERE c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING') -- filter for specific market segment in customer table
    AND li.l_shipmode IN ('AIR', 'SHIP') -- filter for specific shipping modes
    AND ri.r_name IN ('AMERICAS', 'ASIA') -- filter for specific regions

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Addr_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_LineItem_ShipInstruct_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_LineItem_ReturnFlag_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS Num_OrderKeys_ReturnFlagR,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS Num_OrderKeys_ReturnFlagA
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_COMMENT) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, C.C_NATIONKEY, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME, AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY), MIN(O.O_TOTALPRICE), MAX(O.O_TOTALPRICE)
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE, C.C_NATIONKEY, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, C.C_MKTSEGMENT DESC

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN L_DISCOUNT > 0.10 AND O_TOTALPRICE > 1000 THEN 'High Value, Discounted'
        WHEN L_DISCOUNT > 0.10 AND O_TOTALPRICE <= 1000 THEN 'High Value, No Discount'
        WHEN L_DISCOUNT <= 0.10 AND O_TOTALPRICE > 1000 THEN 'Low to Medium Value, Discounted'
        ELSE 'Low to Medium Value, No Discount'
    END AS Discount_Value_Category,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    O_CUSTKEY AS Customer_ID,
    O_TOTALPRICE,
    L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Filled' ELSE 'Partially Filled' END AS Line_Status,
    C_NATIONKEY AS Customer_Nationality,
    S_NATIONKEY AS Supplier_Nationality,
    O_ORDERDATE,
    L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    ORDERS
    JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    L_DISCOUNT IS NOT NULL AND O_TOTALPRICE IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT DESC,
    O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#5' THEN 'Manufacturer#5' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'NONE' THEN 'NONE' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice, COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount, SUM(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY < PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS BelowAvgAvailability, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > (SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
       CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Fulfilled'
            WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
            ELSE 'Other'
       END AS OrderStatus
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ASC, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS CustomerNationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    li.l_shipmode,
    li.l_extendedprice,
    li.l_receiptdate
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
WHERE
    n.n_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM NATION WHERE n_regionkey = (SELECT r_regionkey FROM REGION WHERE r_name = 'ASIA'))
    AND s.s_nationkey IN (SELECT n_nationkey FROM NATION WHERE n_regionkey = (SELECT r_regionkey FROM REGION WHERE r_name = 'EUROPE'))
ORDER BY
    c.c_custkey, li.l_receiptdate DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    S_NATIONKEY,
    C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY, C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 500
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 10 THEN 'Low Stock'
        ELSE 'Ample Stock'
    END AS STOCK_STATUS
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND   
   P.P_RETAILPRICE < 50
AND   
   C.C_ACCTBAL > 1000
AND   
   N.N_NAME LIKE 'S%'
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MarketSegmentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Total_Supply_Cost,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_Supply_Cost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplyCommentLength,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) > 15
    AND AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) > 20
    AND SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_PARTKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'PROMO PLATED NICKEL' THEN 'PROMO PLATED NICKEL' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneNumberLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 100

SELECT
    N_NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DISTINCT_PART_COUNT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N_NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = N_NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
       AVG( Length(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) ) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
       CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
       SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBalance
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCnameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCphoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSphoneLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY / PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgAvailabilityRatio,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY / PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 10

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS PART_RETAILPRICE,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS NATION_REGION,
    PSUP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    PSUP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PSUP
JOIN
    PART P ON PSUP.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PSUP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PSUP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND PSUP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PSUP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, N.N_NAME ASC, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_NAME),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY),
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY, N.N_NAME, P.P_RETAILPRICE, C.C_ACCTBAL, N.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(L.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    SUM(L.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON P.P_PARTKEY = L.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST * PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_SUPPLY_RETAIL_VAL,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    COALESCE(AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) / AVG(PART.P_SIZE), 0) AS AVAIL_QTY_PER_SIZE_AVG,
    COALESCE(AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) / AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), 0) AS ADDRESS_PER_NAME_LEN_AVG
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT O_ORDERPRIORITY, AVG(LENGTH(O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLen, AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen, AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen, AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLen, AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice, AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM ORDERS
JOIN CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_ORDERPRIORITY
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Supplier,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(L_PARTKEY) AS Total_PartKeys,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discounts,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_LineItem,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON C_CUSTKEY = S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON S_SUPPKEY = L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_COMMITDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_NATIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O_FORKED')
    AND N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AMERICAS')

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM CUSTOMER
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY HAVING COUNT(*) > 1))
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgPartAvailQty,
    SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS Num_PartItems,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 10000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) > 20
ORDER BY SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME = 'United Kingdom'
    AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
    AND ps.PS_AVAILQTY < (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 50 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CASE
            WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END = 1 AND
        SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY THEN 1
        ELSE 0
    END) * 100.0 / COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) AS PctOfBuildingPartsSuppliedByEachNation
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalOrderValue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) AS NumOrders
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) > 100
    AND SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS region_name,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS total_quantity_shipped,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS avg_discount,
    MAX(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS max_extended_price,
    MIN(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS min_extended_price
FROM
    SUPPLIER s
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000 AND AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_ORDERKEY, SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY, AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXT_PRICE, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE
FROM ORDERS O
INNER JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' -- 'F' assuming it denotes 'Fulfilled' orders
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE
HAVING SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100 AND AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(Region.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(Supplier.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(Supplier.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(Supplier.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(Length(LineItem.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShippingInstructionLength,
    AVG(LineItem.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    Nation.N_Regionkey AS NationRegionKey,
    Region.R_RegionKey AS RegionRegionKey
FROM
    Nation
INNER JOIN
    Region ON Region.R_RegionKey = Nation.N_RegionKey
INNER JOIN
    Supplier ON Supplier.S_NationKey = Nation.N_NationKey
INNER JOIN
    LineItem ON LineItem.L_SuppKey = Supplier.S_SuppKey
GROUP BY
    Nation.N_RegionKey, Region.R_RegionKey

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS Avg_Region_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
  NATION.N_NAME,
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
  COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME),
  AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
  AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))
FROM
  PARTSUPP
  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
  INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
  NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
  AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50
  AND COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME) > 3
  AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 10
  AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 20
ORDER BY
  AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Account_Balance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Supplier_Average_Account_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Supplier,
    REGION.R_COMMENT AS Region_Comment
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000
    AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Customer_Nation_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    c.C_PHONE AS Customer_Phone,
    c.C_ACCTBAL AS Customer_Account_Balance,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT AS Customer_Market_Segment,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    s.S_PHONE As Supplier_Phone,
    li.L_SHIPMODE As Shipping_Mode,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS Extended_Price,
    li.L_DISCOUNT AS Discount,
    li.L_QUANTITY AS Quantity
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    (li.L_SHIPMODE IN ('AIR', 'BEST') AND li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 1000)
    OR (li.L_SHIPMODE IN ('REGISTERED', 'TRAIN') AND li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE < 500)
ORDER BY
    r.R_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_SHIPMODE DESC, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionLen,
    N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PS_PARTKEY, N_NATIONKEY
HAVING AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 100 AND AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) > 15 AND AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) > 5

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC,
    REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SuppAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_ShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipModeLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_DISCOUNT > 0.1 THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS HighDiscountQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_DISCOUNT <= 0.1 THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS LowDiscountQuantity
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_TAX,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_LINEITEM_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_PER_SUPPLIER,
    MAX(L_RECEIPTDATE) AS LATEST_RECEIVED_DATE,
    MIN(L_RECEIPTDATE) AS EARLIEST_RECEIVED_DATE
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantityShippedPerMode,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPricePerMode
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipMode_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlag_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Part_RetailPrice,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS Customer_AccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    S.S_ACCTBAL As Supplier_AccountBalance,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    N.N_REGIONKEY As Nation_RegionKey,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) < 10

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE ORDER BY SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS LineStatus
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_CUSTKEY) AS NumberOfCustomers,
    AVG(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AverageOrderTotalPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L.L_SUPPKEY) AS NumberOfSuppliers,
    SUM(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * L.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemValue
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY <= 100 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ELSE NULL END) AS AvgAvailQty_LessOrEqual_100,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ELSE NULL END) AS AvgAvailQty_MoreThan_100,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgLengthOfNationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgLengthOfPartName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLengthOfCustomerName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthOfSupplierName,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP,
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')

SELECT
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    LINEITEM
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'N')
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_PARTSUPP,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost_PARTSUPP,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance_SUPPLIER
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT,
    P.P_CONTAINER,
    P.P_MFGR,
    P.P_COMMENT,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND,
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_ADDRESS,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_PHONE,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
       SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
       AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
       AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
       COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
       COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERKEY, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, O.O_CLERK, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, O.O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT AS CustomerComment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS As SupplierAddress,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Fulfilled'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 'Open'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS LineStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS HIGHEST_RETAIL,
    MIN(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS LOWEST_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME

SELECT
    ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER,
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    ORDERS
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' -- 'F' for Full
ORDER BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE '%S%') -- Filter parts with 'S' in name
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, -- Order by supply cost desc
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC, -- If supply costs are equal, order by customer account balance desc
    S.S_ACCTBAL DESC -- If both previous are equal, order by supplier account balance desc

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
    AND SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > (SELECT SUM(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSuppCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    p.p_name AS Part,
    AVG(li.l_quantity) AS AvgQuantity,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_discount) AS TotalDiscountedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) AS SupplierCount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_quantity) > 100

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS PartsWithAvailQtyPercent,
    SUM(CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ELSE 0 END) / SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) * 100 AS PartsWithAvailQtyValuePercentage
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumReturnedItems,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumNonReturnedItems,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AvgNonReturnedItemPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AvgReturnedItemPrice
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
