    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION NC ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NC.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON NC.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_COMMITDATE
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME AS P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_LineItemShipModeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Replaced'
        ELSE 'Not Returned'
    END AS L_RETURNFLAG_Description
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_BRAND, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName, R.R_REGIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
AND
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Bicycle Lovers')

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(CASE WHEN R.R_NAME = 'AMERICA' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS HasAmericaRegion
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    r.r_name AS RegionName,
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY
    p.p_name, n.n_name, r.r_name
ORDER BY
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(L.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(L.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    L.L_RETURNFLAG AS ReturnFlag,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L.L_RETURNFLAG) AS NumDistinctReturnFlags
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM L ON S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    L.L_RETURNFLAG
ORDER BY
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(L.L_DISCOUNT) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityOrdered,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOfOrders,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumOfReturns
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    c.C_CUSTKEY, 
    s.S_SUPPKEY, 
    c.C_NAME, 
    s.S_NAME
HAVING 
    Sum(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT p.P_PARTKEY FROM PART p JOIN PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY WHERE ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND 
    s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT n.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION n WHERE n.N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')
AND 
    c.C_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT n.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION n WHERE n.N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Cancelled'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 'Delivered'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS Status,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE LIKE 'AIR%' THEN 'Air'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE LIKE 'SHIP%' THEN 'Ship'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ShippingMode,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME,
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (
        SELECT AVG(p2.P_RETAILPRICE) 
        FROM PART p2
        JOIN CUSTOMER c2 ON p2.P_PARTKEY = c2.C_CUSTKEY
        GROUP BY p2.P_PARTKEY
        HAVING COUNT(p2.P_PARTKEY) > 1
    )
ORDER BY 
    c.C_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    n.N_NAME

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST,
CASE
    WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'ROTO PAK' THEN 'ROTO PAK'
    WHEN P_TYPE LIKE 'INSERT%' THEN P_TYPE
    ELSE 'Other'
END AS P_CONTAINER_TYPE,
P_MFGR,
C_CUSTKEY,
S_NATIONKEY,
S_ADDRESS
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    SUM(CS.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CS ON P.P_PARTKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CS.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON CS.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- Assuming CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY references SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 5000 AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS NumPartsWithDistinctSupply,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLen,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLen,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSuppAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST < 50.00
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME, SUP.S_NAME, CUST.C_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'BUILDING'
        WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS SEGMENT_CATEGORY,
    S.S_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_PHONE,
    S.S_PHONE,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    C.C_ADDRESS,
    S.S_ADDRESS
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT IN ('BUILDING', 'FURNITURE')
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1
        WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) > 50

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    R.R_REGIONKEY,
    R.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMKTSEGMENTLength,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION N
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    R.R_REGIONKEY, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_TYPE,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_NATIONKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_NATIONKEY) AS Customer_Count
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_TYPE,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthC,
    AVG(P.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_NATIONKEY) AS NumNations,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT c.C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER c WHERE c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING')
AND
    s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT n.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION n WHERE n.N_NAME = 'FRANCE')
ORDER BY
    n.N_NATIONKEY, li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthSUPPLIER,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalLinesReturned,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthREGION,
    S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACC_BAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AVG_TAX,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_SHIP_INSTR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILAiABILITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_SUPPLIERS
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000 AND
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 50 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT N.N_NATIONKEY) = 1

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctParts,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE))

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_COMMENT,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    P.P_SIZE,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_PARTKEY) AS NUM_PARTS_SUPPLIED
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME
HAVING 
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000 AND COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_PARTKEY) > 50

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    P_SIZE,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    P_TYPE,
    P_BRAND,
    PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT 
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_Part_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_Retail_Price,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    PART.P_PARTKEY
FROM 
    PART
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    LINEITEM.L_TAX, 
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, 
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, 
    PART.P_PARTKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLength,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'MED DRUM' THEN 'MED DRUM'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_CONTAINER_Category
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    S.S_PHONE As Supplier_Phone,
    C.C_NAME As Customer_Name,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS Customer_Account_Balance,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'LENGTH METER'
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SOLD,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    MAX(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS MAX_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    MAX(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    SUM(CASE WHEN C.C_CUSTKEY = PS_SUPPKEY THEN P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgLengthContainer,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgLengthName,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgLengthBrand,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthAddress,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthPhone
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    (SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) / SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)) AS AvgExtendedPricePerUnit,
    MAX(MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)) AS MaxReceiptMonth,
    MIN(MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)) AS MinReceiptMonth,
    MAX(MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)) AS MaxShippingMonth,
    MIN(MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)) AS MinShippingMonth
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    MAX(o.o_orderdate) AS LatestOrderDate,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalRevenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) AS SupplierCount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.n_nationkey = o.o_custkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.o_orderkey = li.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierACCTBAL,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength
FROM
    ORDERS
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000000
    AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL)

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNNameLen,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSLNameLen,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    SP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SP.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP))
ORDER BY
    P.P_NAME, SP.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    SUM(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * L.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalRevenue,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON C.C_CUSTKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 50000
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLen,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 5

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE
ORDER BY
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
ORDER BY 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    s.S_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    n.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME,
    S_NAME,
    R_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH_REGION,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH_SUPPLIER
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME,
    S_NAME,
    R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME, AVG(LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LL.L_DISCOUNT), MIN(LL.L_RECEIPTDATE), MAX(LL.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LL ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LL.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LL.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    O_ORDERSTATUS,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_COMMENT)),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    ORDERS
    JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERSTATUS,
    L_SHIPMODE
HAVING
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'Bicycle')
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY),
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME, -- Assuming PART table has P_NAME
    PART.P_PARTKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_ORDERSTATUS FROM ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_Container_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_Type_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS Avg_Brand_Length,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Account_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Num_Distinct_Supplier_Comments
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT 
    s.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    s.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    s.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    s.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    li.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS ExtendedPrice,
    li.L_TAX AS Tax,
    li.L_COMMITDATE AS CommitDate,
    li.L_ORDERKEY AS OrderKey,
    li.L_RETURNFLAG AS ReturnFlag,
    li.L_LINESTATUS AS LineStatus,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE As ReceiptDate,
    li.L_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    li.L_LINENUMBER As LineNumber,
    li.L_SHIPDATE AS ShipDate,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT As ShippingInstructions,
    li.L_DISCOUNT AS Discount,
    li.L_COMMENT As LineComment
FROM 
    SUPPLIER s
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
    JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), REGION.R_REGIONKEY, AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY REGION.R_REGIONKEY DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN 'Manufacturer#4'
        ELSE 'Other Manufacturers'
    END AS Manufacturer,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#42' THEN 'Brand#42'
        ELSE 'Other Brands'
    END AS Brand,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierAccountBalance
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_MFGR, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    L.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    LINEITEM L
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION))
    AND L.L_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE YEAR(O_ORDERDATE) = 2022)
ORDER BY
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice, AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity, COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS NumDistinctSuppliers,
    AVG(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'A' THEN 1.0 ELSE NULL END) AS AvgPriceForCompletedOrders,
    AVG(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'N' THEN 1.0 ELSE NULL END) AS AvgPriceForUncompletedOrders
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY))

SELECT P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
       PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
       Su.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
       C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
       NS.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
       R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM PART P
JOIN PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER Su ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION NS ON Su.S_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON NS.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON Su.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE NS.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME='Antarctica')

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) * 1.2)

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS PartCountWithAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgLengthNationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLengthCustomerName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthSupplierPhone,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthSupplierAddress,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NS.N_NAME AS NationName,
    NP.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(PS.PS_PARTKEY) AS NumPartsSupplied,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NS ON S.S_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION NP ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NP.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NS.N_NAME,
    NP.N_NATIONKEY,
    S.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(PS.PS_PARTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY
    NS.N_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPartContainerLen,
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ReturnStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) AS PartCount,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) > 10 AND AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS num_customers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS num_suppliers,
    SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS total_customer_balance,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS total_supplier_balance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) > 0
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) > 0
ORDER BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN 'Urgent'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2-HIGH' THEN 'High'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '3-MEDIUM' THEN 'Medium'
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '4-NOT SPECIFIED' THEN 'Low'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS OrderPriorityCategory,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Shipped'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 'Open'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS LineStatus
FROM
    ORDERS
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '1992-01-01' AND '1998-01-01'
ORDER BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC, N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 'N' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT C_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY, AVG(C_ACCTBAL), AVG(S_ACCTBAL), SUM(L_DISCOUNT), COUNT(L_RETURNFLAG) AS Num_Of_Returns
FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY
HAVING SUM(L_DISCOUNT) > 1000
ORDER BY SUM(L_DISCOUNT) DESC

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ORDER_STATUS_CATEGORY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS ORDER_VALUE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CASE
        WHEN YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) = YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE) THEN 'On-time'
        ELSE 'Delayed'
    END AS DELIVERY_TIMELINESS
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), SUM(CASE WHEN LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) > 50 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumLongComments
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) > 30 AND SUM(CASE WHEN LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) > 50 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) > 0

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME As RegionName,
    psup.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    psup.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP psup
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON psup.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON psup.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    psup.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND p.P_RETAILPRICE > psup.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    psup.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    psup.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
  PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
  CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
  SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
  SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
  PART.P_NAME
FROM
  PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
  SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
  CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
  PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE
  CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN ('AUTOMOBILE', 'HOME APPLIANCES')
ORDER BY
  SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
  CASE
    WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 1
    ELSE 2
  END,
  SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS_SUPPKEY = S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS_SUPPKEY = C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C_NATIONKEY = N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_RETAIL,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NATIONKEY)) AS AVG_NATION_KEY_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AVG_PART_BRAND_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    p.p_name AS Part,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalSales,
    AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.l_suppkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) > 100000
    AND AVG(s.s_acctbal) > 50000

SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFLAGLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_NATIONKEY) AS UniqueCustomerNationalKeys
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    REGION.R_NAME
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGIon ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 500

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQty,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgProductNameLen,
    C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'Component'
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS O_ORDERSTATUS FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierAvgAccountBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, CUSTOMER.C_NAME DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT), MAX(LI.L_RECEIPTDATE), MIN(LI.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ADDRESS AS CustomerAddress,
    C.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    S.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_DISCOUNT > 0.10
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
