    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice, MAX(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS MaxTax, MIN(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS MinDiscount
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS NUM_ORDERS,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_C_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_C_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_C_PHONE_LENGTH
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS COMBINED_LEN,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PART.P_SIZE BETWEEN 1 AND 30
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND
    NATION.N_NAME IN (
        SELECT
            N_NAME
        FROM
            NATION
        WHERE
            N_REGIONKEY IN (
                SELECT
                    R_REGIONKEY
                FROM
                    REGION
                WHERE
                    R_NAME = 'ANTARCTICA'
            )
    )
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS AS OrderStatus,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE As TotalPrice,
    s.S_NAME As SupplierName,
    li.L_SHIPMODE As ShippingMode,
    li.L_DISCOUNT As DiscountRate
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN ORDERS o ON c.C_CUSTKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_SIZE = li.L_QUANTITY
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PART.P_CONTAINER IN ('SNAPP TOP', 'WRAP PKG')
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PART.P_CONTAINER DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
       AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
       NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY N_NATIONKEY
HAVING AVG(LENGTH(SUPplier.S_NAME)) > 10
AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 15
AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 10000
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC

SELECT 
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'BRUSHED BRASS' THEN PART.P_PARTKEY END) AS BrushedBrassPartCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS MachineryCustomerCount
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_PARTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT_RETURNED,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT_RETAINED,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_L_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    CS.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CS.C_ACCTBAL,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    N.N_COMMENT,
    R.R_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER CS ON S.S_SUPPKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON CS.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 500 AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 15 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS total_line_items,
AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS avg_discount, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS total_extended_price
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 10 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05 AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) > 15 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) > 30 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) > 15
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    O.O_ORDERKEY,
    O.O_ORDERDATE,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    REG.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    NATION N ON O.O_CUSTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION REG ON N.N_REGIONKEY = REG.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) > 1
    AND SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 1000
ORDER BY
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartkeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipmodeLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DiscountedLineItemCount
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'NATION_NAME') -- replace 'NATION_NAME' with the desired nation name
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AVERAGE_FULFILLED_LINE_STATUS,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AVERAGE_AIRSHIPPING_MODE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) AS Unique_Suppliers
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS Avg_PartSupplyCommentLength,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Total_SupplyCost,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS NationRegionKey,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_COMMENT AS Nation_Comment,
    C.C_ADDRESS AS Customer_Address,
    S.S_COMMENT AS Supplier_Comment,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_COMMITDATE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    R.R_NAME LIKE '%A%'
ORDER BY
    Li.L_ORDERKEY DESC,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NATIONKEY AS NATION_KEY,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAILABILITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 10

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME) + LENGTH(S_NAME) + LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_TAX),
    L_SHIPDATE,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(L_PARTKEY) AS TOTAL_PARTKEYS,
    L_LINESTATUS
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON C_CUSTKEY = S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON S_SUPPKEY = L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPDATE,
    L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVERAGE_RETAIL_PRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_PHONE_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS LINEITEM_ORDER_COUNT,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS MAX_QUANTITY,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS MIN_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT DISTINCT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000)
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 500000)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT
    P_BRAND,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_Availability,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_PartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P_BRAND

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemFlagLen,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS ReceiptYear
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) DESC

SELECT
    O_ORDERSTATUS,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_COMMENT)),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPINSTRUCT)),
    SUM(L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O_ORDERSTATUS_X' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS COUNT_X_STATUS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O_ORDERSTATUS_Y' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS COUNT_Y_STATUS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O_ORDERSTATUS_Z' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS COUNT_Z_STATUS
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    p.P_SIZE AS PART_SIZE,
    p.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND AS PART_BRAND,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ASIA')
ORDER BY 
    p.P_NAME

SELECT
    Orders.O_ORDERKEY,
    Orders.O_ORDERDATE,
    SUM(LineItem.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LineItem.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * (1 - LineItem.L_DISCOUNT)) AS AverageRevenuePerLineItem,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LineItem.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOfOrders,
    Orders.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    Orders.O_CUSTKEY,
    Orders.O_TOTALPRICE,
    Orders.O_CLERK,
    Orders.O_ORDERPRIORITY
FROM
    ORDERS
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM
ON
    Orders.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    Orders.O_ORDERKEY, Orders.O_ORDERDATE, Orders.O_ORDERSTATUS, Orders.O_CUSTKEY, Orders.O_TOTALPRICE, Orders.O_CLERK, Orders.O_ORDERPRIORITY
HAVING
    SUM(LineItem.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    S.S_PHONE,
    S.S_ADDRESS,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    Li.L_ORDERKEY,
    Li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    Li.L_LINESTATUS,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    Li.L_PARTKEY,
    Li.L_LINENUMBER,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_COMMITDATE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME LIKE '%excepted%'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME DESC,
    S.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CASE WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'JUMBO BOX' THEN 'JUMBO BOX' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_MFGR, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'TAKE BACK RETURN' THEN 'TAKE BACK RETURN' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_COMMENT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_PARTKEY) AS TotalParts,
    AVG(LENGTH(n.N_NAME)) AS AverageNationNameLength,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountsBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(s.S_NAME)) AS AverageSupplierNameLength,
    MAX(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS MaxAvailabilityQuantity,
    MIN(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS MinAvailabilityQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON n.N_NATIONKEY = ps.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    ps.PS_PARTKEY, s.S_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP_AVG.AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUST_AVG.AVG_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    (SELECT
        PS_PARTKEY,
        AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST
     FROM
        PARTSUPP
     GROUP BY
        PS_PARTKEY) SUP_AVG ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = SUP_AVG.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    (SELECT
        C_CUSTKEY,
        AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL
     FROM
        CUSTOMER
     GROUP BY
        C_CUSTKEY) CUST_AVG ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST_AVG.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP_AVG.AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUST_AVG.AVG_ACCTBAL
ORDER BY
    SUP_AVG.AVG_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    CUST_AVG.AVG_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 0
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS QuantityShippedAir,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalExtendedPriceAir,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'ROAD' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS QuantityShippedRoad,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'ROAD' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalExtendedPriceRoad,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'RAISE' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS QuantityShippedRail,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'RAISE' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalExtendedPriceRail
FROM
    NATION,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    PART.P_MFGR,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON p.P_BRAND = s.S_NAME -- Assuming brand matches supplier name
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 -- Example condition, adjust as needed
    AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000 -- Example condition, adjust as needed

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS "Total_ExtendedPrice_Building",
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOME' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS "Total_ExtendedPrice_Home",
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, S.S_PHONE, S.S_ADDRESS, S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION N
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, PART.P_NAME AS PartName, PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize, CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountsBalance, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
      AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
      AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS CustomerCount_Building,
      COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 100000 THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS SupplierCount_HighBalance
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILITY,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    CUST.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CUSTOMER_SEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY REGION.R_REGIONKEY DESC, PART.P_PARTKEY DESC, SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) > 1
ORDER BY
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustPersNation,
    SUM(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBal,
    MAX(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SegmentA' THEN P.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS MaxRetailPriceSegmentA,
    MIN(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SegmentB' THEN P.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS MinRetailPriceSegmentB
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) DESC

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    CASE 
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN 'HOUSEHOLD'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY 
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Product_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE'))
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderedLinesCount,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        ELSE 'Not Returned'
    END AS LineStatus
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 100

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS ORDER_DATE,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS AS ORDER_STATUS,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS EXTENDED_PRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY AS QUANTITY_ORDERED
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_TYPE = 'Component' -- Filtering for Components only
    AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' -- Filtering for specific market segment (BUILDING)
    AND o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' -- Only looking at shipped orders
    AND li.L_SHIPMODE IN ('AIR', 'SHIP') -- Orders shipped via air or sea
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE >= '2023-01-01' -- Orders from 2023 and beyond
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE < '2024-01-01' -- Until end of 2023
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME,
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_TAX, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUST_COUNT,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUST_BAL,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BAL,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_COMMENT,
    R.R_COMMENT,
    S.S_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPNameLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_MFGR)) AS AvgPMfgLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCMktSegmentLength,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUP.S_COMMENT,
    R.R_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_MFGR = NATION.N_NAME  -- Assuming P_MFGR matches NATION.N_NAME
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 50.00
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS SupplierCountryName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    N_COMMENT,
    S_COMMENT,
    C_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0

SELECT N.N_NAME AS Country, C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName, AVG(LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice, AVG(LL.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LL ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LL.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LL.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME
HAVING AVG(LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND AVG(LL.L_DISCOUNT) > 5

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY AND S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TOTAL_ORDERS,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_ADDRESS,
    C.C_PHONE,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_ADDRESS,
    S.S_PHONE,
    LL.L_SHIPMODE,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LL.L_TAX,
    LL.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LL ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LL.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    LL.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
    AND LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 1000
    AND R.R_NAME IN ('ASIA', 'EUROPE')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY, C.C_CUSTKEY, S.S_SUPPKEY, LL.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvcCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstructLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalDistinctExtendedPrices
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PART_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS CUST_AVG_NAME_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS SUPP_AVG_NAME_LEN,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLineItemShipInstrLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    COUNT(l.L_ORDERKEY) AS LINE_ITEM_COUNT,
    AVG(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_LINE_ITEM_PRICE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(l.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON o.O_ORDERKEY = l.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(l.L_ORDERKEY) > 1 AND AVG(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 500

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), L_SHIPDATE
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, L_SHIPDATE
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000 AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) > 3
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    R_NAME AS R_REGION,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS Avg_NationNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLen,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_CustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    R_NAME

SELECT
    O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(O_TOTALPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT))
FROM
    ORDERS O
    JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT 
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM 
    PART P
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    P.P_PARTKEY, 
    S.S_NAME, 
    C.C_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_SIZE = 10 AND
    S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ARGENTINA') AND
    C.C_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ARGENTINA')

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPL_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC, S_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT PART.P_RETAILPRICE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY)
FROM PART
INNER JOIN PARTSUPP ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtendedPrice,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION
        INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
        INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    N_NAME AS Nation,
    R_NAME AS Region,
    C_NAME AS Customer,
    S_NAME AS Supplier,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, R_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY
    N_NAME, R_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_SHIPDATE AS ShipDate
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    (SELECT * FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_CUSTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART)) AS c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    (SELECT * FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_SUPPKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER)) AS s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_TYPE = 'Component' -- Assuming 'Component' is a specific part type category you want to filter on
ORDER BY
    li.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    p.P_NAME

SELECT SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM CUSTOMER
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 10 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailQty,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CustBal,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SuppBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS Num_Parts,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Account_Balance,
    SUM(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Total_Nation_Comment_Length,
    SUM(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Total_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    SUM(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Total_Supplier_Name_Length,
    SUM(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Total_Region_Name_Length,
    SUM(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Total_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_AddressCommentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierAccountBal,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_LineItemExtendedPrice,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS Pct_ReturnFlagA,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS Pct_ReturnFlagR,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'O' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS Pct_ReturnFlagO
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS EARLIEST_RECEIPT,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) AS LATEST_SHIPMENT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) >= 5 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LL.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- Assuming the typo 'CUSTOMER(C_CUSTKEY)' references 'PART(P_PARTKEY)' is indeed a mistake and should reference SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM LL ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LL.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    LL.L_LINENUMBER = 1 -- Assuming we want only the first lineitem for each supplier-customer pair
    AND LL.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' -- Filtering by shipmode
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY, S.S_SUPPKEY, LL.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    c.C_NATIONKEY AS CUSTOMER_NATION_KEY,
    n_c.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME_2,
    sp.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    sp.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP sp ON p.P_PARTKEY = sp.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON sp.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON sp.PS_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_c.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR LIKE '%E.M.%')

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe'))
    AND P.P_TYPE = 'Component'

SELECT
    C.C_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION AS R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP AS PS2)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MarketSegment,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CustomerPhoneNumberLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierCommentsCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneNumberLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_COST, N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierAccountBalance,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS TotalLineItemsSuppliedByEachNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AverageLengthOfSupplierAddress,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AverageLengthOfShippingInstructions,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AverageLengthOfRegionComment
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE AS O_ORDERDATE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERDATE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalRevenue
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05 * SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY)

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS PART_NATION,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILABLE_QTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS Average_Discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) AS Unique_Suppliers,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * (1 - li.L_DISCOUNT)) AS Total_Revenue
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    SUM(p.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND SUM(p.P_SIZE) > 1000

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 10 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.1
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_SIZE
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE PART.P_SIZE > (SELECT AVG(P_SIZE) FROM PART)
AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA')
ORDER BY PART.P_SIZE DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_COMMENT), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
