    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthRegion,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) > 5 AND
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS2.PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP PS2 WHERE PS2.PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
    AND N.N_NAME LIKE '%%ountry%%'
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_PARTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O' THEN 'O' ELSE 'Other' END AS ORDER_STATUS,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    P_MFGR,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS Avg_Type_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS Avg_Brand_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_Comment_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS Unique_Customers,
    SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS Total_Retail_Price
FROM
    PART
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER
ON
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P_MFGR, C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NAME, C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Product_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE As Order_Total_Price,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON p.P_PARTKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT'
    AND li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE >= DATE('1998-01-01')
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE < DATE('1999-01-01')
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_CONTAINER = 'SM CASE'
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'SM CASE' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT))

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    MAX(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    MIN(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS MinDiscount
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_CUSTKEY,
    c.C_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    MAX(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND MIN(li.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.1

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS Avg_OrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS Avg_ClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_ShipMode,
    O_ORDERPRIORITY AS O_OrderPriority,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 5 THEN AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)
        ELSE 0
    END AS AvgAvailQty_Size5orMore,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'Component' THEN AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
        ELSE 0
    END AS AvgSupplyCost_Components
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME IN ('NATION_NAME_1', 'NATION_NAME_2') -- replace with actual nation names
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS PARTNER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    R.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MarketSegment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS TotalCustomers,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS TotalSuppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Order_Count,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipMode_Length,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Returned_Items_Count,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS total_extended_price,
    SUM(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS total_discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) AS distinct_suppliers,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS avg_customer_account_balance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON li.L_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY AND s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY) > 100
    AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000
ORDER BY
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) AS DistinctAddresses,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER
ON
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR
ORDER BY
    MIN(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC, MAX(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    SU.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName,
    C.C_NAME As CustomerName,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice,
    P.P_BRAND As Brand
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SU ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SU.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SU.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Returned,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'I' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Instructed,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipMode_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY -- Assuming SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY refers to the nation where supplier is based
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(PART.P_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) AS Distinct_LineItem_Nums,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_Returns,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_ShipInstruct_Length,
    C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS ShipDate
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME,
        CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
        SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
        LINEITEM.L_TAX,
        LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
        LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
        REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER) AND N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION))
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA'))
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC, N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    P_NAME AS PartName,
    P_TYPE,
    C_ACCTBAL,
    S_PHONE,
    R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A' ELSE 'Other' END

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON p.P_PARTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS Avg_MFGR_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS Avg_P_Type_Length,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS Distinct_Parts,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_C_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_C_Phone_Length,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_MFGR)) AS AvgMfgrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 500

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'Type#1' THEN 'Type#1'
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'Type#2' THEN 'Type#2'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS PartTypeCategory,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#A' THEN 'Brand#A'
        WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#B' THEN 'Brand#B'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS PartBrandCategory,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT Part.P_TYPE, Supplier.S_NAME, AVG(PartSupp.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PartSupp.PS_COMMENT), AVG(Length(Part.P_NAME)), AVG(Length(Customer.C_NAME)), AVG(Length(Supplier.S_ADDRESS))
FROM PARTSUPP AS PartSupp
JOIN SUPPLIER AS Supplier ON Supplier.S_SUPPKEY = PartSupp.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN PART AS Part ON Part.P_PARTKEY = PartSupp.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER AS Customer ON Customer.C_CUSTKEY = Part.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY Part.P_TYPE, Supplier.S_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS SUPPLIER_REGION,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'Some Specific Nation Name')
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH_CUSTOMER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH_SUPPLIER,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O_ORDERKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT))
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C_CUSTKEY = O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S_NATIONKEY = C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON L_SUPPKEY = S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' OR O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2-HIGH' OR O_ORDERPRIORITY = '3-MEDIUM'
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) > 50
    AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_C_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_P_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_S_Name_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_P_RetailPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax_Per_Order,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Num_Orders,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    PART.P_SIZE AS Average_Part_Size
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    p.P_SIZE AS PART_SIZE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS PART_RETAILPRICE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CUSTOMER_MARKET_SEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_TYPE = 'PIN' -- Example: filter parts of type 'PIN'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'USA') -- Example: filter suppliers from USA
    AND c.C_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'CANADA') -- Example: filter customers from Canada
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT DISTINCT n.N_NAME AS NationName, c.C_NAME AS CustomerName, s.S_NAME AS SupplierName, c.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance
FROM NATION n
JOIN CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierTotalBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG( Length(PART.P_MFGR))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS NationRegionKey,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 0

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    p.p_name AS PartName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalSales,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.l_returnflag = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturns
FROM
    PART p
    JOIN CUSTOMER c ON p.p_partkey = c.c_custkey
    JOIN LINEITEM li ON p.p_partkey = li.l_partkey
    JOIN SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
    JOIN NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name, c.c_name, s.s_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'AFRICA')
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND P.P_TYPE = 'watches'
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    MAX(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Max_Available_Quantity,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_Supply_Cost,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME As Nation_Name
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME LIKE '%A%' -- Filter nations containing 'A' for complexity
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS avg_supply_cost,
 AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS avg_retail_price,
 AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS avg_name_length,
 AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS avg_supplier_name_length
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) > 1 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 50

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'CONTINENT_X'))
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    S.S_NAME As Supplier,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    s.S_PHONE,
    sup.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    sup.PS_AVAILQTY,
    cust.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    cust.C_ACCTBAL,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP sup
JOIN
    PART p ON sup.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON sup.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER cust ON sup.PS_SUPPKEY = cust.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON cust.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    REGION.R_NAME DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY, C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE C.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PERTH')
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC, C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT PART.P_MFGR, AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_MFGR

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING')
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'RAILWAYS')
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Bal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Bal
FROM
    NATION
    LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 1000

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_RETAILPRICE > 50)
    AND SUP.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
    AND N.N_NAME LIKE '%' || 'Europe%'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    N.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) > 50 AND
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 15000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgCommLengthPartMFGR,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCommLengthCustomerAddress,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCommLengthCustomerName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCommLengthCustomerPhone,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_Size
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_TAX, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_COMMENT IS NOT NULL AND SUPPLIER.S_PHONE IS NOT NULL AND LINEITEM.L_TAX IS NOT NULL AND REGION.R_COMMENT IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PART
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) DESC,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS Avg_Nation_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Supplier_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgLShipInstrLength
FROM 
    NATION 
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY 
JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
ORDER BY 
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) DESC, 
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    LINEITEM Li
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)) -- Considering only nations from the largest region
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME ASC, S.S_NAME ASC, Li.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailability,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Supplier_Country,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    L.L_SHIPMODE AS Shipping_Method,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    L.L_TAX,
    L.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    L.L_ORDERKEY,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    LINEITEM L
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON L.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT LIKE '%South%')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME DESC,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    L.L_TAX ASC,
    L.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    AVG(p_retailprice) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(s_acctbal) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(p_retailprice) > 50.00
    AND SUM(s_acctbal) > 100000.00
ORDER BY
    AVG(p_retailprice) DESC,
    SUM(s_acctbal) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS NUM_ORDERS,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AVG_TOTAL_PRICE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AVG_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUST_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME) + LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL + S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDERS,
    AVG(L_QUANTITY) AS AVG_QUANTITY,
    L_SHIPDATE AS SHIP_DATE
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM L ON S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAIL_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, p.P_BRAND, s.S_NAME, c.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'FRANCE')
    AND p.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT'
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000

SELECT 
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM 
    ORDERS o
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '1998-01-01' AND '1998-12-31'
    AND li.L_DISCOUNT > 0.05
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVG_REGION_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNAMELen,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'SHIP' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ShippedQuantity
FROM
    SUPPLIER
    JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, PART.P_NAME DESC

SELECT
    O_ORDERSTATUS,
    O_CUSTKEY,
    AVG(O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(L_QUANTITY),
    L_SHIPMODE,
    O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    O_CLERK,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_ORDERSTATUS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(O_CUSTKEY)),
    AVG(LENGTH(O_ORDERPRIORITY)),
    AVG(LENGTH(O_CLERK)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)),
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT))
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    O_ORDERSTATUS,
    O_CUSTKEY,
    O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    O_CLERK,
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    NATION.N_COMMENT AS NationComment,
    PART.P_COMMENT AS PartComment,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT AS CustomerComment,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT AS SupplierComment
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_MFGR,
    CASE
        WHEN P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN 'Manufacturer#4'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ManufacturerCategory,
    CASE
        WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#42' THEN 'Brand#42'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS BrandCategory,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_MFGR,
    P_BRAND,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierCommentsCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    o.O_ORDERKEY AS Order_Key,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE AS Total_Price,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS Extended_Price,
    li.L_QUANTITY As Quantity_Ordered
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * 1.2 -- Only orders where the part price in PART table is higher than 20% of the extended price in LINEITEM
AND
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Agricultural' -- Focussing on a specific market segment
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Region_Comment_Length
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) > 15

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    MAX(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS L_MAXAIRPRICE,
    MIN(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS L_MINAIRPRICE,
    MAX(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_TAX ELSE NULL END) AS L_MAXAIRTAX,
    MIN(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_TAX ELSE NULL END) AS L_MINAIRTAX
FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, CS.C_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PART P
JOIN PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER CS ON S.S_SUPPKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND CS.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgLengthPartName,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgLengthPartBrand,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthCustomerAddress,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLengthCustomerName,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomerCustKey,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSupplierName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthSupplierPhone,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthSupplierAddress
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS LINEITEM_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE >= DATE('2023-01-01') THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS RECENT_ITEMS_Variance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE < DATE('2023-01-01') THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS PREVIOUS_ITEMS_Total
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_COMMENT, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'ECONOMY BRUSHED TIN' THEN 'ECONOMY BRUSHED TIN' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY, ORDERS.O_CLERK, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN '1-URGENT' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SupplyingNation,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
  AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
  AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQty,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MKTSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneNumberLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS Refunded_Orders_Count,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F'
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#5' THEN 'Manufacturer#5' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)),
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PS_PARTKEY, N_NAME, S_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) ASC

SELECT 
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    li.l_extendedprice,
    li.l_suppkey AS SupplierKey,
    li.l_quantity
FROM 
    LINEITEM li
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON s.s_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
WHERE 
    n.n_regionkey = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)) -- Select the smallest regionkey's country
ORDER BY 
    n.n_name, c.c_name, li.l_extendedprice DESC, li.l_quantity ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_SIZE BETWEEN 1 AND 5)
    AND N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_SIZE As PartSize,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    CUST.C_MKTSEGMENT As MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
ORDER BY
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    CUST.C_MKTSEGMENT DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(PART.P_SIZE) AS TotalPartSize,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    FLOOR(PART.P_RETAILPRICE / 100) * 100

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthCus,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQty,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O' THEN 'O' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O' THEN 'O' ELSE 'Other' END

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS DISTINCT_PARTS_SUPPLIED,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILABILITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUST.C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    AVG(SUPL.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalValueofLineItems
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON N.N_NATIONKEY = CUST.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUPL ON CUST.C_CUSTKEY = SUPL.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON SUPL.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    P_TYPE,
    C_NAME,
    C_COMMENT,
    S_COMMENT,
    S_SUPPKEY,
    P_NAME,
    P_SIZE,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    C_ACCTBAL,
    N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
       SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity
