FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 1

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers,
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 0
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) > 0

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    NATION
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100
    AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNationality,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 'Machinery Segment'
        ELSE 'Other Segment'
    END AS MarketSegment
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'ELECTRONICS'
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS National_Market,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Balance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Supplier_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS Unique_Parts
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) > 50

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE REGION.R_NAME IN (SELECT R_NAME FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(N_NATIONKEY) FROM NATION)))
AND NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(N_NATIONKEY) FROM NATION))
ORDER BY LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AMERICA')
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShipMode,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShipmodeLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgLineItemTax,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    SUPPLIER
    JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    Supplier.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLYING_NATION,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVE_CUST_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVE_SUP_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUP_ACCT_BAL,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVE_AVAIL_QTY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME,
CASE
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AGRICULTURAL' THEN 'Agricultural'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'Building'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'CONSUMER_PK' THEN 'Consumer Pack'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HEAVY_BIKE' THEN 'Heavy Bikes'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HEAVY_CABIAGE' THEN 'Heavy Cabbages'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MITTENS' THEN 'Mittens'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'NOS_ACCOMP' THEN 'No-Sales Accessories'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SUB_COMBO' THEN 'Sub Combo'
  WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'TEA' THEN 'Tea'
  ELSE 'Other'
END AS C_MKTSEGMENT_CATEGORY,
AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal,
COUNT(*) AS TotalEntries
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'retail' THEN C.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS RetailCustomerAcctBal,
    SUM(CASE WHEN C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'wholesale' THEN C.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS WholesaleCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION N
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    o.O_COMMENT,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERDATE >= DATE('1998-01-01') AND o.O_ORDERDATE < DATE('2000-01-01') -- Orders placed between 1998 and 1999
    AND (c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' OR c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'OWNER') -- Customers from 'BUILDING' or 'OWNER' market segments
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN') -- Suppliers from Japan
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, o.O_ORDERKEY DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION CN ON C.C_NATIONKEY = CN.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR = 'ManufacturerX')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC, P.P_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierACCBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_COMMENT) AS NumDistinctSupplyComments,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplyCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY

SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       SUM(P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
       AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
       AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0

SELECT
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT l.l_suppkey) AS supplier_count,
    AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS avg_customer_balance
FROM
    LINEITEM l
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON l.l_partkey = c.c_custkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_nationkey, n.n_name
HAVING
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) > 100000
    AND AVG(c.c_acctbal) > 5000

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n_c.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME,
    n_s.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY -- Assuming CUSTOMER.C_PARTKEY references PART.P_PARTKEY (adjust if necessary)
JOIN
    NATION n_c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_c.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_s ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_s.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL AS C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY AS L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = 1 -- Assuming we're interested only in one nation (change 1 to the desired N_NATIONKEY)
ORDER BY
    L_ORDERKEY, L_LINENUMBER

SELECT AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Product_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Customer_Nation,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    l.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON p.P_PARTKEY = l.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NATION ON s.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME LIKE '%Europe%'
    AND l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 100
    AND l.L_QUANTITY > 50
ORDER BY
    l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_CUSTKEY,
    s.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    SUM(o.O_TOTALPRICE) AS TOTAL_ORDER_PRICE,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_LINE_ITEM_PRICE,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_BALANCE
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON n.N_NATIONKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(o.O_TOTALPRICE) > 100000
    AND AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50
    AND SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 200000

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    COUNT(li.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_SHIPMODE, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
HAVING 
    COUNT(li.L_ORDERKEY) > 1 AND AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.1

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalValue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY) AS NumOrders,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 10000

SELECT
    N.N_COMMENT,
    N.N_NAME,
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    R.R_NAME AS NATION_REGION,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_SUPPLIERS,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY, N.N_COMMENT, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName,
    N.N_NAME As NationName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
    AND R.R_NAME LIKE 'S%' -- Assuming 'S%' for simplification, adjust as necessary
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_RETAILPRICE > 100)
AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE '%%%')
AND R.R_NAME LIKE '%%Lat%'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_RETAILPRICE DESC, S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierBalance,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_TAX, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME LIKE '%%S%' AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' AND LINEITEM.L_TAX > 0
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT ASC, CUSTOMER.C_NAME DESC, LINEITEM.L_TAX DESC, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnQuantity,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, L_SHIPMODE

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName, -- Assuming S_NAME is a column in SUPPLIER table
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS O_ORDERPRIORITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY_SOLD,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_RETURNED_ITEMS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNTED_ITEMS
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 500
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) DESC,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), LINEITEM.L_TAX AS L_TAX FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_TAX

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND  
    p.P_SIZE IN (SELECT P_SIZE FROM PART GROUP BY P_SIZE HAVING COUNT(*) > 1)
ORDER BY 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgPartMFGRLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomersPerPart,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_SIZE,
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationAlbumBalance,
    R.R_NAME AS CustomerNationRegion,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscountedExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS AverageQuantity
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    n.n_name AS CustomerNationality,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS CustomerCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(li.l_extendedprice) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.l_quantity * li.l_discount) AS TotalDiscountAmount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) > 100 AND SUM(li.l_quantity * li.l_discount) > 10000

SELECT 
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.p_partkey) AS PartCount,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS TotalAccountBalance
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY 
    n.n_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.p_partkey) > 10
    AND SUM(c.c_acctbal) > 100000
    AND AVG(p.p_retailprice) > 50

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            PS2.PS_PARTKEY
        FROM
            PARTSUPP PS2
        WHERE
            PS2.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
    )
ORDER BY
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, C.C_NATIONKEY, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count, AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount, SUM(O.O_TOTALPRICE) AS Total_Order_Price
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SU ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = SU.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, C.C_NATIONKEY, C.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) > 1

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
        PART.P_PARTKEY,
        PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
        SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
        PART.P_TYPE,
        PART.P_BRAND,
        PART.P_SIZE,
        PART.P_NAME,
        PART.P_CONTAINER,
        PART.P_MFGR,
        PART.P_COMMENT,
        PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
        PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
        SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
        SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
        (PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST / PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS PRICE_RATIO
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PART.P_SIZE DESC

SELECT PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
  AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
  AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    O.O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_PARTKEY) AS NUM_DISTINCT_PARTS,
    AVG(LENGTH(O.O_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    O.O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS Avg_OrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS Avg_ClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) AS AvgOrderPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' AND
    li.L_TAX NOT BETWEEN 0.01 AND 0.05 AND
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(li2.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM LINEITEM li2 JOIN PART p2 ON li2.L_PARTKEY = p2.P_PARTKEY WHERE p2.P_TYPE = 'component')
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_COMMITDATE ASC, s.S_NAME DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    (SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT LIKE '%ECD%'))
    AND (LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' OR LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'F')
    AND (REGION.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME LIKE 'WEST%'))

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(CASE WHEN c.C_CUSTKEY IS NOT NULL THEN c.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN s.S_SUPPKEY IS NOT NULL AND s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY THEN s.S_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS SupplierToCustomerBalance,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY AND s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING 
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS C_Nation,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Supplier_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_LineItem_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_LineItem_ReturnFlagLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Distinct_Orders,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 THEN 'High'
        ELSE 'Low'
    END AS Price_Category
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 15 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 30 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 20

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) > 20 AND LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) > 20 AND LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) > 15
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCust,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthSupp,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgInstrLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'REG AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDiscountRegAir,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDiscountRail,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDiscountTruck
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 1
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, N.N_NAME ASC, R.R_NAME ASC, S.S_NAME ASC, C.C_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEG1' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS Total_SEG1_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_S_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_L_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Total_Orders,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AcctBal
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE < 10 THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_COMMENT) AS DistinctCommentsCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    PS_SupplyCost DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, N_NATIONKEY, AVG(C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY)
FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST, N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#3' THEN 'Manufacturer#3' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY = (SELECT S_NATIONKEY FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_NAME = 'Supplier-X')))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    c.C_PHONE
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTHERN')
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    s.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    PART.P_NAME AS Part,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    REGION.R_NAME As Region
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Total_Customers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Total_LineItems,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_L_Shipmode_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_L_LineStatus_Length
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS UniquePartCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers,
COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgLngthPName,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_MFGR)) AS AvgLngthP_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_COMMENT)) AS AvgLngthP_Comment,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgLngthC_Name,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLngthC_Address,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgLngthC_MarketSegment,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgPS_AvailQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
ORDER BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    r.R_NAME AS Region,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 0 AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 0

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > P.P_RETAILPRICE AND
    N.N_NAME = 'GUATEMALA'

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME) AS DistSupplierNamesCount,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal
FROM
    NATION
        INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
        INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME) > 5
    AND SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 1000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON C.C_CUSTKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    p.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_TYPE = 'Soft Drink'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'GERMANY')
    AND c.C_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'GERMANY')
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, p.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    r.R_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    p.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_Name,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 1000
AND 
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AMERICAS')
AND 
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY 
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatusLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_ReturnedItems,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SupplierPhoneLen
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLYCOST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVG_MARKET_SEGMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT) AS CustomerMarketSegmentCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineItemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemReturnFlagLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 10000
    AND AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 50000

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    SUPP.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    CUST.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    N2.N_NAME As Customer_Nation,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUPP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUPP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N2 ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = N2.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalPartAvailabilityQuantity,
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierBalance,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PART.P_SIZE < 5 AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME,
    C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 500
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    cu.C_NAME,
    su.S_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    su.S_ACCTBAL,
    cu.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER cu ON o.O_CUSTKEY = cu.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER su ON li.L_SUPPKEY = su.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > 50.00 AND
    su.S_ACCTBAL < cu.C_ACCTBAL AND
    p.P_SIZE IN (1, 2, 3) AND
    o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31'
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    cu.C_NAME ASC,
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NAME), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
AND P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR LIKE '(%mercury%)')
AND N_NAME LIKE 'NORTH%'
AND R_NAME LIKE 'AMERICA%'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, S_ACCTBAL DESC, P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    MAX(L_SHIPMODE) AS MostPreferredShippingMode,
    MIN(L_DISCOUNT) AS MinimumDiscount
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    COUNT(PS.PS_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILABILITY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(N.N_NAME)) AS AVG_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(S.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_COMMENT) AS NumDistinctPartSuppComments
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME As SupplierName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgPContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVGPReviewPrice,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NationKey,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP,
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_RETAILPRICE > 100)
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P_SIZE ASC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 0
    AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_C_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_C_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_S_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS SUM_F_L_QUANTITY,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS SUM_O_L_QUANTITY,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME,
    MAX(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS MAX_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(SUP.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUP_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_TYPE) AS DIFFERENT_PART_TYPES,
    SUM(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TOTAL_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON C.C_CUSTKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05 AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 10000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
AND PART.P_SIZE > 50
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT 
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUP.S_SUPPKEY,
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    R.R_REGIONKEY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE '%Silver%')

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustCommentLength, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBal,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddrLength, SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 100000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 5

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION))
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    li.L_DISCOUNT ASC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC,
    n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    L.L_DISCOUNT,
    L.L_QUANTITY,
    L.L_SHIPDATE,
    L.L_RETURNFLAG,
    R.R_REGIONKEY
FROM
    LINEITEM L
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    L.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' -- Assuming 'A' indicates a returned item, modify if necessary
    AND L.L_DISCOUNT > 0.10 -- Only consider discounts greater than 10%
    AND L.L_SHIPDATE > '2000-01-01' -- Choose any date to filter shipment dates, adjust as needed
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY, C.C_CUSTKEY, S.S_SUPPKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    PS_SUPPKEY AS SupplierKey,
    N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey,
    PS_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    R_NAME AS RegionName,
    N_COMMENT AS NationComment,
    R_COMMENT AS RegionComment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PS.PS_PARTKEY AS PartKey,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, PS.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) AS Revenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(li.l_quantity) AS AvgQuantity,
    MAX(li.l_extendedprice) AS MaxPrice
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * (1 - li.l_discount)) > 1000000

SELECT
        PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
        NATION.N_NAME,
        NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
        CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
        CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
        SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
        REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
        ABS(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY - (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)) AS AVG_AVAIL_DIFF
FROM
        PARTSUPP,
        NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
        CUSTOMER,
        SUPPLIER
WHERE
        CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
        AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
        NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
        CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
        ABS(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY - (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)) DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 0.5 * (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT
