    AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgPSCommentLength,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), PART.P_TYPE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 500
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, PART.P_TYPE DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART p ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME, r.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING 
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PART.P_TYPE = 'JZ' -- Assuming 'JZ' is a specific part type
AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN ('ABS', 'FURNITURE') -- Assuming 'ABS' and 'FURNITURE' are specific market segments
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'MAICH') -- Assuming 'MAICH' is the nation name
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31'
AND
    s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSuppAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSuppPhoneLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShipMode,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderCount
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
HAVING
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
    AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME DESC, AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgLengthNationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSupplierName,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgLengthRegionName,
    SUM(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 100 THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE 0 END) AS HighQtySupplyCostSum,
    SUM(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY <= 100 THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE 0 END) AS LowQtySupplyCostSum
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM
    LINEITEM Li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = 3)
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND Li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength
FROM NATION N, CUSTOMER C
WHERE N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT)) > 50
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(C.C_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NATION ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON P.P_PARTKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME IN ('Nation1', 'Nation2') -- replace with actual nation names or keys
    AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    CUST.C_NAME ASC,
    SUP.S_NAME ASC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_SIZE > 10) -- Example condition, replace as needed
AND
    N.N_NAME LIKE '...' -- Example condition for NATION_NAME, replace '...' with desired pattern
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    C.C_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    o.O_CUSTKEY,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_ORDER_VALUE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_PARTKEY) AS NUM_UNIQUE_PARTS,
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    o.O_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    CASE
        WHEN o.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN 'Urgent'
        WHEN o.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2-HIGH' THEN 'High'
        ELSE 'Normal'
    END AS ORDER_PRIORITY_LEVEL
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE, o.O_CUSTKEY, o.O_ORDERSTATUS, o.O_ORDERKEY, o.O_TOTALPRICE, o.O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CASE WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'MED PKG' THEN 'MED PKG' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, ORDERS.O_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Addr_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_AcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_S_Comment_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_S_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_S_Addr_Length,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    CUSTOMER
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, C_MKTSEGMENT, S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, REGION.R_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, NATION.N_COMMENT ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS LateMostReceiptDate,
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS EarliestReceiptDate
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT 
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY -- assuming a many-to-one relationship between PART and NATION
JOIN 
    CUSTOMer C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY -- assuming a many-to-one relationship between PART and CUSTOMER
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- assuming a many-to-one relationship between CUSTOMER and SUPPLIER
WHERE 
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = 3) -- assuming a specific region identifier (here 3)
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineitemShipModeLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgLineitemTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgLineitemExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineitemDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineitemCommentLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS QuantBooksReturned,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS QuantBooksRefunded,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgLineitemQuantity
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PART P
JOIN PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Some Region')) AND S_ACCTBAL > 100000 AND PS_AVAILQTY > 0

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL ANODIZED TIN' THEN 'SMALL ANODIZED TIN'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS P_TYPE_Category,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 'MACHINERY'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MKT_Segment_Category,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
        ELSE 'Not Returned'
    END AS Return_Status,
    L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Returned'
        ELSE 'Not Returned'
    END

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000
ORDER BY
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    s.S_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS Supplier_Total_Balance,
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_MKTSEGMENT, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM 
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN 
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION AS N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY -- assuming part-region relationship
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER AS C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY -- assuming nation-customer relationship
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER AS S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- assuming customer-supplier relationship
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, N.N_NAME ASC, C.C_NAME ASC, S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnedItemCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DiscountedItemCount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Air freight'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR REGULAR' THEN 'Air regular'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'FALL TRUCK' THEN 'Fall truck'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'MAIL' THEN 'Mail'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN 'Ship'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'TRANSPORT OVERSEAS' THEN 'Transport overseas'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS SHIPPING_MODE_CATEGORY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME = 'UNITED KINGDOM'

SELECT P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PART P
JOIN PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, C_ACCTBAL DESC, S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Returned_Lines,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE LIKE '%SEA%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Sea_Shipping_Lines
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_COMMENT,
    LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) AS NNameLength,
    LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) AS SNameLength,
    LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME) AS RNameLength,
    LENGTH(PART.P_NAME) AS PNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_BRAND AS Brand,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'ROD'
    AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeys,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS Avg_ContainerLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS Avg_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS Avg_BrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(CASE WHEN c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY THEN l.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalQuantityShippedFromNation,
    AVG(CASE WHEN c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY THEN l.L_DISCOUNT ELSE NULL END) AS AverageDiscountForSupplierInNation,
    AVG(CASE WHEN s.S_SUPPKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY THEN s.S_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AverageSupplierAccountBalanceInNation
FROM
    REGION r
JOIN
    NATION n ON r.R_REGIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    r.R_NAME, n.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ADDRESS
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION N WHERE N.N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS Avg_Part_Type_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Customer_Phone_Length,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_AcctBal,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS Avg_LineItem_Tax,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS Distinct_OrderKeys_Count,
    AVG(L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_LineItem_Quantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS Avg_LineItem_ShipInstr_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_LineItem_Comment_Length,
    P_RETAILPRICE AS Part_RetailPrice
FROM
    PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    L_TAX

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE As Order_TotalPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_QUANTITY As Quantity_Ordered,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY AS Total_ExtendedPrice
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
ORDER BY
    p.P_PARTKEY, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, c.C_CUSTKEY, li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_C_ADDR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_S_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVERAGE_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVERAGE_L_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TOTAL_ORDERS,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT_RATE
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLengthC,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthS,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTaxPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscounts
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    n_reg.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    n_cus.N_NAME AS Customer_Nation,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_reg ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_reg.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_cus ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_cus.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemSHIPMODELength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgLineItemDiscount,
    C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX)

SELECT
    c.C_NATIONKEY,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_REVENUE,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NATIONKEY, c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_QUANTITY) > 10000

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS Avg_C_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_C_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_S_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_S_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_L_Shipmode_Length,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS Avg_L_Tax,
    L_LINESTATUS AS L_LineStatus,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_PARTKEY) AS Distinct_L_PartKey_Count
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, L_LINESTATUS

SELECT PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AVERAGE_TAX,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAcctBal
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000
ORDER BY
    N_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustAddrLen,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CustAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SuppNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SuppAddrLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SuppPhoneLen,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSuppComments,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NationName
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, N_NAME

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE
FROM PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PART.P_MFGR IN (SELECT P_MFGR FROM PART GROUP BY P_MFGR HAVING COUNT(*) > 1)
AND PART.P_TYPE = 'WIRE'
AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD'
ORDER BY PART.P_SIZE DESC, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP PS)
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME DESC, R.R_NAME ASC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE))

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartCount,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AveragePartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgLengthContainer,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthAddress,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthComment,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS NumParts
FROM
    PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_SIZE

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C.C_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS Extended_Price,
    li.L_SHIPDATE AS Shipping_Date,
    li.L_DISCOUNT AS Discount_Rate,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON n.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' -- Filtering for returned items
ORDER BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, -- By order date in descending order
    n.N_NAME ASC -- Then by nation name in ascending order

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'SOME_NATION_NAME') -- replace 'SOME_NATION_NAME' with actual nation name to filter
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'COMBANI_SILVER') -- example filter condition
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_NameStatusLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) AS LatestReceivDate
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))
FROM NATION, SUPPLIER
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 5
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_NAME FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME AS PartName, SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName, N.N_NAME As NationName, R.R_NAME As RegionName, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND P.P_SIZE BETWEEN 10 AND 50
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME IN ('FRANCE', 'ITALY', 'SPAIN'))
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, Li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT C_CUSTKEY AS customer_key, N_NAME AS nation_name, S_NAME AS supplier_name, C_MKTSEGMENT AS market_segment, S_ADDRESS AS supplier_address
FROM CUSTOMER C
JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
  CASE
    WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1
    WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 2
    ELSE 3
  END,
  CASE
    WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 1
    WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'ETC' THEN 2
    ELSE 3
  END,
  S_ADDRESS ASC,
  C_CUSTKEY DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    Av.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    PART
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN (
    SELECT L_PARTKEY, AVG(L_QUANTITY) AS L_QUANTITY
    FROM LINEITEM
    GROUP BY L_PARTKEY
) Av ON PART.P_PARTKEY = Av.L_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    PART.P_TYPE = 'Component'
    AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUSINESS_CUSTOMER'
    AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_SIZE) DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG IN ('A', 'F') -- Returning lines with Acknowledged (A) or Fulfilled (F) status
ORDER BY REGION.R_NAME, (LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE) ASC

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY -- S_SUPPKEY is a reference to C_CUSTKEY, not directly to NATION
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOME_Desired_REGION_NAME')
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NATIONKEY, S.S_SUPPKEY, Li.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME AS NationName, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, ps.PS_AVAILQTY, c.C_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP ps
JOIN PART p ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER c ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(ps2.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP ps2)
AND n.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT r.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION r WHERE r.R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
ORDER BY ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, p.P_NAME

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_TAX,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost, NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN C_CUSTKEY END) AS HouseholdCustomerCount, COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS TotalCustomerCount, AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN NATION ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS))

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN ('AUTOMOBILE', 'HOUSEHOLD')
ORDER BY 
    CASE 
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NATION_NAME_LENGTH,
 AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
 AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
 NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
 COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DISTINCT_CUSTOMERS_COUNT,
 MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS MAX_SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY
HAVING SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 20 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10
ORDER BY SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NATIONKEY,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    R_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PS_PARTKEY, N_NATIONKEY, P_RETAILPRICE, R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(C_ACCTBAL) DESC, P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    supp.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    c.C_ACCTBAL AS CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER supp ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = supp.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON supp.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(ABS(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE - LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD' AND PART.P_BRAND = 'BrandX' THEN 'BrandX Standard'
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD' THEN 'Other Standard'
        ELSE 'Non-Standard'
    END AS TypeBrandCategory,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD' THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    PART.P_CONTAINER ASC

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_COMMENT, O.O_ORDERSTATUS, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_LINENUMBER, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_DISCOUNT
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' AND L.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, O.O_ORDERKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME,
CASE
    WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BABIES' THEN 'BABIES'
    WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'COURSE_CATS' THEN 'COURSE_CATS'
    WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Électronique' THEN 'ÉLECTRONICS'
    ELSE 'Other'
END AS C_MKTSEGMENT_DATE,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 'FURNITURE' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F' ELSE 'Other' END, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    c.C_CUSTKEY,
    s.S_SUPPKEY,
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    SUM(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) / COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS AvgPricePerCustomer
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_PARTKEY, c.C_CUSTKEY, s.S_SUPPKEY
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 10

SELECT O_CLERK, L_SHIPMODE, AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(O_TOTALPRICE), L_SHIPDATE
FROM ORDERS, LINEITEM
WHERE LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_CLERK, L_SHIPMODE, L_SHIPDATE, MONTH(L_COMMITDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(O_TOTALPRICE) DESC, L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM CUSTOMER
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION AS SUPPLIERNATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIERNATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
       N_REGION.R_REGIONKEY,
       R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN REGION AS N_REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = N_REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY N_REGION.R_REGIONKEY, R_NAME

SELECT
ORDERs.O_ORDERDATE,
CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVERAGE_EXTENDED_PRICE,
COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDERS,
CASE
    WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'I' THEN 'In Progress'
    WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'D' THEN 'Delivered'
    WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'C' THEN 'Cancelled'
    ELSE 'Unknown'
END AS ORDER_STATUS_TYPE,
SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
CUSTOMER.C_NAME
FROM ORDERS
JOIN CUSTOMER ON ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME = 'desired_nation_name'
AND S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
AND P_TYPE = (SELECT DISTINCT P_TYPE FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'desired_part_type%')

SELECT N.N_NAME AS Supplier_Country, S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name, S.S_ADDRESS AS Supplier_Address, S.S_PHONE As Supplier_Phone, LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LI.L_DISCOUNT, LI.L_QUANTITY
FROM NATION N
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE R.R_NAME IN (SELECT R_NAME FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT S_NATIONKEY FROM SUPPLIER)))

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUS.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER CUS ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = CUS.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVERAGE_SHIPMODE_LEN,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_TAX ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_TAX_WITH_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT <= 0 THEN LINEITEM.L_TAX ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_TAX_WITHOUT_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LEN,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE_F,
    AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'S' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) AS AVG_EXTENDEDPRICE_S
FROM
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND PART.P_SIZE > 50
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL < -1000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) DESC

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PS_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthPS,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthC,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLengthS,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthS,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBalS,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 -- Filtering parts with total available quantity greater than 1000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N_C.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_C.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    N_C.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AVERAGE_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS RETURNED_ORDER_COUNT,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS RETURNED_QUANTITY_SUM,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE'))
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, ps.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT, S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    P_NAME AS PartName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    R_COMMENT As RegionComment,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND
    P_RETAILPRICE > 50.0
AND
    S_ACCTBAL < 1000000
ORDER BY
    N_NAME ASC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    REGION.R_COMMENT NULLS FIRST

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_SIZE AS Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice,
    P.P_TYPE AS Type,
    P.P_BRAND AS Brand,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_SIZE > 10 AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 50
ORDER BY
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    N.N_NAME DESC,
    P.P_TYPE ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE '%Silver%')
    AND N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICAA')
    AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000.00
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC NULLS FIRST,
    P_NAME DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS ORDER_DATE,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON c.C_CUSTKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
    AND li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
    AND li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    p.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS PartRetailPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_TYPE = 'CAMERA'
