    AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_NATION_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY / PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgQuantityPerSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY, PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_S_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierAvgAccountBalance,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS OrderAveragePrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LI.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LI.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnedQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LI.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnOrderCount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT 
    n.n_name AS NationName, 
    r.r_name AS RegionName, 
    c.c_name AS CustomerName, 
    s.s_name AS SupplierName, 
    li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity AS TotalPrice, 
    li.l_shipmode
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
WHERE 
    r.r_regionkey IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTHEAST ASIA')
    AND li.l_extendedprice > 1000
    AND li.l_shipmode IN ('AIR', 'SORT')
    AND s.s_acctbal > 50000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumOfCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumOfSuppliers,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY, P_SIZE, P_RETAILPRICE, C_NATIONKEY, N_NAME, S_NAME, S_PHONE
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PART.P_SIZE > 5 AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 1000 AND SUPPLIER.S_PHONE LIKE '%123%'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 100000)
    AND N.N_NAME = 'Part partional'

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND PART.P_SIZE < 50
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 500000
AND REGION.R_NAME LIKE '%' || 'Asia%'
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
    AND R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_REGIONKEY
    AND C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    S.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    LI.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    p.P_NAME,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY AND c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, p.P_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000 AND AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) < 5000

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_COST,
    N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_COMMENT) AS UNIQUE_SUPPLIER_COMMENTS,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH_REGION
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON O.O_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) > 100 AND
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000 AND
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CS.S_ACCTBAL,
    C.C_NAME,
    COUNT(PS.PS_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER CS ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = CS.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CS.S_ACCTBAL,
    C.C_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(PS.PS_SUPPKEY) > 1
    AND AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT NATION.N_NATIONKEY)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    S_ACCTBAL,
    N_REGIONKEY,
    R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    N_NAME ASC,
    C_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    O.O_ORDERPRIORITY AS OrderPriority,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalValue,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierNation
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON O.O_CUSTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, O.O_ORDERPRIORITY, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 10000
    AND AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY = 2 -- Assuming we're interested in a specific nation with N_NATIONKEY = 2
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, n.N_NATIONKEY, c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, SUP.S_NAME, SUP.S_ACCTBAL, N.N_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE SUP.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
AND N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA')
ORDER BY SUP.S_ACCTBAL DESC, P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthSupplierComment,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgLengthSuppAddress,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLengthLineItemStatus
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerBalance,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'BUILDING'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'CONSUMER_PACK' THEN 'CONSUMER_PACK'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HEALTH' THEN 'HEALTH'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Landscaping' THEN 'Landscaping'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ASC, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    L.L_LINENUMBER,
    L.L_ORDERKEY,
    L.L_RETURNFLAG,
    L.L_PARTKEY,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    L.L_SHIPMODE,
    L.L_COMMITDATE,
    L.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    L.L_QUANTITY,
    L.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN ('FRANCE', 'GERMANY')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    L.L_LINENUMBER DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS HomeNation,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerBalance,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    MIN(PS_AVAILQTY) AS MinimumAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 500
    AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, C.C_NAME, AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY), S.S_NAME, S.S_ADDRESS
FROM PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, P.P_TYPE, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, S.S_ADDRESS
ORDER BY AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
FROM PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) DESC, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) DESC

SELECT 
    c.C_CUSTKEY,
    c.C_NAME,
    c.C_PHONE,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    s.S_SUPPKEY,
    s.S_NAME,
    s.S_PHONE,
    s.S_ACCTBAL,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' 
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PERU')
    AND li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY 
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ASC,
    s.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe')
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ASC,
    PART.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CS.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CS.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SV.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CS ON P.P_PARTKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SV ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SV.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CS.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME, CS.C_NAME, CS.C_MKTSEGMENT, SV.S_NAME
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_COMMENT LIKE '%developed%')
AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
AND LINEITEM.L_COMMENT NOT LIKE '%defect%'
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, NATION.N_COMMENT, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, NATION.N_COMMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region,
    COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPplier.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 5 AND
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 1000

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    SUM(CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 10 THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS HighSizePrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE <= 10 AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 1000 THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS LowAcctBalHighRetPrice
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT'
    AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'GERMANY')
    AND li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_NATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength_SUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrders
FROM
    NATION,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQty
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, c.C_NAME
HAVING 
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY 
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    p.p_name,
    n.n_name AS supplier_nation_name,
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supplycost,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_qty
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    p.p_name,
    n.n_name
HAVING
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) > 1000
    AND SUM(ps.ps_availqty) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    s.S_ACCTBAL,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(p2.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART p2)
ORDER BY
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    s.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 50 AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION CN ON C.C_NATIONKEY = CN.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND
    N.N_NAME NOT IN ('NationX', 'NationY') -- replace 'NationX' and 'NationY' with actual nation names
AND
    CN.N_NAME NOT IN ('NationX', 'NationY') -- replace 'NationX' and 'NationY' with actual nation names
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    CUS.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUS.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUS ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = CUS.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON CUS.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS2.PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP PS2 WHERE PS2.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 100)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    SUP.S_NAME ASC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    CUS.C_NAME ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    R.R_NAME ASC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS L_RECEIPTDATE FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_CUSTKEY, O.O_TOTALPRICE, L.L_PARTKEY, L.L_QUANTITY, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, L.L_DISCOUNT
FROM ORDERS O
INNER JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE O.O_ORDERSTATUS LIKE '%Shipped%'
AND L.L_SHIPDATE IS NOT NULL
AND L.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE '%R%'
ORDER BY O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, L.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 50 AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MKTSegmentLength,
    S_ADDRESS,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SAddressLength,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_LShipModeLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Distinct_LExtendedPriceCount,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS Avg_L_TAX,
    L_COMMITDATE
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_ADDRESS,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    L_COMMITDATE

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '4-NOT SPECIFIED' THEN '4-NOT SPECIFIED' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 'O' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) + LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) / 3 AS AVG_STRING_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
           CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN 'HOUSEHOLD' ELSE 'Other' END AS SEGMENT,
           SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
           MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS MAX_AVAILABILITY,
           AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS_COMMENT,
    N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    COALESCE(P_BRAND, 'No Brand') AS PART_BRAND,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS CUSTOMER_SEGMENT,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    PS_AVAILQTY AS PART_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY -- erroneous, should be SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.05

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MaxRetailPrice,
    MIN(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS MinRetailPrice,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS UniqueSuppliers
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 1
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 1

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
  AVG(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_Fulfilled_Orders,
  AVG(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_Awaiting_Fulfillment_Orders,
  AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
  AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
  AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatus_Length,
  AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Avg_Orders_Shipped_Via_Air,
  AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE NULL END) / AVG(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END) AS Avg_ExtPrice_For_Air_Shipments
FROM
  ORDERS O,
  SUPPLIER S,
  LINEITEM L
WHERE
  O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
  AND S.S_SUPPKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
  AND L.L_ORDERKEY = O.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
  O_CUSTKEY,
  S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N.N_NAME FROM NATION N WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION R WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA'))
    AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
    AND PS_AVAILQTY > 100

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationalOrigin,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalLineItemQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    O_SHIPPRIORITY,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnFlagA,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'N' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnFlagN,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    SUM(O_TOTALPRICE) AS TotalOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrders
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME AS P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT AS PS_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT AS C_COMMENT,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL AS C_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    ABS(LENGTH(C_NAME) - LENGTH(P_NAME)),
    C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBRANDLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMktSegmentLen, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NAME) AS SupplierCount, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 5
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgLengthNationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthSupplierComment,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailabilityQuantity,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) > 20
ORDER BY
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) DESC,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Country,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AS CustomerKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX AS SalesTax,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As ExtendedPrice,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'F' THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ReturnStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_PART_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 10 THEN PART.P_PARTKEY END) AS PARTS_WITH_LARGE_SIZE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 50000 THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS CUSTOMERS_WITH_HIGH_BALANCE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AND
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY AND
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER))
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
    AND SUP.S_ACCTBAL > 5000
    AND P.P_NAME LIKE '%Silver%'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    SUP.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    L_QUANTITY,
    SUM(L_TAX) AS TotalTax,
    SUM(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount
FROM
    SUPPLIER
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY, L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AFRICA')
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
    AND P.P_RETAILPRICE > 50
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_C_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_C_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_S_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Fulfilled_Orders,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_LINENUMBER > 10 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Total_Orders_With_More_Than_10_Lines
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, P_NAME, P_TYPE, N_NAME, R_NAME, S_NAME, PS_AVAILQTY, PS_SUPPLYCOST, S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS Supplier_Country,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Balance,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_Extended_Price,
AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_Return_Flag_Length,
SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped,
SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS Supplier_NationKey
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_SIZE > 10 AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN') AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    P_MFGR,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n_n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    cn.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION cn ON c.C_NATIONKEY = cn.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLLinestatusLength,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLCommentLength,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS ShipInstruction
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SomePreferredRegion')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_QUANTITY ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
FROM PART
JOIN ORDERS ON PART.P_PARTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'A' -- Only consider Completed Orders
ORDER BY ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthC_PHONE,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgLengthC_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthS_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLengthL_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
PART.P_NAME,
PART.P_TYPE,
PART.P_BRAND,
SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
NATION.N_NAME,
PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_RETAILPRICE, P_SIZE, P_TYPE
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 50 AND P_SIZE > 10
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_RETAILPRICE, P_SIZE, P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(*) > 1

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_Length_L_RETURNFLAG,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM
    NATION N
    JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
    AND Li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
    AND Li.L_SHIPDATE > '2000-01-01'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_SIZE,
    AVG(CASE WHEN P_TYPE LIKE '%Electronic%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgElectronicPartSize,
    AVG(CASE WHEN P_TYPE LIKE '%Mechanical%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgMechanicalPartSize,
    AVG(CASE WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = ' segment_A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgSegmentASupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(CASE WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = ' segment_B' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgSegmentBSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQuantity
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Average_Supply_Cost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Total_Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME AS R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 5000
ORDER BY NATION.N_REGIONKEY, S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    P_PARTKEY,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_SUPPKEY,
    SUPLI.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUPLI.S_ADDRESS,
    SUPLI.S_PHONE,
    NAT.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    REG.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUPLI ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPLI.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION NAT ON SUPLI.S_NATIONKEY = NAT.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION REG ON NAT.N_REGIONKEY = REG.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    SUPLI.S_NAME ASC,
    NAT.N_NAME ASC,
    REG.R_NAME ASC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_SUPPLIERS,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTNAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    Customer.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_MFGR AS PartMFGR,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE')

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AvgCPhoneLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustCount
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_MFGR, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
ORDER BY 
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerHomeCountry,
    SUM(CASE WHEN C.C_MktSegment = 'TYPE1' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Type1Count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN C.C_MktSegment = 'TYPE2' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Type2Count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN C.C_MktSegment = 'TYPE3' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Type3Count,
    AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * L_QUANTITY) AS TotalRevenue,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON C.C_CUSTKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_NAME, P_TYPE, C_MKTSEGMENT, S_NATIONKEY, S_ADDRESS
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND P_SIZE BETWEEN 1 AND 10
AND S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'NATION_NAME')
AND C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MKTSEGMENT_NAME'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Customer_Account_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Account_Balance
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, AVG(LENGTH(N_NAME)) AS AvgLengthNationName, AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS AvgLengthSupplierPhone, AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AvgLengthRegionName, AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthSupplierComment
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
    JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrdersCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstrLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_TYPE IN ('STANDARD POLISHED STEEL', 'SPECIALTY FINISHED')
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ARGENTINA')
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 5

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUST_COUNT,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT_A' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS AMOUNT_SEGMENT_A,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT_B' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS AMOUNT_SEGMENT_B,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_LEN_NATION_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_LEN_REGION_NAME
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN ('BUILDING', 'HOUSEHOLD')
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > 150
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 15
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 5

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_PARTKEY) AS UniquePartKeysShipped,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_SUPPKEY) AS UniqueSupplierKeys
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, LINEITEM.L_TAX DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    PART.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS Unique_Parts,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_Retail_Price,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Account_Balance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 10

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    REGION.R_NAME
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))
AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT S_NATIONKEY FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER))
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT ASC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_SIZE > (SELECT AVG(P_SIZE) FROM PART)
    AND p.P_RETAILPRICE < (SELECT MAX(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
ORDER BY
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    p.P_SIZE ASC,
    n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    C.C_NAME ASC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    MAX(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) DESC

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_COMMENT AS Order_Comment,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    r.R_REGIONKEY,
    s.S_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
