LEFT JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_SIZE > 50 AND p.P_RETAILPRICE < 100 AND n.N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES'
ORDER BY 
    n.N_NAME DESC, p.P_RETAILPRICE ASC, s.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, Li.L_SHIPMODE, Li.L_RECEIPTDATE
SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY)

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION)
AND PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY <= (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance, AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 100 AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) > 10

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLinegetItemLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Air Shipment'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR REGISTER' THEN 'Air Registered'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN 'Rail Shipment'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'TRUCK' THEN 'Truck Shipment'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'MAIL' THEN 'Postal Mail'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN 'Sea Freight'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS ShipMode
FROM
    NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT),
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(PS_AVAILQTY), SUM(P_RETAILPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT MAX(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION GROUP BY N_REGIONKEY)
AND REGION.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION GROUP BY R_REGIONKEY)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME DESC, REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > 1000)
    AND N.N_NAME LIKE '%%Europe%%'
    AND C.C_ACCTBAL > 5000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER) + LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE) + LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPartDescriptionLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerInfoLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierInfoLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSupplierCount
FROM
    PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    Li.L_ORDERKEY,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_RETURNFLAG,
    Li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN ('JAPAN', 'GERMANY')
    AND Li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY, C.C_CUSTKEY DESC, Li.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)) -- assuming a REGION table with R_REGIONKEY as smallest value
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC, LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) DESC

SELECT O_CUSTKEY, O_ORDERDATE, O_ORDERPRIORITY, AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE), L_COMMITDATE, MONTH(L_COMMITDATE), COUNT(L_ORDERKEY)
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_CUSTKEY, O_ORDERDATE, O_ORDERPRIORITY, L_COMMITDATE, MONTH(L_COMMITDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, MONTH(L_COMMITDATE) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_COMMENT, PART.P_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, NATION.N_COMMENT ASC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC, REGION.R_COMMENT DESC, PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ShippedOrders,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HighBalSuppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgLineItemCommentLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AS S_SUPPKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS MaxExtendedPrice,
    AVG(li.L_QUANTITY) AS AverageQuantityShipped,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrdersShipped
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN 'Manufacturer#4' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_CLERK, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, 
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName, 
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty, 
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance, 
    LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) AS NationNameLength, 
    LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) AS CustomerNameLength, 
    LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) AS SupplierNameLength
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, 
    NATION.N_NAME, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME, 
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NUM_RETURNABLE_ITEMS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NUM_NON_RETURNABLE_ITEMS,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS TOTAL_TAX,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS Distinct_Customers,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS Distinct_Suppliers,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000 AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 50 AND AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 2000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerSegment, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice, COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS UniqueOrders, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY END) AS OrdersWithReturn
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'R' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000)

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    C.C_NATIONKEY AS Customer_NationKey,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Average_SupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Total_AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 500

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 500
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_COST,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABILITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 20
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX)

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_TYPE) ASC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS NumCustomersWithPositiveBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL END) AS SupplierTotalACCTBAL_withPosCustomerBalance
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))
    AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME,
       NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
       SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
       AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND
    P.P_CONTAINER LIKE '%Metal%' AND
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' AND
    S.S_ACCTBAL > 50000

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_ADDRESS AS SUPPLIER_ADDRESS,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR LIKE 'MFGR%100')
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_BRAND AS PartBrand
FROM 
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN 
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_TYPE = 'Component' AND
    S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'UNITED STATES') AND
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CustBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_SupplierBal,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    L_RECEIPTDATE AS ReceiptDate,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderKeys
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    n_n.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    n_c.N_NAME As Customer_Nation_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST As Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY As Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_c.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumOfCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumOfSuppliers,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS ORDER_DATE,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS AS ORDER_STATUS,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS LINE_ITEM_EXTENDED_PRICE,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    L.L_SHIPMODE AS SHIPPING_MODE
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' AND L.L_SHIPDATE > '2023-01-01'
ORDER BY
    C.C_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, S.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS ProductName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    P.P_TYPE AS ProductType
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_RETAILPRICE > 50
    AND N.N_NAME LIKE 'Backward%'
    AND R.R_NAME LIKE '%Asia%'
ORDER BY
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPKEY, SUP.S_NAME, SUP.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME = 'some_specific_nation_name' AND SUP.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY PS.PS_PARTKEY, SUP.S_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS Avg_PartNameLength,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT, S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    Su.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME As NationName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER Su ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON Su.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_SIZE > 10 AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 500 AND N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Country,
    PART.P_NAME AS P_Part,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_Retail_Price,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Balance,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Length_Customer_Name,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Length_Supplier_Name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_CONTAINER) AS Distinct_Containers,
    PART.P_TYPE AS Part_Type
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY -- assuming suppliers share nation with customers
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    li.L_DISCOUNT AS DiscountAmount
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NAME = 'PERU' -- Example: filter for customers in Peru
    AND li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (p.P_RETAILPRICE * 1.2) -- Example: show items where extended price exceeds 20% of retail
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    n.n_name,
    c.c_mktsegment,
    s.s_name,
    AVG(li.l_quantity) AS avg_quantity,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_discount) AS total_discounted_revenue
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.s_suppkey = c.c_custkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name,
    c.c_mktsegment,
    s.s_name
HAVING
    AVG(li.l_quantity) > 50 OR SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_discount) > 100000

SELECT P_MFGR, C_MKTSEGMENT, AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AvgCnameLen, AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSacctbal, SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity, AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLshipmodeLen
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY P_MFGR, C_MKTSEGMENT, L_DISCOUNT

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LL.L_TAX,
    LL.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LL ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LL.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    LL.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' -- Assuming 'A' indicates a returned item, adjust as necessary
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, R.R_NAME

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    R.R_NAME LIKE ' %{region_pattern}% '
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'VARIOUS PROPERTIES')
    AND Li.L_LINENUMBER BETWEEN 1 AND 100
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'SOME_NATION_NAME') -- replace 'SOME_NATION_NAME' with the actual nation name
ORDER BY
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, Li.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT
    N_NAME AS NationName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 500

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_SIZE As PartSize,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity,
    S.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY -- Assuming PART table has N_NATIONKEY to link with NATION table
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION NC ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NC.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAIL_QTY,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS PART_RETAILPRICE,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, p.P_NAME, p.P_TYPE, p.P_RETAILPRICE, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST, n.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, p.P_NAME, p.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Supplier_Balance,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Average_Customer_Balance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) DESC, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) ASC, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'WRAP PKG' THEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE * PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST / PART.P_SIZE
        ELSE PART.P_RETAILPRICE * PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST / PART.P_SIZE * 1.1 -- 10% higher cost for non-WRAP PKG
    END AS ADJUSTED_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_CONTAINER IN ('WRAP PKG', 'OTHER')
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'WRAP PKG' THEN PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
        ELSE PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST * 1.1 -- sort non-WRAP PKG items higher
    END DESC,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT
    p.p_name,
    s.s_name,
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS avg_supplycost,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_availqty,
    AVG(LENGTH(ps.ps_comment)) AS avg_comment_length,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS supplier_total_acctbal
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
GROUP BY
    p.p_name,
    s.s_name,
    s.s_nationkey
HAVING
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) > 500 AND SUM(s.s_acctbal) > 10000

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierCountryName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND    S.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
AND    C.C_ACCTBAL < 50000
AND    N.N_NAME NOT IN ('Antarctica')

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) DESC

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS PartsAvailable,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY = 0 THEN PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY END) AS PartsUnavailable
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_PARTKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM 
    NATION
JOIN 
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 0

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    L_SHIPMODE AS ShipMode,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthRegion,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST * PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) as TotalSupplyCostWithQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY As RegionKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY PART.P_BRAND

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT AS L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_DISCOUNT

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F' ELSE 'Other' END AS LineStatusCategory
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * (1 - LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)) AS Total_Revenue
FROM 
    PART
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING 
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_TYPE, P.P_RETAILPRICE, C.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PART P, CUSTOMER C
WHERE P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
AND P.P_BRAND IN (SELECT P_BRAND FROM PART GROUP BY P_BRAND HAVING COUNT(*) > 1)
AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT IN (SELECT C_MKTSEGMENT FROM CUSTOMER GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT HAVING COUNT(*) > 5)
ORDER BY P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, C.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_BRAND IN ('Brand#35', 'Brand#72') AND
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' AND
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT))
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPKEY, N_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME, PS_AVAILQTY, PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT N_REGIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ANTARCTICA'))
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Agricultural' THEN 'Agricultural'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Build' THEN 'Construction'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Wholesaler' THEN 'Wholesaler'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    CASE
        WHEN SUPPLIER.S_PHONE LIKE '%1%' THEN 'Supplier has area code 1'
        WHEN SUPPLIER.S_PHONE LIKE '%2%' THEN 'Supplier has area code 2'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS SupplierAreaCode,
    MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'Returned'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG IS NULL THEN 'Not Returned'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ReturnStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE),
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT 
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    r.r_name AS region_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s_suppkey) AS supplier_count,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_discount) AS total_discounted_sales,
    AVG(li.l_quantity) AS avg_quantity_per_order
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON s.s_suppkey = li.l_suppkey
GROUP BY 
    n.n_name, r.r_name

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliersCount,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) > 10 AND SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) DESC, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT 
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    s.S_PHONE AS Phone,
    s.S_ACCTBAL As AccountBalance,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    o.O_CUSTKEY AS CustomerKey,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    li.L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM 
    SUPPLIER s
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Account_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Supplier_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supplier_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Supplier_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_LINENUMBER,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_ORDERKEY,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_COMMITDATE
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'CountryA')
    AND Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > Li.L_DISCOUNT + 100.00
    AND Li.L_SHIPDATE >= DATE('1998-09-02')
    AND Li.L_SHIPDATE < DATE('1998-10-01')
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NATIONKEY, C.C_CUSTKEY, S.S_SUPPKEY, Li.L_LINENUMBER

SELECT
    O_ORDERPRIORITY,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS AvgOrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(O_CLERK)) AS AvgClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    L_RETURNFLAG
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_ORDERPRIORITY, L_SHIPMODE, L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    p.P_CONTAINER,
    p.P_MFGR,
    p.P_BRAND
FROM 
    PART p
LEFT JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY 
    p.P_NAME, p.P_SIZE, p.P_TYPE, p.P_RETAILPRICE, p.P_CONTAINER, p.P_MFGR, p.P_BRAND
ORDER BY 
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    pa.P_NAME AS PartName,
    st.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART pa ON c.C_CUSTKEY = pa.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON pa.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER st ON li.L_SUPPKEY = st.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'AMERICA')
    AND li.L_LINESTATUS = 'R'

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_SIZE
ORDER BY
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    Sa.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    Cu.N_NAME AS Customer_Nation,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION Sa ON S.S_NATIONKEY = Sa.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION Cu ON C.C_NATIONKEY = Cu.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    Sa.N_NAME ASC,
    Cu.N_NAME ASC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS Part,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerBalance,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgPartCommentLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    MAX(li.L_TAX) AS MaxTax,
    MIN(li.L_TAX) AS MinTax
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_SUPPKEY
HAVING 
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBal,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AvgShipInstructLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ShippedOrderCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Delivered' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DeliveredOrderCount
FROM
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    O_ORDERSTATUS

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SUPPLIER_COUNT,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_BALANCE,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) + SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 1000000

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, N_NAME, S_NAME, R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN NATION ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST, N_NAME, S_NAME, R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT S_SUPPKEY) > 1
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_TYPE, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT, LINEITEM.L_COMMENT FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_PHONE

SELECT 
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS BuildingCustomers,
    SUM(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT LIKE '%Defected%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS DefectiveSuppliers,
    AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FURNITURE' THEN 1 ELSE NULL END)filtered_avg,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthInRegion
FROM 
    NATION 
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY 
INNER JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_COMMENT, 
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    n.n_name AS CustomerHomeCountry,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS NumCustomers,
    AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_quantity) AS TotalRevenue,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.l_returnflag = 'A' THEN li.l_quantity ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturns
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE))

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, REGION.R_REGIONKEY DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL PLATED BRASS' THEN 'SMALL PLATED BRASS' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(CASE WHEN PART.P_SIZE >= 10 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AverageSizeLarge,
    SUM(CASE WHEN NATION.N_REGIONKEY = 1 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NationRegion1Count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 100000 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS SupplierBalOver100kCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
    AND S_SUPPKEY IN (SELECT PS_SUPPKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
ORDER BY
    P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    n_r.R_NAME AS SUPPLIER_REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION n_r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = n_r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    p.P_PARTKEY ASC

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME = 'country_name'
AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND P.P_NAME IN (SELECT P_NAME FROM PART WHERE P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)))
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000)
AND N.N_NAME = 'Some Nation Name' -- replace with desired nation name
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE AS PART_SIZE,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS NATION_REGION,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    REGION.R_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PART.P_TYPE DESC,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME As CountryName,
    R.R_NAME As RegionName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EU'))
    AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P_NAME

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    p.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_TYPE = 'SMALL'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
    AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC NULLS FIRST,
    p.P_SIZE DESC,
    s.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
  C_NATIONKEY,
  AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
  AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
  AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
  AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
  SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNT,
  AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
  SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY,
  L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS SHIPMENT_INSTRUCTIONS
FROM
  CUSTOMER
JOIN
  SUPPLIER ON C_CUSTKEY = S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
  LINEITEM ON S_SUPPKEY = L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
  C_NATIONKEY,
  L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT 
    C.C_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_TYPE IN ('SMALL PLATED BRASS', 'LARGE NICKEL PLATE')
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME, 
    P.P_SIZE DESC, 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_C_MKTSEGMENT_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_S_ADDRESS_Length,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_L_RETURNFLAG_Length,
    COUNT(L_LINESTATUS) AS Total_Lines,
    COUNT(DISTINCT L_SUPPKEY) AS Unique_Suppliers,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantities
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE AS OrderTotalPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_QUANTITY As QuantityShipped
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    li.L_RETURNFLAG = ' '
AND
    li.L_SHIPMODE = 'air'
AND
    o.O_ORDERDATE >= '2023-01-01'
AND
    o.O_ORDERDATE <= '2023-12-31'
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQty
FROM
    PARTSUPP
