INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT, S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLYING_NATION,
    Su.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PSS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PSS
JOIN
    PART P ON PSS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER Su ON PSS.PS_SUPPKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON Su.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTH AMERICA'))
    AND Su.S_ACCTBAL > 500000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDR_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) AS AVG_SHIPINSTRUCT_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS TOTAL_CUSTOMERS,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND SUP.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000 AND R.R_NAME NOT LIKE 'Antarctica%'

SELECT AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Average_Part_RetailPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_LineItem_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Average_LineItem_Discount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MARKET_SEGMENT_NAME' -- replace with actual market segment name
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_LINENUMBER,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'Some Nation Name')
ORDER BY
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    Li.L_LINENUMBER DESC,
    R.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_QUANTITY,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE,
    LI.L_SHIPMODE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON P.P_PARTKEY = LI.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME LIKE '%%a%%' -- Replace 'a' with any letter to filter specific nations
ORDER BY
    N.N_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE DESC,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    LI.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS CustomerNationalName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    r.R_NAME AS SupplierRegionName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    LINEITEM li
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    s.S_COMMENT IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAIL_QTY
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
    AND AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) < 100

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation, CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) DESC, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND))

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnRate
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAILABILITY, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON SUP.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, SUP.S_NAME, N.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100 AND SUM(SUP.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalRevenue,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)
FROM
    PART
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 500

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TotalSupplyCost,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance,
    COUNT(S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME
HAVING 
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000 AND 
    COUNT(S_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTH AMERICA')
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(L_TAX),
    L_SHIPDATE,
    L_LINESTATUS
FROM
    CUSTOMER INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON C_CUSTKEY = S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON S_SUPPKEY = L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_SHIPDATE,
    L_LINESTATUS
HAVING
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) + AVG(S_ACCTBAL) > 1000

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Average_Retail_Price,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_Extended_Price,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS Distinct_Order_Count,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS Avg_Quantity
FROM 
    PART, 
    CUSTOMER, 
    SUPPLIER, 
    LINEITEM 
WHERE 
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY 
    AND CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY 
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY 
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY 
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_NAME, 
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    Suppliers_Info.S_NATIONKEY,
    Suppliers_Info.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    (SELECT S_NATIONKEY, S_ACCTBAL FROM SUPPLIER) Suppliers_Info ON Suppliers_Info.S_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
ORDER BY
    Suppliers_Info.S_NATIONKEY DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, P_CONTAINER, AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY < 100 THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplyCost_LowQty, AVG(CASE WHEN PS_AVAILQTY >= 100 THEN PS_SUPPLYCOST ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplyCost_HighQty
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PS_PARTKEY, P_CONTAINER
HAVING AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) <= 100

SELECT 
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgLenPartName,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLenCustomerName,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBalSupplier,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrders,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax
FROM 
    PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY 
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY 
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    PART.P_TYPE, 
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Supplier_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS Avg_LineItem_LineStatus_Length,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    L_SHIPMODE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgS_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgS_CommentLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS TotalPartTypes,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength
FROM 
    NATION
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE

SELECT
    p.p_name AS Part_Name,
    n.n_name AS Supplier_Country,
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) AS Average_Supply_Cost,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS Total_Available_Quantity
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    p.p_name, n.n_name
HAVING
    AVG(ps.ps_supplycost) > 1000 AND SUM(ps.ps_availqty) > 1000

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, P.P_NAME AS PartName, R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND C.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
ORDER BY N.N_NAME ASC, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, C.C_ACCTBAL ASC, R.R_NAME DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    P.P_SIZE,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT ps.PS_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS avg_household_customers, AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS avg_building_customers
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) DESC, AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 1 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 5000
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(P.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100000
    AND AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 500

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
         AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000 AND COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS Country, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount, REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG))

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000
    AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 500 AND COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 100 AND COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 50
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)),
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, PS_AVAILQTY, PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    cus.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER cus ON s.S_SUPPKEY = cus.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 100000)
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, n.N_NAME, cus.C_NAME, r.R_NAME, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    O.O_ORDERDATE,
    S.S_NAME,
    S.S_PHONE,
    S.S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT L.L_ORDERKEY),
    L.L_SHIPMODE,
    L.L_RETURNFLAG
FROM
    ORDERS O
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    O.O_ORDERDATE, S.S_NAME, S.S_PHONE, S.S_ACCTBAL, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_RETURNFLAG
ORDER BY
    AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, COUNT(DISTINCT L.L_ORDERKEY) DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT),
    LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER),
    LENGTH(PART.P_NAME),
    LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE),
    LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Avg_Tax,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Total_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    MIN(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE),
    MAX(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'TAKE BACK RETURN' THEN 'TAKE BACK RETURN' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_COMMENT FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    COUNT(REGION.R_REGIONKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthN,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthR
FROM
    NATION
LEFT JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(REGION.R_REGIONKEY) > 1 OR AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 50
ORDER BY
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    pa.P_NAME AS PartName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE As OrderTotal,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As ExtendedPrice,
    li.L_QUANTITY As QuantityShipped
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    PART pa ON li.L_PARTKEY = pa.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_ORDERKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-Urgent'
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE >= DATE('1998-01-01')
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE < DATE('1999-01-01')
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME ASC,
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 100)
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'North America')
    AND R.R_NAME = 'North America'

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT O.O_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrders,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS TotalSuppliers,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) AS C_NameLength
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME
ORDER BY
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) DESC,
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSPhoneLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 0.1 AND LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT < 0.2 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS MidDiscountExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT <= 0.1 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS LowDiscountExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT >= 0.2 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS HighDiscountExtendedPrice
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, L_DISCOUNT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
        ELSE NULL
    END) AS CustomerCount_Building,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgLength_CustomerName,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgLength_RegionName
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_DISCOUNT ELSE 0 END),
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END)
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME AS PartName, NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName, REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC, PART.P_NAME ASC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, c.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER AS L_LINENUMBER FROM ORDERS, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY GROUP BY L_LINENUMBER ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG))

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer,
    P.P_NAME AS Part,
    R.R_NAME AS Region,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) > 1
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME, AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 50
    AND SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, N_NAME AS SUPPLYING_NATION_NAME, S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT MIN(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION)))
AND PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Country,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumOfCustomers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantitiesShipped,
    CASE
        WHEN SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX) = 0 THEN 'No Tax'
        ELSE 'Tax Applied'
    END AS TaxStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION AS N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION AS R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000)
AND N.N_NAME LIKE '%%Europe%%'
AND S.S_ACCTBAL < 500000
ORDER BY P.P_NAME ASC, S.S_NAME DESC, N.N_NAME ASC, R.R_NAME DESC, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    C.C_CUSTKEY As CustomerKey,
    S.S_SUPPKEY As SupplierKey,
    N.N_NAME As NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT'
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = 160 --iso code for 'UNITED STATES'
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
ORDER BY
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'Component'
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplyingNation,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUST.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPL.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    CUST.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPL.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUPL ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPL.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER CUST ON SUPL.S_NATIONKEY = CUST.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON CUST.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND CUST.C_ACCTBAL > 5000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    n_c.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    n_s.N_NAME As SupplierNation,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY As AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_c.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_s ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_s.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT),
    SUM(L_QUANTITY),
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, L_SHIPINSTRUCT
ORDER BY
    C_NATIONKEY DESC, SUM(L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
    AND P.P_NAME IN (SELECT P_NAME FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR LIKE 'MFGR%A%')

SELECT 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailableQuantity,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS DistinctPartKeyCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
AND
    S.S_ACCTBAL > 500000
AND
    N.N_NAME LIKE 'S%'
AND
    R.R_NAME LIKE 'Asia%'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    li.l_extendedprice,
    li.l_discount,
    li.l_quantity,
    r.r_name AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON li.l_suppkey = c.c_custkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.c_custkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE
    n.n_regionkey = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA') -- Assuming a region with R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA'
    AND li.l_suppkey IS NOT NULL
    AND li.l_quantity > 10
    AND li.l_discount IS NOT NULL
    AND li.l_extendedprice > (1.1 * li.l_discount)

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailableQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SCOmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LL.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LL ON P.P_PARTKEY = LL.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LL.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ABóVeFreeze')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    LL.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalOrderItems, AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount 
FROM NATION 
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY 
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY 
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY 
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS Region
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT DESC,
    R.R_NAME

SELECT
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY = 0 THEN 'Out of Stock'
        ELSE 'In Stock'
    END AS StockStatus,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    CASE
        WHEN PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY = 0 THEN 'Out of Stock'
        ELSE 'In Stock'
    END

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_TYPE, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'BUILDING' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY REGION.R_COMMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_VALUE, AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_COMMENT_LENGTH, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVERAGE_PHONE_LENGTH, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_COMMENT_LENGTH, AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AVERAGE_QUANTITY
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT
    ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER,
    LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    ORDERS
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_BRAND AS Part_Brand,
    P.P_CONTAINER AS Part_Container,
    P.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Part_RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SEGMENT_YOU_WANT')

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN ('FRANCE', 'GERMANY') -- Example: only for France and Germany
ORDER BY
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    lp.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON c.C_CUSTKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM lp ON o.O_ORDERKEY = lp.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON lp.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'USA%') -- Filter for nations with 'USA' in their name
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE >= '2023-01-01' AND o.O_ORDERDATE < '2023-07-01' -- Orders in H1 2023
    AND lp.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 500 -- Items priced over $500
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%')
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    REGION.R_COMMENT AS RegionComment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName,
       COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
       AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
       AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance,
       COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
       C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(CAST(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS DECIMAL(10,2))) AS AvgSupplyCost,
       AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCustomerCommentLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Cust_Name_Length,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Cust_BAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Supp_Name_Length,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supp_BAL
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT MAX(N_REGIONKEY) FROM NATION GROUP BY N_REGIONKEY)
AND REGION.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT MAX(R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION GROUP BY R_REGIONKEY)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME DESC, REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    PART.P_SIZE DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PART.P_CONTAINER IN ('WRAP PKG', 'DRUM', 'CARTON')
ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC, CASE
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'WRAP PKG' THEN 1
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'DRUM' THEN 2
    WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'CARTON' THEN 3
    ELSE 4
END

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, P_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME, PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND PS_AVAILQTY < (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P_RETAILPRICE ASC, S_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(ll.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(ll.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ll ON p.P_PARTKEY = ll.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ll.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(ll.L_QUANTITY) > 100
ORDER BY
    AVG(ll.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Account_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Supplier_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY)) AS Avg_NationKey_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY, P_SIZE, P_TYPE, C_NAME, S_NAME, C_COMMENT, S_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < PART.P_SIZE
AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING')
    AND ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
    AND ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME As NationName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_SIZE = 50 AND
    N.N_NAME LIKE '{%}' AND
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'Brass'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_C_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_L_LINESTATUS_LENGTH,
    MAX(L_DISCOUNT) AS MAX_L_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_L_QUANTITY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    AVG(li.l_extendedprice) AS AverageOrderPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.l_returnflag = 'A' THEN li.l_quantity ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnedQuantity,
    SUM(CASE WHEN li.l_quantity > 100 THEN li.l_quantity ELSE 0 END) AS LargerQuantityOrders
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, c.c_name, s.s_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS ORDER_COUNT,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVG_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AVG_CUSTOMER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_BRAND, COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_BRAND
HAVING COUNT(PART.P_PARTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 500 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    MAX(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS MaxAccountBalance,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCountOfCustomers
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME,
    r.R_NAME

SELECT 
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_QUANTITY,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM 
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    Li.L_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O_SHIP')
ORDER BY 
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, C.C_CUSTKEY, S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlag_Length,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Distinct_ExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Avg_Discount,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS CommitDate
FROM
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName, R.R_NAME AS RegionName, COUNT(C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumCustomers, COUNT(S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers, AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance
FROM NATION N
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS NumReturns,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnValue,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE AS OrderReceiptDate
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE)
HAVING SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 10000 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05
ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    MIN(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MIN_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAIL_QTY,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NATIONKEY AS CUSTOMER_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME,
    C.C_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    MIN(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(PART.P_SIZE)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100000 AND AVG(PART.P_SIZE) > 5
ORDER BY SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    MAX(c.c_acctbal) AS MaxCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS AveragePartRetailPrice,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey AND c.c_custkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
    AND P.P_RETAILPRICE < 50
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, 
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, 
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, 
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, 
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, 
    LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, 
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, 
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, 
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT
FROM 
    SUPPLIER
INNER JOIN 
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
