    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT LIKE '%specific_comment_pattern%'
    AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG NOT IN ('A','D')

SELECT
    P_MFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AvgTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AvgBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustKeyCount
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER
ON
    PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P_MFGR,
    C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 10000
ORDER BY
    SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC,
    P_MFGR ASC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_TAX
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '1996-01-01' AND '1996-12-31'
AND
    li.L_SHIPMODE IN ('REG AIR', 'AIR FREM')
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    MAX(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MAX_SUPPLY_COST,
    MIN(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MIN_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABILITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    s.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_COMMENT,
    C_PHONE,
    S_SUPPKEY,
    R_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PS_AVAILQTY > 0 THEN 1
        ELSE 2
    END,
    C_PHONE DESC,
    R_COMMENT ASC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_PARTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    (CASE
        WHEN PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART) THEN 'High Price'
        ELSE 'Low Price'
    END) AS PriceCategory
FROM
    NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS UniqueCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS UniqueSuppliers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT R.R_REGIONKEY) AS Regions
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT))

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AVERAGE_QUANTITY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DISTINCT_ORDERS,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_N_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_S_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_S_PHONE_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AND
    LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    P.P_SIZE AS PART_SIZE,
    P.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    P.P_BRAND AS PART_BRAND,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RETAIL_PRICE,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS TotalCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS TotalSuppliers
FROM
    NATION
    JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
    JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT o.O_ORDERSTATUS, o.O_CUSTKEY, o.O_ORDERPRIORITY, l.L_SHIPMODE, l.L_RETURNFLAG, COUNT(l.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * l.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalExtendedPriceWithQuantity
FROM ORDERS o
JOIN LINEITEM l ON o.O_ORDERKEY = l.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY o.O_ORDERSTATUS, o.O_CUSTKEY, o.O_ORDERPRIORITY, l.L_SHIPMODE, l.L_RETURNFLAG
HAVING COUNT(l.L_ORDERKEY) >= 10 AND SUM(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * l.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgLengthCustomerComment,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSupplierName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'REGION_A' THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS CountMarketingInRegionA,
    SUM(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'REGION_B' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS TotalAccountBalanceInRegionB,
    AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS AvgSupplierAcctBalPositive
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    cn.N_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION cn ON c.C_NATIONKEY = cn.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'ю%' AND N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME LIKE 'Europe%'))
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    c.C_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 20
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPartBrandLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAcctBal,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) THEN 'Longer Customer Name'
        ELSE 'Shorter or Equal Customer Name'
    END AS NameComparison
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    L_SHIPMODE,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgOnlyFulfilled,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_LINESTATUS = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgAbandoned
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AVG_C_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_S_NAME_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = ' segment_X ' THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS COUNTY_X,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = ' segment_Y ' THEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY END) AS COUNTY_Y,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName, LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY AS TotalExtendedPrice
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT = 'Some specific comment for nation')
AND C_CUSTKEY NOT IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_COMMENT LIKE '%Add%')
AND S_NATIONKEY NOT IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT = 'Some other specific comment for nation')

SELECT 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    PART ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOME_REGION_NAME') -- replace 'SOME_REGION_NAME' with an actual region
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    C.C_NAME ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND   
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'AMERICA')
AND   
    s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'AMERICA')
AND   
    r.R_NAME = 'AMERICA'
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, 
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName, 
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName, 
    NATION.N_COMMENT, 
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, 
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    cp.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    ot.O_ORDERDATE AS Order_Date,
    ct.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    st.S_NAME As Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART cp
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON cp.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS ot ON li.L_ORDERKEY = ot.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ct ON ot.O_CUSTKEY = ct.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER st ON li.L_SUPPKEY = st.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    ot.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
ORDER BY
    ot.O_ORDERDATE DESC, L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON P.P_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY -- Assuming part keys are consistent across tables
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS NATION ON S.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    S.S_Name AS SupplierName,
    P.P_Name AS PartName,
    P.P_Size,
    P.P_Type,
    P.P_Brand,
    P.P_RetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    S.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION N WHERE N.N_NAME = 'AF performs Arabian horse breeding')
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'Grocery'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    (PART.P_SIZE > 100 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 500)
    OR (CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'EDUCATION' AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL < 10000)
    OR (SUPPLIER.S_NAME LIKE 'S%Q%' AND LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 1000)
ORDER BY
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_SIZE > 100 THEN 1
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'EDUCATION' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_Supplier,
    SUM(S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND
    s.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
FROM NATION N
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_NATIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE N.N_COMMENT LIKE '%developed%'
AND R.R_COMMENT LIKE '%stable% economy%'
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT R.R_REGIONKEY) > 1
ORDER BY N.N_NAME ASC, R.R_NAME DESC

SELECT
    nm.N_NAME AS NationName,
    cus.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    sup.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_TAX,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    CUSTOMER cus ON li.L_SUPPKEY = cus.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER sup ON li.L_SUPPKEY = sup.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION nm ON cus.C_NATIONKEY = nm.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON nm.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    nm.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'SOME_NATION_NAME')
ORDER BY
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_QUANTITY DESC, li.L_TAX DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUPPL.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUPPL ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPL.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON SUPPL.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART P ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'AF'))
ORDER BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' -- Considering only 'A' ( full array ) returned items
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_SHIPDATE DESC, r.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_TAX AS L_TAX FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_TAX

SELECT 
    p.p_name,
    n.n_name AS nation,
    s.s_name AS supplier,
    SUM(ps.ps_supplycost) AS total_supply_cost,
    SUM(ps.ps_availqty) AS total_available_quantity
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.p_partkey = ps.ps_partkey
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY 
    p.p_name, n.n_name, s.s_name
HAVING 
    SUM(ps.ps_supplycost) > 10000 AND SUM(ps.ps_availqty) > 500

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNATION,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSUPPLIER,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthREGION,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON P.P_PARTKEY = Li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    Li.L_SHIPDATE IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT DESC,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME As Region_Name,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST As Supply_Cost,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY As Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    O.O_ORDERDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON N.N_NATIONKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON O.O_CUSTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON O.O_ORDERKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    O.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'R' -- 'R' for Returned
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, O.O_ORDERDATE DESC, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SuppName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) > 500

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS Avg_AvailQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_NameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_AddressLength,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_NAME, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'PROMO BRUSHED COPPER' THEN 'PROMO BRUSHED COPPER' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_TYPE, ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'AUTOMOBILE' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY PART.P_SIZE

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IN (SELECT DISTINCT C_MKTSEGMENT FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 100000)
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT ASC

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, P_NAME, P_SIZE, PS_SUPPLYCOST, S_NAME, S_COMMENT, S_NATIONKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'NATION_NAME')
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, S_NAME ASC, P_NAME DESC, S_COMMENT DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY,
       CASE
           WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'SACK' THEN 'SACK'
           WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'BOX' THEN 'BOX'
           ELSE 'Other'
       END AS ContainerType,
       CASE
           WHEN P_TYPE = 'Type#A' THEN 'Type#A'
           WHEN P_TYPE = 'Type#B' THEN 'Type#B'
           ELSE 'Other'
       END AS TypeCategory,
       CASE
           WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#10' THEN 'Brand#10'
           WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#15' THEN 'Brand#15'
           ELSE 'Other'
       END AS BrandGroup
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
       CASE
           WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#15' THEN 1
           WHEN P_BRAND = 'Brand#10' THEN 2
           ELSE 3
       END,
       CASE
           WHEN P_TYPE = 'Type#A' THEN 1
           WHEN P_TYPE = 'Type#B' THEN 2
           ELSE 3
       END,
       CASE
           WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'SACK' THEN 1
           WHEN P_CONTAINER = 'BOX' THEN 2
           ELSE 3
       END

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    COUNT(p.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME, c.C_NAME, p.P_NAME
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME, AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY)

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(R_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_REGION_NAME_LENGTH
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUM(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    L.L_SHIPMODE,
    L.L_TAX
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON C.C_CUSTKEY = L.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, L.L_SHIPMODE, L.L_TAX

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierCountry,
    P.P_SIZE,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, P.P_SIZE

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    s.S_NAME,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    SUM(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS TotalDiscount
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100 AND SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 10 AND SUM(li.L_DISCOUNT) > 0.5 * SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY
HAVING AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) > 15
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT C_NATIONKEY, COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) > 50 THEN C_CUSTKEY END) AS CustWithLongCommentCount, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) > 50 THEN C_CUSTKEY END) > 0
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP,
    NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    SUM(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_PARTKEY, ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT), LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT), LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT) ASC, LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME) DESC, LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT) ASC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    n.N_NAME AS ORDER_NATION,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT'
    AND li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
    AND o.O_TOTALPRICE > 1000
    AND n.N_REGIONKEY = 1 -- Assuming NATION table has a N_REGIONKEY column
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME AS PartName, PART.P_SIZE AS PartSize, PART.P_TYPE AS PartType, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LL ON P.P_PARTKEY = LL.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LL.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PROTECTIVE')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, P.P_NAME, LL.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_shipMode,
    Li.L_TAX,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'USA%') -- filtering nations with names starting with 'USA'
    AND Li.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE '%R%' -- excluding returned items
    AND Li.L_RECEIPTDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31' -- filtering items received in 2023
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, Li.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_PARTKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#31' THEN 'Brand#31' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY REGION.R_COMMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, PART.P_TYPE DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)),
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY),
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS Supplier_NationName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    s.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    s.S_ADDRESS As SupplierAddress,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_ORDERKEY,
    li.L_COMMITDATE,
    r.R_NAME As RegionName
FROM 
    LINEITEM li
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT LIKE '%Developed%')
ORDER BY 
    n.N_NATIONKEY DESC, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailability,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AverageAddressLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    p.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    r.R_NAME As Region_Name
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, n.N_NAME ASC, p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLen,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAcctBal,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgPartRetailPrice
FROM
    PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, PART.P_RETAILPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) > 50
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PART.P_SIZE DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AverageRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) AS PartCount
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT P.P_PARTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierBalance
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 100
    AND SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) IS NOT NULL

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    AVG(li.l_extendedprice) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) AS DistinctSuppliers
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, c.c_name, s.s_name
HAVING
    AVG(li.l_extendedprice) > 1000 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.l_suppkey) > 5

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NAME LIKE 'South%'
    AND c.C_ACCTBAL > 5000
    AND ps.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT O_CLERK,
        MONTH(O_ORDERDATE),
        YEAR(O_ORDERDATE),
        AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
        AVG(L_DISCOUNT),
        SUM(L_QUANTITY),
        COUNT(DISTINCT L_PARTKEY)
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_CLERK, MONTH(O_ORDERDATE), YEAR(O_ORDERDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(L_DISCOUNT) DESC, SUM(L_QUANTITY) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN 'SHIP' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_TAX, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_CONTAINER,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    p.P_COMMENT,
    p.P_MFGR,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    p.P_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AveragePhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AverageCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AverageRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT LIKE '%Advanced%')
ORDER BY
    R.R_NAME, LI.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, MAX(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), MIN(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS, ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'TAKE BACK RETURN' THEN 'TAKE BACK RETURN' ELSE 'Other' END FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 50

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_SIZE,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AvgContainerNameLength,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    P_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_PARTKEY,
    P_SIZE,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    P_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
    AND AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) > 5
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC,
    P_SIZE DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    Su.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER Su ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON Su.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE'))

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPplier.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, NATION.N_COMMENT ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
       COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
       AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierBalance,
       SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturnedItems,
       SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalOrderValue
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_Customer,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_Supplier,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal_Customer,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAcctBal_Supplier,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 2000
ORDER BY
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT O_ORDERPRIORITY, AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1- urgent' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_Urgent_Orders, SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '2- high' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_High_Orders, SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '3- normal' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_Normal_Orders, SUM(CASE WHEN O_ORDERPRIORITY = '4- not specified' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Num_NotSpecified_Orders
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O_ORDERPRIORITY

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    S.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ShippedViaAirCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS TotalExtendedPriceAir,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalQuantityShippedAir,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgSupplierPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineItemLineStatusLength
FROM
    NATION,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    n.N_NAME,
    s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100000
    AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE ORDER BY SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER)

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))

SELECT n.n_name, p.p_name, c.c_name
FROM NATION n
JOIN CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
WHERE p_retailprice > (SELECT AVG(p2.p_retailprice) FROM PART p2)
AND n.n_name NOT IN (SELECT n3.n_name FROM NATION n3 WHERE n3.n_regionkey IN (SELECT r.r_regionkey FROM REGION r WHERE r_name = 'AMERICA'))
ORDER BY p_retailprice DESC, n.n_name ASC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_BALANCE,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_VALUE,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'Return'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'C' THEN 'Cancel'
        ELSE 'No Return'
    END AS LINEITEM_RETURN_STATUS
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N.N_NAME FROM NATION N JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY WHERE R_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE'))
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, p.P_PARTKEY, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, n.N_NAME

SELECT p.P_NAME AS PartName, 
       n.N_NAME AS NationName, 
       s.S_NAME AS SupplierName, 
       r.R_NAME AS RegionName, 
       ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity, 
       ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost
FROM PARTSUPP ps
JOIN PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Some Specific Region Name'))
ORDER BY p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME, r.R_NAME, ps.PS_AVAILQTY, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    (PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST / PART.P_RETAILPRICE) * 100 AS CostPercentageOfRetailPrice
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumOfCustomers,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumOfSuppliers,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNationNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMktSegmentLength,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLineItemShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLineItemType,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgQuantity,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    s.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'GERMANY')
    AND c.C_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'FRANCE')
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS ProductName,
    n_c.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    n_s.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_c.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_s ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_s.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
AND S_ACCTBAL > 50000
AND N_NAME LIKE '%Europe%'
AND R_NAME LIKE 'UK%'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, S_NAME ASC, N_NAME DESC, R_NAME ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_SIZE ASC

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R'
ORDER BY
    PART.P_NAME, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE AS L_SHIPDATE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPDATE

SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost, NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation, AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength, AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST < 50
ORDER BY PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    O.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    O.O_TOTALPRICE AS TotalPrice,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE As ExtendedPrice,
    L.L_DISCOUNT As DiscountRate
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS O ON C.C_CUSTKEY = O.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN ('CANADA', 'MEXICO') -- Filtering by specific Nations
    AND O.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31' -- Orders placed in 2023
    AND L.L_DISCOUNT > 0.10 -- Orders with discount greater than 10%
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME ASC,
    O.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LI.L_QUANTITY) > 100000

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, O_ORDERDATE DESC, C_ACCTBAL DESC, S_NAME ASC, L_QUANTITY DESC, L_DISCOUNT ASC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthSupplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgNameLengthRegion,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT l.L_PARTKEY) AS UniqueParts,
    SUM(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * l.L_DISCOUNT) / SUM(l.L_QUANTITY) AS AvgDiscountedPrice,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS SupplierAvgAcctBal
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_CUSTKEY, c.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * l.L_DISCOUNT) / SUM(l.L_QUANTITY) IS NOT NULL

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT 
        PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
        PART.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
        SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
        CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
        PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
        SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
        CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
        PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
        SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM 
        PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
        PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
        CUSTOMER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN 
        SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    p.P_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    r.R_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON p.P_BRAND = s.S_NAME
WHERE
    n.N_NAME LIKE '%S%'
ORDER BY
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    s.S_ACCTBAL ASC,
    r.R_REGIONKEY DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS TotalSupplierBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.c_custkey) AS UniqueCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS UniqueSuppliers,
    AVG(c.c_acctbal) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(s.s_acctbal) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS Customer_Count,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AcctBalance,
    COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength
FROM
    NATION JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_COMMENT,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AvgLengthSupplierName,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1.0 ELSE 0.0 END) AS PctReturnedItems,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLengthShippingMode
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MktSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBal,
    LINEITEM.L_ShipMode,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#43'
    AND LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT IN ('DELIVER IN PERSON', 'OTHER')
ORDER BY
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSegment DESC,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE NULLS FIRST

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY,
    NATION.N_COMMENT AS N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT AS C_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT AS S_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
