    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLength,
    AVG(P.P_SIZE) AS AvgPoolSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(P.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_LINENUMBER,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    li.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
    AND n.N_NAME = 'PERU'
ORDER BY
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC, c.C_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS PS_SUPPLYCOST FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 5000

SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) DESC, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLen, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLen
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_SIZE) > 5 AND AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, AVG(NATION.N_NATIONKEY) as AvgNationKey, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) as AvgCustomerKey, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) as AvgSupplierKey, R_COMMENT
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, REGION.R_COMMENT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    P.P_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE,
    S.S_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 100

SELECT P.P_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, C.C_PHONE, C.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PARTSUPP AS PS JOIN PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER AS C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION AS N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Antarctica')
AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD'
ORDER BY PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)) AS AVERAGE_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AVERAGE_BRAND_LENGTH,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVERAGE_RETAIL_PRICE,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS SUM_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_ADDRESS_LENGTH
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    C_PHONE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_TYPE = 'Gloves'
    AND P.P_RETAILPRICE > (
        SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE)
        FROM PART
        WHERE P_TYPE = 'Gloves'
    )
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM PART
 INNER JOIN PARTSUPP ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
 INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
 INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 100 AND C_MKTSEGMENT LIKE '%Electronics%'
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS NumParts,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CASE
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUSTRALIA' THEN 'AU'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BRAZIL' THEN 'BR'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'CANADA' THEN 'CA'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'FRANCE' THEN 'FR'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'GERMANY' THEN 'DE'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'ISRAEL' THEN 'IL'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'JAPAN' THEN 'JP'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'KR' THEN 'KR'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MEXICO' THEN 'MX'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'SOUTH AFRICA' THEN 'SA'
        WHEN c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'UNITED KINGDOM' THEN 'UK'
        ELSE 'OTHER'
    END AS CountrySegment,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY < 20)
ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, SUPPLIER.S_NAME DESC, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_TYPE AS P_TYPE FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_TYPE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), PART.P_CONTAINER AS P_CONTAINER FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_CONTAINER

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME LIKE '%%%L%T%' AND
    S.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S2.S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER S2)
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS customer_country,
    SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS total_order_value,
    AVG(liz.l_quantity) AS average_quantity_per_order,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS supplier_account_balance
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM liz ON o.o_orderkey = liz.l_orderkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON liz.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name

SELECT PS_SUPPKEY AS SupplierKey, P_NAME AS PartName, C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerSegment, S_NAME AS SupplierName, PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PERTH')
ORDER BY PS_AVAILQTY DESC, C_MKTSEGMENT ASC, S_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS SUPPLIER_REGION,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_NATIONKEY AS CUSTOMER_NATION
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    C.C_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_CONTAINER, CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#2' THEN 'Manufacturer#2' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'P' THEN 'P' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_COMMENT FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustNameLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSuppAddressLen,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS DistinctOrderCount,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS
FROM
    CUSTOMER
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_COMMENT, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_TYPE, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'LARGE POLISHED TIN' THEN 'LARGE POLISHED TIN' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY PART.P_BRAND

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Customer_Nation_Name,
    C.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    C.C_ADDRESS AS Customer_Address,
    C.C_PHONE As Customer_Phone,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS Customer_Account_Balance,
    R.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    S.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    S.S_PHONE AS Supplier_Phone,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS Supplier_Account_Balance
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS National_Name, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS Supplier_Phone, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length, MIN(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS Min_Tax, MAX(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS Max_Discount
FROM NATION
JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE
HAVING COUNT(LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) > 1

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    Li.L_SHIPMODE,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'PACIFIC')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, Li.L_SHIPMODE, Li.L_RECEIPTDATE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_BRAND
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART p)
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER s)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ADDR_LEN,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_STATUS_LEN,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_TAX > 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TAX_PAYING_LINEITEMS,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_LINEITEM_DISCOUNT,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT SUM(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY AS O_SHIPPRIORITY FROM ORDERS, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY GROUP BY O_SHIPPRIORITY

SELECT
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMarketSegmentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_MFGR, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))
FROM PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_MFGR
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT N.N_NAME AS NationName, R.R_NAME AS RegionName, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName, S.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone
FROM NATION N
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT S_NATIONKEY FROM SUPPLIER WHERE S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)))

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, P.P_NAME
HAVING AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Air'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'ROAD' THEN 'Road'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'RAIL' THEN 'Rail'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'SHIP' THEN 'Ship'
        ELSE 'Unknown'
    END AS SHIP_MODE_CATEGORY
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY ORDER BY SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE)

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT))
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) > 15

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL BRUSHED STEEL' THEN 'SMALL BRUSHED STEEL' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, ORDERS.O_COMMENT, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' THEN 'F' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN '1-URGENT' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'R' ELSE 'Other' END FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_COMMENT

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength_NATION,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_NAME) AS CountDistinctCustomers_C,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance_C,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength_R,
    CASE
        WHEN AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) THEN 'True'
        ELSE 'False'
    END AS N_CommentLongerThanRegionName,
    C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, C_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) DESC, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 100)
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    C.C_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME,
    R.R_NAME

SELECT
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)) AS AvgLenMFGR,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgLenType,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgLenName,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgLenBrand
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_MFGR,
    PART.P_TYPE

SELECT PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, ORDERS.O_CLERK, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'TAKE BACK RETURN' THEN 'TAKE BACK RETURN' ELSE 'Other' END, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_CLERK

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLYER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%')
    AND R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'ASIA')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AGRICULTURAL')
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'BRAZIL')
    AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC,
    S.S_NAME ASC,
    C.C_NAME ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N_C.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    N_S.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_C ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N_C.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N_S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_S.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
AND N_NAME LIKE 'S%'
AND R_NAME LIKE 'EU%'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY ASC, S_NAME, P_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY),
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT / 100) AS TOTAL_DISCOUNTED_REVENUE
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTH AMERICA'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName, SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName, PART.P_NAME AS PartName
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS ExtendedPrice,
    li.L_QUANTITY As QuantityShipped
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON c.C_CUSTKEY = o.O_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME, o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLength,
    S_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NS.N_NAME AS NationName, P_NAME AS PartName, C_NAME AS CustomerName, R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION NS ON C.C_NATIONKEY = NS.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON NS.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), L_SHIPDATE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, L_SHIPDATE
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_NationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_SupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS Avg_RegionNameLength,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgPartNameLength,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS AvgPartSize,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)) AS AvgPartTypeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AvgCustomerAddrLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgCustomerMarketSegmentLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL PERFORATED' THEN 'Small Perforated'
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'LARGE PRESSURE-TREATED' THEN 'Large Pressure-Treated'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS PartTypeCategory,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE ASC,
    CASE
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'SMALL PERFORATED' THEN 1
        WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'LARGE PRESSURE-TREATED' THEN 2
        ELSE 3
    END,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation, C.C_NAME AS CustomerName, S.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN NATION N ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_REGIONKEY = 2) -- Assuming region 2 for demonstration purposes, adjust as necessary
AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 -- Example filter for parts with more than 100 available quantity
AND C.C_ACCTBAL > 5000 -- Example filter for customers with account balance greater than 5000
ORDER BY PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, C.C_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_CONTAINER, PS_SUPPKEY AS SUPPLIER_KEY, P_MFGR, C_CUSTKEY AS CUSTOMER_KEY, S_NATIONKEY, S_ADDRESS
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE P_CONTAINER IN ('MED JAR', 'Lgs Jrana', 'STN Qty')
AND P_TYPE LIKE 'COMPONENT'
AND PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT CASE WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#43' THEN 'Brand#43' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT))

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(ps2.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP ps2)
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC,
    s.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY = 11 -- for instance, using USA nation key if present in NATION table
    AND li.L_SHIPDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31'

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    SUM(li.l_extendedprice * li.l_discount) AS TotalDiscountGiven,
    SUM(li.l_quantity) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, c.c_name, s.s_name
HAVING
    SUM(li.l_quantity) > 1000

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY) AS PartCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgSupplierAddressLength
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX)

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) AS TotalLineItems,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS ReturnedItems,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_BALANCE, SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Account_Balance,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    Region.R_NAME
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    Region.R_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    p.P_SIZE,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
LEFT JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(p2.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART p2)
ORDER BY
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    c.C_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_SIZE ASC,
    NATION.N_NAME DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    REGION.R_NAME AS Region_Name,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Account_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS Supplier_Count,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Nation,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS Avg_Name_Length_Supplier,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS Avg_Comment_Length_Region
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_MFGR)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NAME LIKE 'A%' AND s.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, ps.PS_AVAILQTY ASC, p.P_NAME

SELECT 
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM 
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    Li.L_ORDERKEY IN (SELECT O_ORDERKEY FROM ORDERS WHERE O_ORDERDATE Between '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31')
ORDER BY 
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_SUPPKEY,
    N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name
FROM 
    LINEITEM li
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON li.L_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > (SELECT AVG(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) FROM LINEITEM)
AND  
    s.S_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
AND 
    li.L_SHIPMODE IN ('REG AIR', 'REG SEA')
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, 
    li.L_SHIPDATE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
ORDER BY AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT DESC, PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, REGION.R_NAME ASC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    MIN(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS MinSupplierAccountBalance
FROM 
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN 
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND 
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND 
    MIN(S.S_ACCTBAL) < 5000
ORDER BY 
    N.N_NAME, AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NATIONKEY,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NATIONKEY,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * li.L_DISCOUNT) / SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS AVG_DISCOUNTED_PRICE_PER_UNIT,
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_ORDERKEY) AS NUM_UNIQUE_ORDERS
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NATIONKEY, c.C_NAME, s.S_NATIONKEY, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT li.L_ORDERKEY) > 100

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalances,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AvgLenReturnFlag,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgLenShipMode
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_TAX
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT LIKE '%Asia%')
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME DESC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE DESC, LINEITEM.L_TAX ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AVERAGE_RETAIL_PRICE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS UNIQUE_CUSTOMERS,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS SUPPLIER_ACCT_BAL
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 100000
ORDER BY
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    P.P_SIZE AS PartSize,
    P.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    P.P_BRAND AS PartBrand,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierBalance
FROM 
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN 
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
CASE
    WHEN SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY IS NOT NULL THEN SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
    ELSE 'Supplier not found'
END AS S_COMMENT
FROM CUSTOMER
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) AS Part_Count,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Average_RetailPrice,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_AccountBalance
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) > 10 AND AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50.00 AND SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000.00

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, n.N_NAME, s.S_NAME, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME, s.S_NAME, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY ASC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PART.P_SIZE AS Part_Size,
    PART.P_TYPE As Part_Type,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE As RetailPrice,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL As Supplier_AccountBalance
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 10000 AND SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) > 50

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TotalReturns
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_CustNameLen,
    MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Max_CustAddrLen,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_AcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS TotalCustomers
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
ORDER BY
    REGION.R_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N_C.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION,
    PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PSS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PSS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PSS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PSS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N_C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_C.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N_C.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%')
ORDER BY 
    PSS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, 
    N_C.N_NAME ASC, 
    C.C_NAME ASC, 
    S.S_NAME ASC, 
    R.R_NAME ASC, 
    PSS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS)) AS Avg_OrderStatusLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(ORDERS.O_CLERK)) AS Avg_ClerkLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS Avg_ShipModeLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS Avg_ReturnFlagLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE AS L_SHIPMODE,
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS AS OrderStatus,
    ORDERS.O_CLERK AS Clerk
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY
    ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS,
    ORDERS.O_CLERK,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT PART.P_CONTAINER, PART.P_MFGR, PART.P_COMMENT, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 'MACHINERY' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY PART.P_COMMENT

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY AS RegionKey,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY) AS PartsCount,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY BETWEEN 1 AND 10 -- Assuming N_NATIONKEY ranges from 1 to 10 for illustrative purposes
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT DESC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE AS PART_TYPE,
    P.P_SIZE AS PART_SIZE,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS RETAIL_PRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), O.O_CLERK, COUNT(L.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM L ON O.O_ORDERKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE, O.O_CLERK
ORDER BY AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(L.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) DESC

SELECT
    n.n_name AS Nation,
    p.p_name AS Part,
    p.p_type AS PartType,
    c.c_name AS Customer,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS AverageRetailPrice
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN
    PART p ON c.c_custkey = p.p_partkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, p.p_name, p.p_type, c.c_name
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.p_partkey) > 1
ORDER BY
    n.n_name, p.p_type, ABS(AVG(p.p_retailprice) - MIN(p.p_retailprice)) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_PARTKEY, ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY, ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '5-LOW' THEN '5-LOW' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_COMMENT FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10

SELECT AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY
HAVING AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) > 5

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PART P
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND 
    S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'PERU')

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    MAX(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS HasAcceptedLineItems,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*) AS AcceptancePercentage,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_CONTAINER)) AS AVERAGE_CONTAINER_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)) AS AVERAGE_TYPE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)) AS AVERAGE_BRAND_LENGTH,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AVERAGE_MKTSEGMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS AVERAGE_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_SUPPKEY) AS UNIQUE_SUPPLIER_COUNT
FROM
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    c.C_NATIONKEY,
    n.N_NAME AS CustomerNationName,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NATIONKEY,
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) > 0
    AND AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 10000 -- Example threshold
ORDER BY
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPKEY, PS_PARTKEY, N_NAME, S_NAME, R_NAME, PS_AVAILQTY, PS_SUPPLYCOST, S_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY ASC, S_ACCTBAL DESC, LENGTH(N_NAME) DESC, LENGTH(S_NAME) ASC, LENGTH(R_NAME) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS HighBalanceCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL = 0 THEN CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY END) AS ZeroBalanceCustomers,
    SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND))

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_BRAND, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#42'
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE, PART.P_BRAND, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CUSTOMER.C_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, AVG(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS AvgReturnRate, SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY ELSE 0 END) AS TotalDistributedQuantities, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, LINEITEM, SUPPLIER
WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT IS NOT NULL)
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
AND REGION.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_COMMENT IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, ORDERS.O_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    n.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN 
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > 500000
    AND c.C_ACCTBAL < 1000000
ORDER BY 
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, n.N_NAME ASC, c.C_NAME DESC, r.R_NAME ASC

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_BRAND), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM PART
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE
HAVING AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) DESC

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CS.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER CS ON S.S_SUPPKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTHERN')
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART.P_TYPE, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100 AND PART.P_SIZE > 50
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    COUNT(C.C_CUSTKEY) AS NUM_CUSTOMERS,
    COUNT(S.S_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_SUPPLIERS,
    SUM(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    SUM(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Europe'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER AS S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION AS N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION AS R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
AND N_NAME LIKE '%%%south%'
AND R_NAME LIKE '%%%Americas%'
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY ASC, P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    COUNT(L.L_ORDERKEY) AS Total_Order_Lines,
    AVG(L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(L.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount,
    SUM(L.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM L ON C.C_CUSTKEY = L.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
