    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Asia'))
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION CUS_NATION ON C.C_NATIONKEY = CUS_NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME = 'USA' -- assuming all US suppliers and customers are in nations with N_NAME = 'USA'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, CUS_NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    CUSTOMER C
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'SOME_COUNTRY_NAME') -- replace 'SOME_COUNTRY_NAME' with actual country name
ORDER BY
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, N.N_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
INNER JOIN PART p ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION n ON n.N_NATIONKEY = ps.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER c ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 1000
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    p.P_NAME ASC

SELECT n.n_name AS Nation, c.c_name AS Customer, s.s_name AS Supplier, li.l_tax, li.l_extendedprice, li.l_discount
FROM NATION n
JOIN CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN SUPPLIER s ON c.c_custkey = s.s_suppkey
JOIN LINEITEM li ON s.s_suppkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
WHERE n.n_name IN ('FRANCE', 'GERMANY')
AND li.l_shipmode = 'AIR'
ORDER BY n.n_name, c.c_name, s.s_name, li.l_tax DESC, li.l_extendedprice DESC, li.l_discount DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_QUANTITY AS QuantityShipped,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE AS TotalPriceShipped
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    ORDERS o ON li.L_ORDERKEY = o.O_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERDATE >= '2023-01-01' AND o.O_ORDERDATE < '2024-01-01' -- Assuming we only want orders from the year 2023
ORDER BY
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC,
    o.O_ORDERDATE ASC

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLen,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) AS AvgRegionNameLen,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY AS NationKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, NATION.N_NAME ASC, REGION.R_NAME DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'F' THEN 'Canceled'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'O' THEN 'Open'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS = 'H' THEN 'Held'
        ELSE 'Closed'
    END AS LineStatus
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS))

SELECT
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P_NAME AS PartName,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    P_SIZE,
    S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(NATION.N_NATIONKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE),
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_RETURNED_ITEMS,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS TOTAL_RETRIEVED_ITEMS
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_COUNTRY,
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS TOTAL_SUPPLY_COST,
    AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVERAGE_AVAILABILITY
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, N.N_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)),
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) > 10 AND
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 50
ORDER BY
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) DESC,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) DESC

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD POLISHED COPPER'
AND 
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HOUSEHOLD'
AND 
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
ORDER BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT))
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 500 AND MAX(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) > 15

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_SIZE BETWEEN 1 AND 10
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY, P_CONTAINER, P_RETAILPRICE, S_ADDRESS
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY < (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, S_ADDRESS ASC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT))
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)) > 5 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) > 20

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    S.S_PHONE,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%')
    AND S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'ARGENTINA')
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 20
    AND AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) > 15

SELECT 
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliersCount,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AvgRegionCommentLength
FROM 
    NATION 
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING 
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10 AND 
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10 AND
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) > 50

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AVAILABLE_QUANTITY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SUPPLY_COST,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CUSTOMER_ACCOUNT_BALANCE
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_MFGR = 'ManufacturerX')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_PhoneLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS Avg_SupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_MarketSegmentLength,
    COUNT(*) AS TotalRecords,
    C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY, C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    COUNT(*) > 10

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    p.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    AVG(ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost,
    SUM(ps.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, n.N_NAME, p.P_TYPE, p.P_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_TAX, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME IN ('France','Japan'))
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_TYPE AS PartType,
    PART.P_CONTAINER AS ContainerType,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS AS SupplierAddress,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND PART.P_CONTAINER IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVERAGE_CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(P.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(C.C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(LENGTH(Su.S_PHONE))
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER Su ON Su.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS.PS_PARTKEY) > 100

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    SUM(c.c_acctbal) AS TotalCustomerBalance,
    SUM(s.s_acctbal) AS TotalSupplierBalance,
    r.r_name AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.n_nationkey = s.s_nationkey
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
GROUP BY
    n.n_name, r.r_name
HAVING
    SUM(c.c_acctbal) > 10000 AND SUM(s.s_acctbal) > 5000

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TOTAL_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DISTINCT_COMMENTS,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AVG_PHONE_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AVG_ADDRESS_LENGTH,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) + LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)),
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME) + LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) > 30
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) > 100

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    CASE
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 'R'
        WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'D' THEN 'D'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS L_RETURNSTATUS,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    NATION.N_NAME LIKE '%%%' -- Example: filter by region
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY AS L_QUANTITY FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_QUANTITY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'AUTOMOBILE' THEN 'AUTOMOBILE' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NAME LIKE '%S%' AND PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS Distinct_Customers,
    SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_Balance,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY AND c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 100 AND SUM(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 0

SELECT SUM(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), PART.P_SIZE AS P_SIZE FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_SIZE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, CUSTOMER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    c.C_CUSTKEY,
    n.N_NAME AS CUST_NATION,
    c.C_NAME,
    c.C_PHONE,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    s.S_SUPPKEY,
    s.S_NAME AS SUP_NAME,
    s.S_PHONE,
    s.S_ACCTBAL,
    n2.N_NAME AS SUP_NATION
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY -- Assuming PART table is necessary for reference, though not directly used
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n2 ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n2.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE), REGION.R_NAME FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS Avg_PART_Name_Length,
    AVG(PART.P_SIZE) AS Avg_PART_Size,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Customer_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS Avg_Customer_Name_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS Avg_Customer_MarketSegment_Length
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)

SELECT
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_NAME)) AS AVG_NAME_LENGTH,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_SHIPMODE)) AS AVG_SHIPMODE_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_TAX) AS AVG_TAX,
    SUM(L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS SUM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH,
    AVG(L_DISCOUNT) AS AVG_DISCOUNT,
    L_QUANTITY,
    COUNT(*) AS LINEITEM_COUNT
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    S_NATIONKEY, L_QUANTITY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), SUM(LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000 AND AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.1
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, N_NAME AS NationName, C_NAME AS CustomerName, S_NAME AS SupplierName, PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_AVAILQTY
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0 AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, NATION.N_NAME AS NationName, REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName, S_NAME AS SupplierName, S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > (SELECT AVG(PS_AVAILQTY) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME))

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgNationCommentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)) AS AvgPartBrandLength,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS AvgSupplierCommentLength
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, PS_SUPPKEY, P_CONTAINER, P_MFGR, P_COMMENT, C_NATIONKEY, S_PHONE
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100
AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, C_NATIONKEY, S_PHONE

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    c.C_ACCTBAL,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(p2.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART p2)
AND 
    n.N_NAME LIKE 'USA%'
ORDER BY 
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, 
    c.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 1 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 2000

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) AS part_count,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS avg_retail_price,
    SUM(p.P_SIZE) AS total_size,
    c.C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME, c.C_MKTSEGMENT
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) > 10 AND AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50.00

SELECT
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (
        SELECT
            C_CUSTKEY
        FROM
            CUSTOMER
        WHERE
            C_ACCTBAL > 100000
    )
ORDER BY
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT O.O_ORDERDATE, SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), COUNT(DISTINCT LI.L_PARTKEY)
FROM ORDERS O
JOIN LINEITEM LI ON O.O_ORDERKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
WHERE LI.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE 'R%' -- Exclude returned items
GROUP BY O.O_ORDERDATE
ORDER BY SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(LI.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_TAX,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    PART.P_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_COMMENT, CASE WHEN PART.P_CONTAINER = 'JUMBO PKG' THEN 'JUMBO PKG' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'PROMO BRUSHED TIN' THEN 'PROMO BRUSHED TIN' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#23' THEN 'Brand#23' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' THEN 'BUILDING' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN 'Manufacturer#4' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'AIR' ELSE 'Other' END, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_PHONE

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    p.P_COMMENT AS Part_Comment,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    su.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    su.S_COMMENT AS Supplier_Comment,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS Supply_Cost,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER su ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_NATIONKEY

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(PART.P_SIZE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    o.O_ORDERDATE AS OrderDate,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE AS OrderTotalPrice,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_QUANTITY AS QuantityOrdered
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON li.L_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
    AND o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2023-01-01' AND '2023-12-31'
ORDER BY
    c.C_NAME ASC,
    p.P_NAME ASC,
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 0
ORDER BY AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME, MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), MIN(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, PART.P_NAME
ORDER BY MAX(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) DESC, MIN(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT AVG(ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) FROM ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT))

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < PART.P_SIZE
AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)

SELECT 
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    AVG(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AVG_AVAILQTY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CUSTOMER_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PS.PS_PARTKEY, P.P_NAME, SUP.S_NAME, C.C_NAME, C.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, PART.P_PARTKEY, PART.P_BRAND, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, ORDERS.O_CLERK, ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG, MONTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE) FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)), LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG AS L_RETURNFLAG FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_RETURNFLAG

SELECT AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY)
FROM ORDERS
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY) > 10
ORDER BY AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE) DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUM(l.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(l.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT l.L_PARTKEY) AS NumParts
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(l.L_QUANTITY) > 1000
    AND AVG(l.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.05

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    n_n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n_n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    c.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    n_n.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS COUNTRY_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE '%silver%')

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS NumOfCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumOfSuppliers,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_NATIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME,
    r.R_NAME

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS NationName, 
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName, 
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName, 
    l.L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode, 
    AVG(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice
FROM 
    NATION n
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM l ON s.S_SUPPKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME, s.S_NAME, l.L_SHIPMODE
HAVING 
    AVG(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 1000

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS P_RETAILPRICE FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY P_RETAILPRICE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) ASC

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)) AS AvgMKTSegmentLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    CASE
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR' THEN 'Air'
        WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'RD' THEN 'Road'
        ELSE 'Other'
    END AS ShipModeCategory,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS CustomerNationKey,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM CUSTOMER
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, LineItem.L_SHIPMODE

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT IS NOT NULL THEN LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT) ELSE 0 END) AS AvgMKTSegmentLength, AVG(CASE WHEN SUPPLIER.S_PHONE IS NOT NULL THEN LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE) ELSE 0 END) AS AvgPhoneLength, COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers, SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalCustomerBalance
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL),
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY),
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ASNum_Returned_Items,
    SUM(CASE WHEN L_SHIPMODE LIKE 'AIR%' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) ASNum_Air_Shipments
FROM
    NATION,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
       SUP.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
       REG.R_NAME As Region_Name,
       N.N_NAME As Nation_Name,
       PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
       PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
       C.C_NAME As Customer_Name
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION REG ON N.N_REGIONKEY = REG.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, NATION.N_REGIONKEY, ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE, ORDERS.O_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT, LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, N.N_REGIONKEY AS REGION_KEY
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'SOUTHEAST ASIA')
AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
ORDER BY
    PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, PS_AVAILQTY DESC

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    pu.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    su.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price
FROM 
    PARTSUPP pu
JOIN 
    PART p ON pu.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER su ON pu.PS_SUPPKEY = su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE 
    p.P_TYPE = 'COMPONENT'
    AND su.S_NATIONKEY = (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'JAPAN')
    AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY 
    pu.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, p.P_RETAILPRICE ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    Su.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    (PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST / PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS COST_PER_UNIT,
    Su.S_ACCTBAL AS SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER Su ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = Su.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON Su.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY > 100 AND P.P_PARTKEY < 200

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
JOIN
    PART AS P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
    AND SUP.S_ACCTBAL > 1000000
    AND N.N_REGIONKEY = (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS Nation,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS DistinctCustomers,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS DistinctSuppliers,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_ORDERKEY,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM Li ON S.S_SUPPKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'Party Region')

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME,
    NATION.N_NAME
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    p.P_PARTKEY,
    s.S_NATIONKEY,
    n.N_NAME AS SupplyingNation,
    c.C_NATIONKEY AS BuyingNation,
    c.C_NAME AS BuyerName,
    pss.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    pss.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP pss
JOIN 
    PART p ON pss.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON pss.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION buyingNation ON c.C_NATIONKEY = buyingNation.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY 
    pss.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    buyingNation.N_NAME ASC,
    p.P_PARTKEY ASC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON s.S_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > 1000.00
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME DESC, c.C_NAME, li.L_SHIPDATE DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, PS_SUPPLYCOST, P_SIZE, P_NAME, S_NAME, C_NAME, C_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, C_ACCTBAL DESC, P_SIZE ASC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) AS PartTypesCount,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
    SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT p.P_NAME) > 10 AND AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) > 50 AND SUM(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 100000

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME AS SuppliersNationName,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_COMMENT As Comment
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS PS
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION AS N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION AS R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPKEY,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AverageCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AverageSupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG))

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 0
AND
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_C_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_C_Phone_Length,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_C_Account_Balance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Supp_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_S_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_S_Address_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_S_Comment_Length
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME))

SELECT 
    n.n_name AS customer_nation_name,
    c.c_name AS customer_name,
    s.s_name AS supplier_name,
    li.l_extendedprice,
    li.l_discount
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.c_custkey = li.l_suppkey
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey
WHERE 
    n.n_regionkey = 1 -- replace 1 with desired region key
    AND li.l_comment LIKE '%urgent%' -- filter for specific comment type
    AND s.s_name NOT LIKE 'Supplier%' -- exclude suppliers with 'Supplier' in their name
ORDER BY 
    li.l_extendedprice - (li.l_extendedprice * li.l_discount / 100) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL > (SELECT AVG(S_ACCTBAL) FROM SUPPLIER)
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT DESC, REGION.R_NAME ASC, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT,
        MONTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE),
        YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE),
        SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
        LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY,
        LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE
FROM NATION
JOIN ORDERS ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = ORDERS.O_CUSTKEY -- assuming O_CUSTKEY corresponds to customer, and by extension nation
JOIN LINEITEM ON ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY = LINEITEM.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE) = 2023 -- assuming we're interested in orders from 2023
AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE '%R%' -- excluding returned items
AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY > 50 -- assuming some regional criteria
ORDER BY NATION.N_COMMENT DESC, MONTH(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE), LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_PARTKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'STANDARD POLISHED BRASS' THEN 'STANDARD POLISHED BRASS' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM PARTSUPP JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_SHIPDATE
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped' -- Examples of more complex orders: o.O_TOTALPRICE > 1000, etc.
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS PartRetailPrice,
    S.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'FRANCE')
    AND P.P_TYPE = ' component '
    AND C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > C.C_ACCTBAL

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT = 'DELIVER IN PERSON' THEN 'DELIVER IN PERSON' ELSE 'Other' END FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), PART.P_BRAND AS P_BRAND FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_BRAND

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) AS AverageDiscount
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON s.S_SUPPKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 1 AND SUM(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 100000 AND AVG(li.L_DISCOUNT) < 0.1

SELECT 
    n.N_NAME AS Supplier_Country,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    s.S_PHONE AS Supplier_Phone,
    s.S_ADDRESS AS Supplier_Address,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_TAX,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name
FROM 
    LINEITEM li
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME LIKE 'United%')
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, s.S_NAME ASC, n.N_NAME ASC, r.R_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
    AND LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'AIR'
ORDER BY
    CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, NATION.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY), LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LINESTATUS FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_LINESTATUS

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PART.P_SIZE > 10 AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE < 50 AND REGION.R_REGIONKEY IN (1, 3)
ORDER BY REGION.R_REGIONKEY ASC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC, PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(S_ACCTBAL) > 500000
ORDER BY AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CASE WHEN PART.P_BRAND = 'Brand#22' THEN 'Brand#22' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY  JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE * LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TOTAL_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AVERAGE_DISCOUNT,
    COUNT(LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY) AS TOTAL_LINE_ITEM_COUNT
FROM 
    NATION,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM,
    REGION
WHERE 
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY 
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY 
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY 
    NATION.N_COMMENT, 
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME, 
    LINEITEM.L_COMMENT, 
    REGION.R_NAME

SELECT
    PS_PARTKEY,
    N_NATIONKEY,
    N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C_NATIONKEY,
    C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP
JOIN
    NATION ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 1000
    AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > 50
    AND NATION.N_NAME NOT LIKE 'ANTARCTICA%'

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS CountryName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    COUNT(C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCountPerCountry,
    AVG(C.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalancePerCountry,
    COUNT(S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCountPerCountry,
    AVG(S.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalancePerCountry
FROM
    NATION N
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_MKTSEGMENT, S.S_NAME

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    c.C_CUSTKEY IN (SELECT L_SUPPKEY FROM LINEITEM WHERE L_RETURNFLAG = 'A')
    AND s.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT L_SUPPKEY FROM LINEITEM WHERE L_RETURNFLAG = 'A')
ORDER BY 
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, c.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplierCost,
       AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice,
       AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)) AS AvgCustomerNameLength,
       AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    P_NAME AS PartName,
    P_SIZE,
    P_RETAILPRICE,
    PS_AVAILQTY,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N_REGIONKEY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP 
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN 
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    L_SHIPMODE AS ShippingMode,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AvgExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantity,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS)) AS AvgLineStatusLength
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    L_SHIPMODE

SELECT N.N_NAME AS Nation, C.C_NAME AS Customer, P.P_NAME AS Part, S.S_NAME AS Supplier, C.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerAccountBalance, SUM(P.P_RETAILPRICE) AS TotalRetailPrice
FROM NATION N
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN PART P ON C.C_CUSTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_ACCTBAL
ORDER BY N.N_NAME ASC, SUM(P.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
WHERE NATION.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT LIKE '%developing%')
AND LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG NOT LIKE '%RETURN%'
AND LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT < 0.05
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME ASC, ABS(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) DESC, CUSTOMER.C_NAME ASC, SUPPLIER.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    SUP.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    N.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS Available_Quantity,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST As Supply_Cost,
    P.P_TYPE AS Part_Type,
    P.P_RETAILPRICE AS Retail_Price,
    SUP.S_ACCTBAL As Supplier_Account_Balance
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
        AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthNation,
        AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLengthCustomer,
        AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLengthSupplier
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL, SUPPLIER.S_NAME
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 10

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AvgSupplyCost,
 PART.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
 COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
 SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailQuantity
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 100

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_NAME)) FROM NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    p.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'Component')
    AND c.C_ACCTBAL > 1000
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > 5000

SELECT
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgSupplyQuantity,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupplierNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS AvgCustomerPhoneLength,
    S_NATIONKEY AS SupplierNationKey
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    C_MKTSEGMENT, S_NATIONKEY
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
    AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10
    AND AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) > 20

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) AS AvgNameLen, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSupNameLen
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)) > 10 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 10

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    MAX(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MaxSupplyCost,
    SUM(PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    MAX(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL),
    MIN(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL

SELECT 
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE,
    li.L_SHIPDATE,
    li.L_SHIPMODE
FROM 
    PART p
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    li.L_PARTKEY = (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME = 'Some Specific Part Name') -- replace 'Some Specific Part Name' with an actual part name if known
ORDER BY 
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    li.L_RECEIPTDATE DESC,
    li.L_SHIPDATE ASC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 10000
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_PHONE As SupplierPhone,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    NATION N
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON N.N_NATIONKEY = S.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT C.C_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER C WHERE C.C_ACCTBAL > 10000)
    AND R.R_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT RG.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION RG WHERE RG.R_NAME LIKE 'North%')
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME, R.R_NAME

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY) AS OrderCount,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerAccountBalance,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgLineitemTax,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE) AS OrderYear
FROM
    NATION,
    ORDERS,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    YEAR(ORDERS.O_ORDERDATE)

SELECT
    PS.PS_PARTKEY,
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_COMMENT,
    N.N_COMMENT,
    S.S_COMMENT,
    S.S_PHONE,
    S.S_SUPPKEY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER C ON S.S_NATIONKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 1000

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    n.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_TYPE,
    o.O_TOTALPRICE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'F' -- Filter for 'F' status indicating 'Shipped' orders
    AND li.L_SHIPMODE IS NOT NULL -- Exclude rows with no shipping mode
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC, o.O_TOTALPRICE DESC

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    s.S_PHONE AS Supplier_Phone,
    s.S_ADDRESS As Supplier_Address,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_DISCOUNT,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name
FROM
    LINEITEM li
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    li.L_RETURNFLAG NOT IN ('A', 'R')
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME, r.R_NAME, s.S_NAME, li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, li.L_DISCOUNT DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice
FROM
    PART p
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, p.P_RETAILPRICE
HAVING
    COUNT(DISTINCT c.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.S_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT 
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
AND 
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_TYPE = 'Brass')
AND 
    N.N_NAME LIKE 'North%'
AND 
    C.C_ACCTBAL > 5000
ORDER BY 
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL ASC,
    P.P_PARTKEY ASC

SELECT
    o.O_ORDERDATE,
    c.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    li.L_SHIPMODE,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    ORDERS o
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON o.O_ORDERKEY = li.L_ORDERKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON o.O_CUSTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    o.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'Shipped'
AND
    o.O_ORDERDATE BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31'
AND
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE > li.L_DISCOUNT * li.L_QUANTITY
ORDER BY
    o.O_ORDERDATE DESC,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC,
    li.L_QUANTITY DESC,
    s.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_Address_Length,
