    AVG(LENGTH(C_PHONE)) AS Avg_Phone_Length,
    SUM(C_ACCTBAL) AS Total_AcctBal,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_Supplier_Comments,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_PHONE)) AS Avg_S_Phone_Length,
    AVG(LENGTH(S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_S_Address_Length,
    C_MKTSEGMENT AS Customer_Market_Segment,
    S_NATIONKEY AS Supplier_NationKey
FROM
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER
WHERE
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY,
    C_MKTSEGMENT,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT PART.P_NAME AS P_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS Avg_SupplyCost, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) AS Avg_RetailPrice, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)) AS Avg_CommentLength, PART.P_SIZE AS P_Size, SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS Total_Supplier_AccountBal
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_SIZE

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE), CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG = 'A' THEN 'A' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPDATE, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgSuppNameLength,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT > 1 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS HighDiscountExtendedPriceSum,
    SUM(CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT <= 1 THEN LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE ELSE 0 END) AS LowOrNoDiscountExtendedPriceSum,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)) AS AvgShipModeLength,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) AS AvgTax,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_COMMENT)) AS AvgCommentLength,
    LINEITEM.L_LINESTATUS AS L_LineStatus
FROM
    SUPPLIER
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    L_LINESTATUS

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_LINENUMBER), LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT AS L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_SHIPINSTRUCT
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_COMMENT,
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    P.P_TYPE,
    S.S_PHONE,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    R.R_NAME AS NATION_REGION
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER S ON S.S_SUPPKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN PART P ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    n.n_name AS NationName,
    c.c_name AS CustomerName,
    c.c_acctbal AS CustomerAccountBalance,
    s.s_name AS SupplierName,
    s.s_acctbal AS SupplierAccountBalance
FROM
    NATION n
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.n_nationkey = c.c_nationkey
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.c_custkey = s.s_suppkey
WHERE
    n.n_nationkey IN (SELECT n.n_nationkey FROM NATION n WHERE n.n_regionkey IN (SELECT r_regionkey FROM REGION WHERE r_regionkey IS NOT NULL))
    AND c.c_mktsegment = 'BUILDING'
    AND s.s_acctbal > 0

SELECT CASE WHEN PART.P_MFGR = 'Manufacturer#4' THEN 'Manufacturer#4' ELSE 'Other' END, PART.P_RETAILPRICE, ORDERS.O_COMMENT, ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERPRIORITY = '1-URGENT' THEN '1-URGENT' ELSE 'Other' END, CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 'MACHINERY' ELSE 'Other' END, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, CASE WHEN LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE = 'FOB' THEN 'FOB' ELSE 'Other' END, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, REGION WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(ORDERS.O_TOTALPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_TAX) FROM ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    P.P_PARTKEY,
    MIN(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS MIN_SUPPLY_COST,
    C.C_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_CUSTKEY,
    S.S_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME
FROM 
    PART P
JOIN 
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    P.P_PARTKEY, 
    P.P_NAME, 
    S.S_NAME, 
    C.C_NAME, 
    C.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY 
    MIN(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) ASC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Shipped,
    AVG(li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    MAX(li.L_SHIPDATE) AS Latest_ShipDate
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON c.C_CUSTKEY = li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(li.L_QUANTITY) > 1000

SELECT PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_TYPE, NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) > 100 AND SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000
ORDER BY AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_CAddress_Len,
AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) AS Avg_CPhone_Len,
AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_CAccountBal,
COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS Distinct_SComment,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS Avg_SPhone_Len,
AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS Avg_SAddress_Len,
CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY
FROM CUSTOMER
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) > 1

SELECT 
    P.P_NAME,
    S.S_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    N.N_REGIONKEY AS REGION_KEY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CS.C_ACCTBAL
FROM 
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN 
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER CS ON P.P_PARTKEY = CS.C_CUSTKEY
ORDER BY 
    P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    CS.C_ACCTBAL ASC NULLS FIRST,
    N.N_NAME,
    S.S_NAME

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    P.P_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TOTAL_AVAILABLE_QUANTITY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, P.P_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY)
FROM NATION
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
ORDER BY SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)) ASC

SELECT SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), COUNT(DISTINCT PART.P_PARTKEY), AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL), PART.P_MFGR AS P_MFGR FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND PART.P_PARTKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY GROUP BY P_MFGR ORDER BY SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY)

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)), LINEITEM.L_COMMITDATE AS L_COMMITDATE FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY L_COMMITDATE ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME))

SELECT
    n.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN c.C_CUSTKEY IS NOT NULL THEN c.C_CUSTKEY END) AS SupplierCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN s.S_SUPPKEY IS NOT NULL THEN s.S_SUPPKEY END) AS CustomerCount,
    SUM(CASE WHEN c.C_CUSTKEY IS NOT NULL THEN c.C_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS CustomerTotalBalance,
    SUM(CASE WHEN s.S_SUPPKEY IS NOT NULL THEN s.S_ACCTBAL ELSE 0 END) AS SupplierTotalBalance
FROM
    NATION n
LEFT JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON n.N_NATIONKEY = s.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CASE WHEN PART.P_TYPE = 'MEDIUM ANODIZED NICKEL' THEN 'MEDIUM ANODIZED NICKEL' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_CLERK, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT FROM NATION, PART, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT n.N_NAME, c.C_NAME, c.C_PHONE, c.C_ACCTBAL
FROM NATION n
JOIN CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
WHERE n.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT r.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION r WHERE r.R_REGIONKEY > (SELECT AVG(r.R_REGIONKEY) FROM REGION r) - 10)
AND n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT c_nationkey FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_ACCTBAL > 1000000)
AND c.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY c.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS ProductName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    sup.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    sup.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    c.C_ACCTBAL As AccountBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP AS sup
JOIN
    PART AS p ON sup.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER AS c ON sup.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION AS n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER AS s ON sup.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    REGION AS r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER C ON P.P_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    N.N_REGIONKEY = ( -- assuming region filter for demonstration, adjust as needed
        SELECT R_REGIONKEY
        FROM REGION
        WHERE R_NAME = 'North America'
    )
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'HEALTH' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) + AVG(CASE WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'TECHNOLOGY' THEN CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ELSE NULL END) AS MKT_Segment_Avg_ACCTBAL, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, NATION
WHERE SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
AND CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS Nation_Name,
    COUNT(c.C_CUSTKEY) AS Num_Customers,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Customer_Balance,
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) AS Num_Suppliers,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS Avg_Supplier_Balance,
    r.R_NAME AS Region_Name
FROM
    NATION n
    INNER JOIN REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
    INNER JOIN CUSTOMER c ON n.N_NATIONKEY = c.C_NATIONKEY
    INNER JOIN SUPPLIER s ON s.S_NATIONKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    n.N_NAME,
    r.R_NAME

SELECT P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION R WHERE R.R_NAME = 'SOME_REGION')
AND P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT
    P.P_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    C.C_ACCTBAL,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PART P
JOIN
    PARTSUPP PS ON P.P_PARTKEY = PS.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON C.C_CUSTKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT PS_PARTKEY FROM PARTSUPP WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 0)
AND
    S.S_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME = 'SPACE')
AND
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING'
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    P.P_NAME ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    s.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    n.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    r.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME,
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY,
    ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM
    PARTSUPP ps
JOIN
    PART p ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    ps.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > 50000
    AND n.N_NAME LIKE '%%%'

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    SUP.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST AS SupplyCost,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY AS AvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER SUP ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = SUP.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON SUP.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    N.N_NAME IN (SELECT N_NAME FROM NATION WHERE N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION WHERE R_NAME = 'EUROPE'))
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_CONTAINER,
    PART.P_NAME AS PartName,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CASE
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'CONSUMER' THEN 'Consumer'
        WHEN CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BULK' THEN 'Bulk'
        ELSE 'Unknown Segment'
    END AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PART.P_TYPE AS ProductType,
    PART.P_BRAND AS ProductBrand,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS MarketSegment,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL As SupplierBalance
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM 
    REGION R
JOIN 
    NATION N ON R.R_REGIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R2.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION R2 WHERE R2.R_NAME = 'NORTH AMERICA')

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, CUST.C_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PART P
JOIN PARTSUPP ON P.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER CUST ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = CUST.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN NATION N_PART ON P.P_PARTKEY = N_PART.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN NATION N_SUPP ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N_SUPP.N_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY CUST.C_ACCTBAL DESC, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC, P.P_NAME

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    COUNT(DISTINCT C.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount,
    COUNT(DISTINCT S.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount,
    SUM(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TotalExtendedPrice,
    AVG(LI.L_DISCOUNT) AS AvgDiscount
FROM 
    NATION N 
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM LI ON C.C_CUSTKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    N.N_NAME

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT)) FROM NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))

SELECT SUM(PART.P_RETAILPRICE), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE)), COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT) FROM PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE))

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST)

SELECT P.P_NAME, C.C_NATIONKEY, C.C_ADDRESS, C.C_NAME, C.C_PHONE, C.C_ACCTBAL, S.S_NAME, S.S_PHONE, S.S_ADDRESS, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PART p
JOIN PARTSUPP ps ON p.P_PARTKEY = ps.PS_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER s ON ps.PS_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER c ON ps.PS_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE p.P_NAME LIKE '%e%'
ORDER BY c.C_ACCTBAL DESC, ps.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC, s.S_NAME DESC

SELECT
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    SUM(l.L_QUANTITY) AS Total_Quantity_Sold,
    AVG(l.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS Average_Price_Sold,
    SUM(l.L_DISCOUNT) AS Total_Discount_Given,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT l.L_PARTKEY) AS Number_Of_Parts_Sold
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    LINEITEM l ON c.C_CUSTKEY = l.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON l.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNation,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    L.L_TAX,
    L.L_DISCOUNT,
    L.L_QUANTITY,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_PHONE,
    S.S_ADDRESS
FROM
    LINEITEM L
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON L.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON L.L_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT = 'BUILDING' -- Or any other specific market segment you're interested in
ORDER BY
    N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, L.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC, L.L_QUANTITY DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS N_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS S_Name,
    SUPPLIER.S_PHONE AS S_Phone,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS AS S_Address,
    REGION.R_NAME AS R_Name,
    REGION.R_COMMENT AS R_Comment
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > 100.00
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    NATION.N_NAME ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CustomerCount, AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgAccountBalance, COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) AS SupplierCount, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM NATION
LEFT JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
LEFT JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) > 10 AND COUNT(SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY) > 5

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    Li.L_DISCOUNT,
    Li.L_QUANTITY
FROM 
    NATION N
JOIN 
    CUSTOMER C ON N.N_NATIONKEY = C.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM Li ON C.C_CUSTKEY = Li.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER S ON Li.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_COMMENT = 'Independent')
    AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 50000
ORDER BY 
    Li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_LineStatus)) AS Avg_Length_LineStatus,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_Discount) AS Total_Discount,
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_ExtendedPrice) AS Avg_ExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_Quantity) AS Total_Quantity
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_ShipMode

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    C.C_NATIONKEY,
    C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    C.C_ACCTBAL
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT C_CUSTKEY FROM CUSTOMER WHERE C_MKTSEGMENT = 'WELL-BUILT')
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY ASC,
    C.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_COMMENT,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    CUSTOMER.C_PHONE,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS,
    LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE,
    LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT,
    LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY
FROM
    NATION,
    PART,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND PART.P_PARTKEY = LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    NATION.N_COMMENT ASC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS))
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) > 500000
ORDER BY AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_Phone
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
WHERE PART.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART)
AND CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL < (SELECT AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) FROM CUSTOMER)
AND LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS) > 50
ORDER BY PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL ASC

SELECT
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME, C.C_NAME, S.S_NAME
HAVING
    SUM(PS.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME, AVG(CAST(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) AS FLOAT)) AS AvgCustNameLen, AVG(CAST(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME) AS FLOAT)) AS AvgSupplierNameLen
FROM NATION
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, REGION.R_NAME

SELECT 
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL)
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN 
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL
HAVING 
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000 AND AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) > 5000

SELECT 
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) AS AvgCustomerBalance,
    AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) AS AvgSupplierBalance
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY 
    c.C_NAME, s.S_NAME, n.N_NAME
HAVING 
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) > 1000 AND AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) > 500
ORDER BY 
    AVG(c.C_ACCTBAL) DESC, AVG(s.S_ACCTBAL) DESC

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE,
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME,
    PART.P_BRAND,
    PART.P_SIZE,
    NATION.N_REGIONKEY
FROM
    NATION
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    PART ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    PART.P_BRAND IN ('Brand#19', 'Brand#21')
    AND PART.P_SIZE > 10
    AND PART.P_RETAILPRICE > 50
ORDER BY
    PART.P_RETAILPRICE DESC

SELECT 
    N.N_NAME AS SupplierNationName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    S.S_PHONE,
    S.S_ADDRESS,
    LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    LI.L_SHIPDATE,
    R.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM 
    SUPPLIER S
JOIN 
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    LINEITEM LI ON S.S_SUPPKEY = LI.L_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    REGION R ON N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE 
    N.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N.N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION N WHERE N.N_REGIONKEY IN (SELECT R.R_REGIONKEY FROM REGION R WHERE R_NAME = 'SOME_REGION_NAME'))
ORDER BY 
    LI.L_SHIPDATE DESC, S.S_NAME ASC

SELECT
    N_NAME AS Nation,
    C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    NATION N ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    N_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_COMMENT, PART.P_TYPE, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, REGION.R_NAME FROM PARTSUPP, NATION, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY ORDER BY CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    P_MFGR,
    AVG(P_RETAILPRICE),
    COUNT(DISTINCT C_CUSTKEY),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_NAME)),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_TYPE)),
    AVG(LENGTH(P_BRAND)),
    AVG(LENGTH(C_ADDRESS)),
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL),
    C_MKTSEGMENT
FROM
    PART
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    P_MFGR,
    C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT NATION.N_NAME AS SupplierNation, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS AvgAvailQty, AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength, SUM(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAcctBal
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NAME
HAVING AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 1000 AND AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) > 5

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME,
    s.S_NAME,
    p.P_TYPE,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE,
    n.N_NAME AS NationName
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_RETAILPRICE > (SELECT AVG(p2.P_RETAILPRICE) FROM PART p2)
ORDER BY
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, n.N_NAME ASC, c.C_NAME DESC, s.S_NAME ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), AVG(LINEITEM.L_QUANTITY) FROM NATION, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME))

SELECT 
    PART.P_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS Nation,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM 
    PARTSUPP
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
AND 
    NATION.N_NAME LIKE 'Sca%' -- as an example, filter by Nation name starting with 'Sca'
ORDER BY 
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME

SELECT AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE))

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'P' THEN 'P' ELSE 'Other' END, CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS, CUSTOMER.C_PHONE, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY, REGION.R_REGIONKEY FROM NATION, ORDERS, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM, REGION WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY=REGION.R_REGIONKEY

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_SHIPMODE)), AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT), SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY AS S_NATIONKEY FROM CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY GROUP BY S_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, LINEITEM.L_TAX, REGION.R_NAME, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM NATION INNER JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, N_NAME AS Supplier_Nation_Name, R_NAME AS Region_Name, S_PHONE
FROM PARTSUPP
JOIN SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE PS_AVAILQTY > 1000 AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT NATION.N_NATIONKEY, AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL), AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), REGION.R_NAME
FROM NATION
JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY NATION.N_NATIONKEY, REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC, NATION.N_NATIONKEY ASC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM NATION, PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND))

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, PART.P_NAME, PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PART.P_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN NATION ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY > 100 AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME DESC, PART.P_NAME ASC, CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL DESC

SELECT
    AVG(PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)*PART.P_SIZE),
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT)*PART.P_RETAILPRICE),
    AVG(LINEITEM.L_DISCOUNT*PART.P_SIZE*SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM
    PART, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_PARTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY

SELECT
    PART.P_NAME,
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST),
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY),
    COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY),
    PART.P_TYPE
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    PART
ON
    PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
GROUP BY
    PART.P_NAME,
    PART.P_TYPE
HAVING
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 1000
    AND SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) > 500
    AND COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY) > 3
ORDER BY
    AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_CONTAINER)), AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) FROM PARTSUPP JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, SUPPLIER WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT))

SELECT
    C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AVG_PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    AVG(C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_C_ACCTBAL,
    AVG(S_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_S_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_PARTKEY) AS NUM_PARTS,
    COUNT(DISTINCT PS_SUPPKEY) AS NUM_SUPPLIERS
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND, AVG(PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_TYPE)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_BRAND)), AVG(SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL)
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, PART.P_TYPE, PART.P_BRAND

SELECT
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AvgNameLength,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_PHONE) + LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_PHONE)) AS AvgPhoneLength,
    SUM(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS TotalAccountBalance,
    COUNT(DISTINCT SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT) AS DistinctSupplierComments,
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY AS C_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS) * LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_ADDRESS)) AS AvgAddressLength
FROM
    CUSTOMER
JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    C_NATIONKEY

SELECT PS_PARTKEY, P_NAME, C_NAME, S_NAME, PS_AVAILQTY, PS_SUPPLYCOST
FROM PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN PART ON PART.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
WHERE PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY < 100 AND PS_SUPPLYCOST > (SELECT AVG(PS_SUPPLYCOST) FROM PARTSUPP)

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PartName,
    S.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    C.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) AS AverageSupplyCost
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
GROUP BY
    P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, C.C_NAME
HAVING
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) > 10000
ORDER BY
    AVG(PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST) DESC

SELECT PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
FROM PART
JOIN CUSTOMER ON PART.P_PARTKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN LINEITEM ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY PART.P_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_NAME, SUPPLIER.S_NAME, YEAR(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE), MONTH(LINEITEM.L_RECEIPTDATE)
HAVING AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) > 5000
ORDER BY AVG(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) DESC

SELECT NATION.N_NAME, customer_segments.SEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
FROM NATION
JOIN (
    SELECT C_NATIONKEY,
         CASE
             WHEN C_MKTSEGMENT = 'MACHINERY' THEN 'MACHINERY'
             ELSE 'Other'
         END AS SEGMENT
    FROM CUSTOMER
) AS customer_segments ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = customer_segments.C_NATIONKEY
JOIN CUSTOMER ON NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
ORDER BY NATION.N_NAME, customer_segments.SEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NAME,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUSTOMER_COUNT,
    S_NATIONKEY,
    AVG(LENGTH(SUPPLIER.S_NAME)) AS AVG_SUPPLIER_NAME_LENGTH,
    SUM(LINEITEM.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS TOTAL_LINEITEM_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    AVG(LENGTH(LINEITEM.L_RETURNFLAG)) AS AVG_LINEITEM_RETURNFLAG_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    LINEITEM
WHERE
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY = CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY
    AND CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY
    AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NAME,
    S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    SUM(PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY) AS TotalAvailableQuantity
FROM
    PARTSUPP
INNER JOIN
    SUPPLIER ON PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
INNER JOIN
    NATION ON SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
INNER JOIN
    REGION ON NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    NATION.N_NAME,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME,
    REGION.R_NAME
ORDER BY
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME, P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME, C.C_NAME AS CUSTOMER_NAME, S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME, R.R_NAME AS REGION_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP, NATION N, PART P, CUSTOMER C, SUPPLIER S, REGION R
WHERE C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
AND P.P_PARTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY
AND C.C_CUSTKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
AND N.N_REGIONKEY = R.R_REGIONKEY
AND S.S_SUPPKEY = PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY
AND (N.N_NAME || ',' || P.P_NAME || ',' || C.C_NAME || ',' || S.S_NAME || ',' || R.R_NAME) IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION.N_NAME, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT, CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY, SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL, REGION.R_COMMENT FROM PARTSUPP, NATION JOIN REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY=NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CUSTOMER, SUPPLIER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY ORDER BY SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY

SELECT
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY,
    COUNT(CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY) AS CUST_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)) AS AVG_COMMENT_LENGTH,
    AVG(CUSTOMER.C_ACCTBAL) AS AVG_ACCTBAL,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT) AS MKTSEGMENT_COUNT,
    AVG(LENGTH(REGION.R_COMMENT)) AS AVG_REGION_COMMENT_LENGTH
FROM
    NATION
JOIN
    CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    REGION ON REGION.R_REGIONKEY = NATION.N_REGIONKEY
GROUP BY
    NATION.N_NATIONKEY

SELECT NATION.N_REGIONKEY, CASE WHEN ORDERS.O_ORDERSTATUS = 'O' THEN 'O' ELSE 'Other' END, ORDERS.O_CLERK, ORDERS.O_SHIPPRIORITY, SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY, LINEITEM.L_SHIPINSTRUCT FROM NATION, ORDERS, SUPPLIER, LINEITEM WHERE SUPPLIER.S_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=ORDERS.O_ORDERKEY AND LINEITEM.L_SUPPKEY=SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY

SELECT 
    c.C_CUSTKEY,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    c.C_PHONE AS CustomerPhone,
    c.C_ACCTBAL AS CustomerBalance,
    n_c.N_NAME AS CustomerNation,
    s.S_SUPPKEY,
    s.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    s.S_PHONE AS SupplierPhone,
    s.S_ACCTBAL AS SupplierBalance,
    n_s.N_NAME AS SupplierNation
FROM 
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN 
    NATION n_c ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n_c.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN 
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
JOIN 
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN 
    NATION n_s ON s.S_NATIONKEY = n_s.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE 
    n_c.N_NATIONKEY = n_s.N_NATIONKEY
    AND c.C_ACCTBAL > 0
    AND s.S_ACCTBAL > 0

SELECT PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY, PARTSUPP.PS_COMMENT, NATION.N_NATIONKEY, PART.P_COMMENT, PART.P_BRAND, CUSTOMER.C_COMMENT, SUPPLIER.S_PHONE, SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL FROM PARTSUPP INNER JOIN SUPPLIER ON SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY, NATION, PART, CUSTOMER WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY AND CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY=CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY

SELECT P.P_NAME, S.S_NAME, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST, N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME
FROM PARTSUPP PS
JOIN PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE P.P_SIZE > 50 AND PS.PS_AVAILQTY < 1000 AND S.S_ACCTBAL > 100000
ORDER BY P.P_RETAILPRICE DESC, PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC, N.N_NAME DESC

SELECT
    PARTSUPP.PS_PARTKEY,
    NATION.N_NAME AS NationName,
    CUSTOMER.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    SUPPLIER.S_NAME AS SupplierName,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL,
    REGION.R_NAME AS RegionName,
    PARTSUPP.PS_AVAILQTY,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT
FROM
    PARTSUPP,
    NATION,
    CUSTOMER,
    SUPPLIER,
    REGION
WHERE
    CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY = NATION.N_NATIONKEY
    AND SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY = CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY
    AND PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPKEY = SUPPLIER.S_SUPPKEY
    AND NATION.N_REGIONKEY = REGION.R_REGIONKEY
ORDER BY
    NATION.N_NAME ASC,
    SUPPLIER.S_ACCTBAL DESC,
    PARTSUPP.PS_SUPPLYCOST ASC,
    CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT,
    SUPPLIER.S_COMMENT

SELECT
    P.P_NAME AS PART_NAME,
    S.S_NAME AS SUPPLIER_NAME,
    N.N_NAME AS NATION_NAME,
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST,
    PS.PS_AVAILQTY
FROM
    PARTSUPP PS
JOIN
    PART P ON PS.PS_PARTKEY = P.P_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON PS.PS_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON S.S_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
WHERE
    P.P_PARTKEY IN (SELECT P_PARTKEY FROM PART WHERE P_NAME LIKE 'A%') -- Filter parts starting with 'A'
    AND N.N_NAME = 'ANTARCTICA' -- Filter nations as Antarctica
    AND S_ACCTBAL > 1000000 -- Filter suppliers with account balance greater than 1,000,000
ORDER BY
    PS.PS_SUPPLYCOST DESC, P.P_NAME ASC, S.S_NAME ASC, N.N_NAME ASC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME AS Part_Name,
    c.C_NAME AS Customer_Name,
    s.S_NAME AS Supplier_Name,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE,
    li.L_QUANTITY,
    li.L_TAX,
    li.L_DISCOUNT
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    LINEITEM li ON p.P_PARTKEY = li.L_PARTKEY
JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON li.L_SUPPKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
WHERE
    li.L_RETURNFLAG = 'R' -- Only interested in 'Returned' items
ORDER BY
    p.P_NAME,
    li.L_EXTENDEDPRICE DESC

SELECT
    p.P_NAME,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) AS NumSuppliers,
    AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) AS AvgRetailPrice
FROM
    PART p
JOIN
    CUSTOMER c ON p.P_PARTKEY = c.C_CUSTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    SUPPLIER s ON c.C_CUSTKEY = s.S_SUPPKEY
GROUP BY
    p.P_NAME, c.C_NAME
HAVING
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) > 1 AND AVG(p_retailPrice) > 100
ORDER BY
    COUNT(s.S_SUPPKEY) DESC, AVG(p.P_RETAILPRICE) DESC

SELECT AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_COMMENT)), AVG(LENGTH(NATION.N_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(PART.P_NAME)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_ADDRESS)), AVG(LENGTH(CUSTOMER.C_NAME)), CUSTOMER.C_MKTSEGMENT AS C_MKTSEGMENT FROM NATION, PART INNER JOIN CUSTOMER ON CUSTOMER.C_CUSTKEY=PART.P_PARTKEY WHERE CUSTOMER.C_NATIONKEY=NATION.N_NATIONKEY GROUP BY C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    N.N_NAME AS NationName,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT AS CustomerMarketSegment,
    AVG(LI.L_EXTENDEDPRICE) AS AverageExtendedPrice,
    SUM(LI.L_QUANTITY) AS TotalQuantityShipped
FROM
    LINEITEM LI
JOIN
    SUPPLIER S ON LI.L_SUPPKEY = S.S_SUPPKEY
JOIN
    CUSTOMER C ON S.S_SUPPKEY = C.C_CUSTKEY
JOIN
    NATION N ON C.C_NATIONKEY = N.N_NATIONKEY
GROUP BY
    N.N_NAME,
    C.C_MKTSEGMENT

SELECT
    n.N_NAME AS NationName,
    p.P_NAME AS PartName,
    c.C_NAME AS CustomerName,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE AS RetailPrice,
    r.R_NAME AS RegionName
FROM
    CUSTOMER c
JOIN
    NATION n ON c.C_NATIONKEY = n.N_NATIONKEY
JOIN
    PART p ON c.C_CUSTKEY = p.P_PARTKEY
LEFT JOIN
    REGION r ON n.N_REGIONKEY = r.R_REGIONKEY
WHERE
    p.P_TYPE = 'PRETENDER'
    AND p.P_RETAILPRICE > 50.00
    AND n.N_NATIONKEY IN (SELECT N_NATIONKEY FROM NATION WHERE N_NAME IN ('FRANCE', 'GERMANY', 'ITALY'))
ORDER BY
    n.N_NAME ASC,
    p.P_RETAILPRICE DESC,
    c.C_NAME ASC
